 <office:body>
  <office:text text:use-soft-page-breaks="true">
   <text:sequence-decls>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Illustration"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Table"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Text"/>
    <text:sequence-decl text:display-outline-level="0" text:name="Drawing"/>
   </text:sequence-decls>
   <text:p text:style-name="P2">scripta, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. diligenter retractare et quasi r. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid härledn. af</text:span> religio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> religiosus), C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till denna betydelse hör ock</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">part.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭgens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">From, gudfruktig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ur ett</text:span> antiquum carmen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">anfördt af</text:span> Nigidius Figulus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ifrån honom hos</text:span> Gell. IV. 9.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sēlĭgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttaga, -plocka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från mängden), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utwälja:</text:span></text:span> exempla; bonum; sententiæ s-tæ, C. - judices s-ti (i. e. a prætore electi: prætores urbani debent optimum quemque in selectos judices referre), C., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sēlectio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utplockande, urwal, wal:</text:span></text:span> iniqua est - prætermissis bonis vitiorum s.; res s-e digna; virtutem rerum s-e spoliare, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĕgo</text:span>, lēgi, lectum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plocka upp, upphemta:</text:span></text:span> ficum; bacam (quæ decidit), Col.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smulor från bordet),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undansnappa:</text:span></text:span> liberos alicui, Pt.; carmina alicui [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förstulet uppsnappa</text:span> (auribus)], Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wälja i ngns ställe:</text:span></text:span> alqm in locum demortui, L.; in ordinem s-i, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Translĕgo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomläsa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēgo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lex?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förordna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn till något, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppdraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt åt ngn:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. obj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förordna, utnämna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till sändebud, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skicka ss. sändebud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. eller med offentligt uppdrag:</text:span> hominem suæ civitatis nobilem ad alqm l-re; l-ti ex senatus auctoritate l-antur; eum Cæsari l-arat Appius, C.; tres adolescentes in Africam l-antur, qui (regibus) senatus populique Romani verbis nuntient -, Sa.; ego sum publicus nuntius populi Rom.; juste pieque l-tus venio, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wanl. om fältherre l. provinshöfding) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utnämna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">antaga till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">legatus</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">underbefälhafware</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (adjutant) l. underhöfding:</text:span> Dolabella me sibi; Cæsar sibi Cassium, C.; Calpurnius sibi homines nobiles, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. obj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppdraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt åt ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">låta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> säga ngn ngt:</text:span> negotium alicui, Pt.; verba ad hostium ducem, Gell.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom testamente </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förordna, tillordna, testamentera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ngn:</text:span> alicui (testamento) alqd, C., Qu.; alicui alqd ab aliquo (a filio, a secundo herede) l-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(åt ngn från ngn l. på ngns post, räkning</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">att utgå från ngns del i arfwet, att utbetalas af honom),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillskrifwa:</text:span></text:span> fortunæ adversa, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sändebud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från en regering till en annan):</text:span> Athenienses ad senatum (Romanum) l-os de suis rebus maximis miserunt; l. sine mandatis; l. cum auctoritate <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bemyndigande, fullmakt);</text:span> l-os eligere, constituere, C.; l-os mittere ad alqm; l-i Allobrogum; l-os de injuriis questum mittere, Sa.; mittere l-os accusatum, exposcendi gratia, N.; ad res repetendas l-os mittere, L.; l-i responsa ferunt ab urbe Diomedis, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">generals l. provinshöfdings </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fullmäktig, adjutant,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">legat,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> underbefälhafware (för en legion l. flera):</text:span> Murena Lucullo l. fuit; l-os sibi legare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förordna, antaga);</text:span> Cæsari decem l-i decreti sunt a senatu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(detta antal, ej personerna),</text:span> C.; l. operam fiduciariam obtinet; l. pro prætore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med prætors myndighet),</text:span> Cs.; C. Antonius, quod proelio adesse nequibat, M. Petrejo l-o exercitum permittit, Sa.; obtinere locum l-i, N. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under kejsarne):</text:span> l. Cæsaris (consulari potestate) i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">höfding i en kejserlig provins (mots.</text:span> proconsul, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">höfding i en senatorisk provins),</text:span> T., Su., Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Testamentariskt förordnande, bestämmelse, disposition;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> testamenteradt gods:</text:span> Hortensii l-a cognovi, C.; l-a (Augusti) non ultra civilem modum (fuerunt), T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Testamentstagare:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beskickning, ambassade:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg., abstract mening:</text:span> obire, accipere, C.; l-em ad civitates suscepit; munus, officium l-is, Cs.; administrare, N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> libera l., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fri (sken -) beskickning</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillåtelse åt en senator att resa utom Italien utan offentligt uppdrag, men med namn och wärdighet af</text:span> legatus: l-e libera legatus; l-em liberam sumere, dare alicui voti causa, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beskickning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = de personer, s. skickas, sändebuden:</text:span> l-em mittere; l-i respondere, Cs.; l. venit ab Eumene, L. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppdrag, ärende,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarmed l. hwari ngn skickas, och resultatet af beskickningen:</text:span> l-em renunciare, C., L.; referre, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Legats-</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">adjutants-, underbefälhafwares, fullmäktigs befattning:</text:span></text:span> C., Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātīvum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sändebuds arwode:</text:span></text:span> Ulp.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Testator, testamentsgifware:</text:span></text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: provincia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som styres af</text:span> legatus Cæsaris, Lpd. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> legatus, c.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablēgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(befalla att gå bort), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortskicka, affärda, aflägsna, låta gå:</text:span></text:span> pueros venatum, L.; alqm aliquo, Ter.; consilium dimittere et a.; alqm a consilio removere et a., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortdrifwa:</text:span></text:span> foras alqm, Pt.; pecus a prato, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablēgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortskickning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (-commendering):</text:span> juventutis ad bellum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allēgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beordra till ngt, skicka i ngt ärende</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngn:</text:span> ad negotium alqm; villicum, Pt.; petit a me, amicos a-at, facile impetrat; nobiles homines iis a-at, qui petant; te ipso a-to et deprecatore (Fam. XV. 15. 2), C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anföra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. skäl, exempel), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">åberopa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig på -:</text:span> mandata regis sui, T.; dignitatem, Qu.; exemplum, Pn.; causam, Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allēgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sändning, beskickning, bud:</text:span></text:span> a-bus expugnare alqd, C. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anförande, påstående:</text:span></text:span> Ap., Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allēgātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sändning:</text:span></text:span> venire alicujus a-u, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlēgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skicka, wisa, lemna, skjuta bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ifrån sig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. om personer o. saker:</text:span> oves, Cato; alicui alqd faciendum, Pt.; alicui laborem, C. ep.; obsidionem in curam collegæ d., L.; agrorum cura feminis d-ta (principes Germanorum) ipsi hebent; nunc natus infans d-atur Græculæ alicui ancillæ, T.; curam, Qu.; officium, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hänskjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sak till annans behandling); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hänwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn till annat ställe l. person:</text:span> rem ad senatum, C.; studiosos Catonis ad aliud volumen d-amus, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hänwisa till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gifwa anwisning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngn för en fordrans utbekommande:</text:span> petebatur a me frumenti copia - d-vi amico locupletiori, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> spem fortunæ, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> skuld l. förtjenst från sig på ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillägga, tillskrifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt:</text:span> hæc ipsa, quæ ad me d-re vis, semper in te eximia et præstantia fuerunt; crimen optimis nominibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. erkänna den),</text:span> C.; causam peccati alicui, Cs.; scelera alicui, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlēgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anwisning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på annan person för en fordrans utbekommande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(wexel):</text:span></text:span> d. a mancipe annua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att betalas inom året),</text:span> C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> ea res non recipit d-em, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælēgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med förmonsrätt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">testamentera:</text:span></text:span> alicui centies sestertium, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlēgo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skicka undan, bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att wara gömd; jfr</text:span> reconditus, removeo); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">aflägsna, förwisa, bortwisa:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> <text:line-break/>1. med personl. obj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> alqm in prædia rustica; filium ab hominibus, C.; longe ab ceteris r-tos fame aut ferro interire, Cs.; tauros in pascua; Hippolytum Diana nemori, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Landsförwisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej till straffort):</text:span> r-tus mihi videor, postquam in Formiano sum, C.; in exsilium alqm, L.; in decem annos, T. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hänwisa:</text:span></text:span> ad auctores, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. obj.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wisa ifrån sig; sky, undfly:</text:span></text:span> dona, C. ap. Non.; ambitionem, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skjuta, kasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skuld) på ngn:</text:span> culpam in alqm, Qu. - invidiam rei in alqm, Vell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlēgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwisning, landsförwisning:</text:span></text:span> C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēgŭlejus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmodl. af</text:span> lex): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">pedantisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagkarl, lagwrängare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> paragraphryttare:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Legulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕgo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕgūmen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skidfrukt, baljfrukt:</text:span></text:span> terra freta frugibus et vario l-um genere, C.; Vg., cicer est l., Val. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕgūmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: id.: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leiostrĕa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ostron med glatt skal:</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕlex, ĕgis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: - <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> -lĕges, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslagsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĕlĕgēis, eĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Lĕlĕgēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ögonwar:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕmannus <text:line-break/>(Lĕmānus), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Geneversjön.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lembus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Julle, båt:</text:span></text:span> Vg., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemma,</text:span> ătis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Thema, sats, ämne,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. för ett epigramm, deraf </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">epigrammet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sjelf:</text:span> Pn., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemniscus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Band,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. hänger ned från en krans:</text:span> coronæ l-ique, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lemniscātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">prydd med -:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>emnos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lemnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lemnĭus (C.), <text:line-break/>Lemnĭăcus (St.), <text:line-break/>Lemnĭensis (Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lemnĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patron.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lemnĭcŏla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lemnier.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>emonia tribus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i Rom.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕmŏvīces, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folkslag.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>emovii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germaniskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕmŭres,</text:span> um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T1">sing.</text:span> Ap.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">De dödes andar; spöken, gastar:</text:span></text:span> l. animæ silentum, Ov.; nocturnos l-es videre, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕmŭria</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n. pl.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de dödes festdag:</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopplerska:</text:span></text:span> callida, Tib. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> blanda conciliatrix et quasi sui l. natura, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēno</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopplare, skök-wärd:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; perjurissimus, impurissimus, C.; insidiosus, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Underhandlare:</text:span></text:span> Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnōcĭnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopplareyrke, koppleri; kopplarelön:</text:span></text:span> facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(drifwa),</text:span> Pt.; profiteri, Su.; - l. petere ab aliquo, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: medel att locka, winna: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lockelse, smicker; fagert, wänligt tal; wackra ord:</text:span></text:span> cupiditatum l-is se dedere, C.; l-is existimationem colligere; fraudem et l-a rei adhibere, Su.; Galba orationi (quam ad milites habebat) nullum l. addit aut precium, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Puts, prydnad, grannlåt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. är egnad att locka l. behaga), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">flärd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen i ord </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(ordprål):</text:span></text:span> corporum, C.; omnis l-i negligens et in capite comendo incuriosus (Augustus), Su.; caret l-is expositio, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnōcĭnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(koppla hos ngn) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Söka locka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ställa sig in</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krusa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngn:</text:span> mercede quasi l-ante; tibi serviet, tibi l-bitur, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(koppla, wara kopplare för ngn) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skaffa ynnest åt, gifwa behag åt, förhöja werkan, intrycket</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (effecten) af ngt:</text:span> novitas libro l-atur, Pn.; insitæ feritati ars et tempus (noctis) l-atur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnōnĭce</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På kopplares sätt:</text:span></text:span> Lpd. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnōnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. tillhör l. anstår kopplare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kopplare-:</text:span></text:span> fides, P<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">t.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnullus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnuncŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ēnæus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bacchisk, Bacchus.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lene, Lenim . . ., Lenio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lenis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēnis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg., sinlig mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för känseln l. i sina physiska werkningar </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Len, blid, mild, lindrig, lätt:</text:span></text:span> quid judicant sensus? dulce amarum, l-e asperum; auster; venenum, C.; vinum, Hor., Ter.; somnus, Hor.; auræ, Ov.; ventus, Vg., Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om rörelser) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sakta:</text:span></text:span> gressus, L.; fluvius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sakta flytande; stilla),</text:span> Vg., Ct. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om sluttningar) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt, lindrig, jemn:</text:span></text:span> clivus, L.; fastigium, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställningens gång l. ton: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jemn, lugn:</text:span></text:span> tractus orationis l. et æquabilis; sonus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> vehemens), C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinne, ord, tillstånd: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mild, saktmodig, blid, godmodig, beskedlig, god, lindrig:</text:span></text:span> animus, Ter.; l. et facilis a te existimari debeo, qui nihil tecum expostulem; homo naturā et disciplinā l-simus; populus Romanus in hostes quondam l-simus; virtutes l-ores; verbis l-simis uti, C.; sententia l-ior, Cs.; l-ior fis accedente senecta; l. dominus; l. Ilithyia; bellante prior, jacentem l. in hostem; non l. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ej låter sig beweka)</text:span> recludere fata Mercurius, Hor.; servitus l., Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēne</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sakta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> lätt:</text:span> sonans aqua, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnio</text:span>, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sakta sig:</text:span></text:span> iræ l-unt, Pt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med döda object: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lindra, stilla:</text:span></text:span> miseriam alicui, Ter.; dolorem, Hor., Ov.; incommoda; desiderium alicujus; ægritudinem, C.; inopiam frumenti; invidiam, Sa.; seditionem, iras, L.; curas; timorem, Vg.; iram, T.; l-ite (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tystnen med)</text:span> clamorem impium, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med lefwande object l. sådana, s. tänkas lefwande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lugna, mildra; blidka, (tämja, göra spak, genom godhet winna):</text:span></text:span> me (lugentem) scriptio et literæ non l-unt, sed obturbant, C.; l-it albescens animos capillus, Hor.; iratum l.; fratrem l., C.; alqm; ferocem animum, Sa.; invidiam obsequio, N.; dictis animum alicujus, Vg.; panis cum sale latrantem stomachum l-et; l. tigres rabidosque leones, Hor.; superos, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnīmen</text:span>, ĭnis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lindringsmedel,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, som förljufwar, förmildrar:</text:span> laborum, senectæ dulce l-n, Hor., Ov.; l-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af)</text:span> honestæ missionis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlēnio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīnio</text:span>, 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stilla, lugna, smeka:</text:span></text:span> dolorem, Phdr.; dolentem purpurarum usus non d-it <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwer ro åt),</text:span> Hor.; animos hominum, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjusa, locka, dåra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> lenio 2. b.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">winna, intaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för sig, till ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förföra, -leda:</text:span></text:span> plebem aliqua re; mulierem donis; genus hominum disertorum oratione d-tum - urbibus se sæpsit; animos prædā, pretio, sermone benigno, illecebris voluptatis; blanditiis voluptatum d-tus, C.; ita d-tus sum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tjusad, förtrollad),</text:span> ut, qui sim, nesciam, Pt.; popularium animos prædā d.; Campania instrumento omnium voluptatum d-tos animos avertit a memoria patriæ, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlēnĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjusande; förledande, -förande:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlēnīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjusningsmedel (trollkonster), förförelse, lockmedel, lockelse:</text:span></text:span> illius d-is et venenis imbutum nec parentis nec deorum verecundiam habere; illam furiam omnibus d-is animum suum avertisse (dicebat); imbuti et infecti Romanis d-is, L.; d. vitæ, vitiorum; d. exercitui Germanico <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medel att winna),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlēnītor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjusare:</text:span></text:span> judicis d. debet esse orator, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblēnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjusa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lugna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett upprördt sinne):</text:span> lectio carminum (iratum) o-iat, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lenhet, mildhet; jemnhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i rörelser:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> vocis, C.; vini; gustus, Pn.; flumen est Arar - incredibili l-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sakta, stilla lopp),</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om talets gång l. ton: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jemnhet, lugn, mildhet:</text:span></text:span> genus orationis - l-e æquabili profluens; gravissimi sermonis l., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om sinnelaget): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Saktmod, mildhet, godhet, beskedlighet:</text:span></text:span> revocare mentes ad l-em; non est jam l-i locus, severitatem res ipsa desiderat, C.; inepta, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mildt, lent, lindrigt, lätt, lugnt, stilla, sakta, makligt (långsamt):</text:span></text:span> presse et l. loqui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mjukt till sjelfwa uttalet);</text:span> l. arridere; sensim ac l. accedere; dicere; agere remisse et l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lugnt),</text:span> C.; collis l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lätt)</text:span> acclivis; l. agere, Sa.; agere, procedere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(långsamt),</text:span> Cs.; l. atterens caudam (canis); l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i godt mak)</text:span> purgare ungues; l. in spem arrepe officiosus; traducere l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stilla, i lugn)</text:span> ævum, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. (om sinnelaget och deß yttringar): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beskedligt, i godo, mildt:</text:span></text:span> petere l. bonis dictis, Pt.; l. sentire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(yttra sig, i senaten),</text:span> C.; agere in castigando, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēnĭtŭdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lenhet; godhet (efterlåtenhet):</text:span></text:span> l. orationis, mollitudo corporis, Pacuv.; nimia virorum (in Verrem) l., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Leno <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lena.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Lens,</text:span> lendis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gnet:</text:span></text:span> tollere, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Lens</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lentis, Prisc.), tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span> Non.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lins, ärt:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentĭcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Pall. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linsform,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> form af en l.:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">linsformigt kärl:</text:span> Ce.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fräken:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentĭcŭlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">linsformig:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentīgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linsformig fläck, fräken, (-nar):</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentīgĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fräknig,</text:span></text:span> os: Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lente, Lenteo, -tesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lentus. <text:line-break/>Lentic . . ., Lentig . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Lens.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lentiscus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentiscum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mastixträd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bit, sticka af mastixträd (ss. tandpetare):</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mastixolja:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentiscĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär mastix:</text:span> (terra), Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentiscīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: oleum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mastix-olja,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lentitia, -titudo, Lento, -tor, -tulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lentus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>entŭlus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Cornelia. <text:line-break/>Lentŭlĭtas, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en</text:span> Lentuli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höga) börd l. anor:</text:span> C. Ep. ad. Fam. III. 7. . </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lentus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> lenis?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Seg, trög:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Seg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smidig, böjlig, wek:</text:span></text:span> pix; gluten; vimen; salix; humor, Vg.; aurum, Ov.; l-is adhærens brachiis, Hor.; calamus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om massor = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trög, stillastående, orörlig:</text:span></text:span> marmor (= æquor), Vg.; pondus, Ppt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om rörelser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långsam, maklig:</text:span></text:span> gradus l., Pn., Val. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långsam, långdragen, trög, sen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. långsamt utwecklas l. werkar); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ihållig, enwis:</text:span></text:span> negotium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(affär);</text:span> principia (orationis); nomen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skuld, s. trögt inflyter),</text:span> C.; duellum; ignes, Hor.; pugna l-ior fit, L.; remedia, Ct.; amor, Ov.; vivacitas, Pn. <text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Matt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om färger:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Seg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">trög, senfärdig, maklig, lugn, saktmodig, trygg, kallblodig, phlegmatisk:</text:span></text:span> infitiatores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tredskare),</text:span> C.; tu, Tityre, l. in umbra - resonare doces Amaryllida silvas, Vg.; nihil illo l-ius (de eo, qui non movetur contumeliis); judex l. et consideratus; genus ridiculi patientis et l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(torrt),</text:span> C.; l-um spectare hostem tendentem ad moenia, L.; amara l-o temperat risu, Hor.; l. in ira, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lente</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böjligt, eftergifwet:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långsamt, trögt:</text:span></text:span> procedere; subsequi, Cs.; gradi, Ov.; nasci, Pn.; agere, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lugnt, kallt; utan ifwer, wärme, hetta; saktmodigt:</text:span></text:span> l. ferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(taga kallt)</text:span> injurias; disputare; respondere; l. probare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pröfwa)</text:span> alqd <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kallblodigt, lugnt),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lenteo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara långsam, gå trögt:</text:span></text:span> opus, Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentesco</text:span>, ĕre:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa seg, smidig, mjuk:</text:span></text:span> pix, Vg.; salix, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mattas, taga af:</text:span></text:span> curæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlentesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter kallna:</text:span></text:span> amor, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Lentĭtes, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Lucil.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Seghet, böjlighet:</text:span></text:span> pituitæ; virgæ, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långsamhet, senfärdighet:</text:span></text:span> hominis, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tröghet, känslolöshet, brist på lif</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">intresse, likgiltighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (phlegma):</text:span> lenitatem - vitioso l-is nomine appellant; non irasci - non solum est gravitatis, sed nonnumquam etiam l-is, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lento</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Böja:</text:span></text:span> remus in Trinacria unda l-dus est, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Seghet; seg wätska:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lentŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något trög, sen:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lenullus, I. Lenunculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lena.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēnuncŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Litet fartyg, båt:</text:span></text:span> Cs., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leo,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lejon:</text:span></text:span> validus, Lucr.; acerrimus, N.; asper; flavus; Gætulus, Hor.; fulvus, Vg.; ferus, Ov.; l. fremit, Sen. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lejonet ss. stjernbild:</text:span> Hor., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lea</text:span>, ae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(poet.) och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leæna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lejoninna:</text:span></text:span> sæva lea, Ov.; torva l-na, Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leōnīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lejon-:</text:span></text:span> pellis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕōcŏrĭon, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tempel i Athen.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕon, ontis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕōnĭdas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕonnātus i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiska personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕontīni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Sicilien och deß inwånare.</text:span><text:line-break/>Lĕontīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕŏpardus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leopard:</text:span></text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕōty̆chĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕpas</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lopas), ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mußla:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕpĭdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl. om personer, deras utseende och sätt o. s. w.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nätt, täck, treflig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (älsklig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wacker, sirlig:</text:span></text:span> forma; cantio; senex; mores; fama; dies, Pt.; caput, Ter.; puer l. et delicatus, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning och enskilda uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fin, sirlig:</text:span></text:span> ea, quæ l-a et concinna sunt, cito fastidio afficiunt aures, C.; l-o dicto seponere inurbanum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(groft, platt),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕpĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nätt, täckt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lustigt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fint, sirligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (qwickt):</text:span> l. ornatus; l. ludificatus; l. efficere alqd; memorare, Pt.; euge, euge l., Ter.; l. lexeis compostæ, Lucil.; l. ludere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĕpĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otreflig, grof; utan behag; smaklös:</text:span></text:span> parens i., in liberos difficilis, C.; deliciæ, Catl.; dictum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĕpĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Groft, smaklöst, dumt:</text:span></text:span> lepidam i. vocare, Pt.; crasse i-eve compositum, Hor.; anima sui pro sale data non i-e existimatur, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĕpĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ganska nätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fint:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕpos</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕpor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Täckhet, behag, finhet, treflighet, smak</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= smakfullt sätt):</text:span> ridens pavonis; (veris), Lucr.; nativus hominis, N.; homo affluens venustate et l-e, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Finhet, smak, behag,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tal och infall; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">qwickhet, humor:</text:span></text:span> tantus (Crassi) l. in jocando fuit (ut tristitia sermonis tolleretur); admirabilis l. dicendi; l. quidam facetiæque et eruditio libero digna; omnes verborum et sententiarum l-es; oratorius, non scurrilis lepos; L. Cæsar inusitatum nostris oratoribus l-em et salem est consecutus, C.; facetus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕpĭdus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Aemilia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕpis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fjäll:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕpista,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skål:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĕpontii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i cisalpinska Gallien.</text:span><text:line-break/>Lĕpontĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lepor, Lepos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lepidus.<text:line-break/>Leporarium, -porinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lepus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕpræ,</text:span> ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hudsjukdom, spetälska:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eptīnes, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eptis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afric. stadsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Leptĭcus, <text:line-break/>Leptīnus, <text:line-break/>Leptītānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕpus,</text:span> ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hare:</text:span></text:span> auritus l.; canibus venari l-em, Vg.; fecundus; pavidum l-em captare, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Haren ss. stjernbild:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕpŏrārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hargård; inhägnad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> der harar hållas:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕpŏrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af hare, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Har -:</text:span></text:span> lac, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕpuscŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>erna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">träsk wid Argos:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Lernæus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: hydra, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>esbos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lesbus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö i ægeiska hafwet.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lesbĭus, <text:line-break/>Lesbĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Lesbis, bĭdis, <text:line-break/>Lesbias, ĭădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lesbisk qwinna.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lesbōus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lessum,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klagogråt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer afliden:</text:span> facere, Pt., funeris ergo l. habere, C. de Legg. II. 13.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Letal . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Letum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēthargus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sömnsjuka:</text:span></text:span> Hor., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēthargĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: id.: Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēthargĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sömnsjuk:</text:span></text:span> Hor., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ēthē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(glömska): flod i underjorden:</text:span> (ad L-en mortui) longa oblivia potant, Vg. <text:line-break/>Lēthæus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Letifer, Leto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Letum.<text:line-break/>Letōis, Letōius = Lat . . ., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lētum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Död:</text:span></text:span> l-o malo emori; l-um consciscere, Pt.; l-o dari, C., Varr.; eodem l-o interire, perire, C.; l-i potiri, Lucr.; l-o affici, N.; l-o se eripere, Vg.; l-o adimere alqm, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttr.:</text:span> vide, quam turpi pereamus l-o (de interitu reip.), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lētālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dödlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= dödande):</text:span> hæret lateri l. arundo; vulnus l-e, Vg.; inedia, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lētāle</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lētālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dödligt:</text:span></text:span> Pn., St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lētĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dödsbringande, dödlig:</text:span></text:span> annus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pestår),</text:span> Vg.; ictus, Ov.; morbus, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Döda:</text:span></text:span> insignis ad deformitatem puer l-tus, C. (inc. l.); hunc ille l-at, Vg.; l-tus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>evăci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Levam . . ., Levat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Levo. Lĕvis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leuca</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leuga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gallisk mil (fr. lieue)</text:span> = 1500 passus: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leucăcantha,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwit törnebuske:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leucanthĕmum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en blomma (prestkrage):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucădĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wid grekiska kusten af Ioniska hafwet.</text:span><text:line-break/>Leucădĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Leucāta, ae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Leucātē, ēs, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Leucātes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landtudde på ön Leucas.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leucaspis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f. A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rustad med hwita sköldar:</text:span> phalanx (Macedonum), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>euci, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">belgiskt folk.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucippus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Leucippē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Leucippis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leucŏcŏmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har hwita (hår) blommor:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leucŏĭon</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leucŏĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwit viol</text:span> (ἴον), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">levkoja:</text:span> Col., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett galliskt folkslagsnamn:</text:span> lana, Pn.<text:line-break/>Leucŏnĭcum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">leuconisk ull:</text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏnŏē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏpĕtra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">udde i Bruttium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leucŏphæus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ask-färgad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Leucŏphæātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gråklädd:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏphry̆na, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">binamn för Diana.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏsĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ö wid Italiens kust.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏsy̆ri, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i mindre Asien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏthĕa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>eucŏthŏē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>euctra, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Boeotien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Leuctrĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕvenna</text:span> pro levi (<text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>) Laberius dixit, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Leuga <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Leuca.<text:line-break/>Leviculus, -vidensis, -vifidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕvis.<text:line-break/>Levigatio, -vigo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævis.<text:line-break/>Levipes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕvis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lēvir,</text:span> (ĭri), <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mans broder, swåger:</text:span> Fs., Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lēvis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĕvis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots. tung,</text:span> gravis):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att bära l. s. kännes lätt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i rörelser, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lättrustad):</text:span> armatura C., Cs.; pondus; piper, Pn.; terra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lätt</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mager),</text:span> Vg.; malvæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lättsmält),</text:span> Hor.; vinum, Pn.; - cursu l., Vg.; milites ad motus l-ores, N.; mus l. exsilit, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ljud:</text:span> susurri l-es, Vg., Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att draga l. utstå; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lindrig, mild:</text:span></text:span> noxa, Ter.; dolor, periculum; reprehensio, C.; periculum; proelium, Cs., L.; discrimen, Ct.; l. et tenuis motus animi, Sen.; imperium, Sa.; eo, quod l-simum videbatur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(den lindrigaste utwägen),</text:span> decursum est, L.; cura non l., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">föga wigtig, owigtig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. föga gäller l. får gälla, aktas: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">simpel, obetydlig, ringa, föraktlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> gravis = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wigtig, maktpåliggande, aktad, aktningswärd):</text:span> causa, C., Cs.; artes l-ores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej practiskt wigtiga);</text:span> l-e nomen habet utraque res: quippe, l-e enim est hoc totum risum movere; inania quædam et l-ia conquirere, quæ reprehendat; nomen imperii etiam in l-i persona grave; huic pecunia semper l-sima fuit, C.; meritum, Cs.; sententia, Ter.; haud l. auctor, L.; necessitudo, Sa.; nomen; fama, Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinne l. lynne, i mildare bet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flygtig, ostadig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i strängare: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lättsinnig, characterslös, samwetslös, utan heder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">grundsatser; simpel, usel, dålig:</text:span></text:span> mitte l-es spes; l. juventus; urimur non præter solitum l-es, Hor.; homo l. et fallax; judex l. et nummarius, C.; quid l-ius quam auctore hoste de summis rebus capere consilium?, Cs.; l-sima fidei mutandæ ingenia, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭcŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obetydlig; något fåfäng:</text:span></text:span> res, Gell.; homo, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭdensis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: (densus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gles, (grof)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i wäfnaden; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">grof, simpel:</text:span></text:span> l. i. e. leviter densata vestis, Isid.; munus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭfĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: (fides): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trolös:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭpes</text:span>, ĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättfotad:</text:span></text:span> lepus, Varr., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭsomnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. sofwer lätt:</text:span> canis, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätthet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> armorum, Cs.; naturalis l. agit naves; teli vis est in l-e, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löslighet, ytlighet; barnslighet, narraktighet:</text:span></text:span> l. opinionum; l. temere assentientium; hæc plena sunt summæ l-is et creduntur stultissime, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättsinne, löshet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i grundsatser och seder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">swaghet; hållnings-, charakterslöshet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-swaghet, brist på stadga; pojkaktighet; brist på grundsatser; samwetslöshet, wingleri:</text:span></text:span> amatoriæ l-es; ut adversas res, sic secundas immoderate ferre l-is est; inconstantia, mobilitas, l.; judiciorum l.; perpetua in populari ratione l., C.; jactatio et l., L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt, (litet):</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om bördor, ljud m. m.:</text:span> armatus, Ct.; strepere, Sa.; genæ l. eminentes, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. l. ferre alqd: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med tålamod; med likgiltighet:</text:span></text:span> dolorem, C.; injurias (alienas), L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lösligt, ytligt, obetydligt, föga:</text:span></text:span> eruditus; l. tangere, l. attingere alqd, C.; Ennius l. curare videtur, quo - cadant - somnia Pythagorēa, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ej hårdt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tungt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">strängt; lindrigt:</text:span></text:span> saucius; ægrotare; lippire; succensere alicui; inter se dissidere; dicere l-sime, C.; l-ius miser, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinl. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra lätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lättare; skaffa lättnad (befria):</text:span></text:span> alqm onere, vinculis, C.; sarcinis jumenta, Sa.; fasce alqm, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyfta, höja, stödja:</text:span></text:span> naves tridenti; se cubito; corpus, Vg.; nebula in nubes l-ta, L.; multa Dircæum l-at aura cygnum, Hor.; manum, Qu.; aves l-ant se pennis; mare l-atur, Ct.; in sublime se l., Pn.; equus alqm dorso, Phdr.; manu alqm, Sa.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyfta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lossa, taga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af:</text:span> manicas et arta vincula l. alicui, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt, l. mödan, smärtan af ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lindra, mildra:</text:span></text:span> curam, Enn.; paupertatem, morbum alicui, Pt.; cruciatum, dolorem, metum alicui; luctum, angorem alicujus sermone; laborem, C.; laborem; sermone viam; omen, Vg.; inopiam publicam opibus, N.; annonam, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bereda lättnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lindring; befria</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">understödja, lisa, hugna, wederqwicka:</text:span></text:span> miseriis civitates; ægritudine alqm; se infamiā; infamiā, vitiis, erroribus l-ri; ære alieno, supplicio, exsilio alqm; me literæ tuæ nonnihil l-ant; animi exercitatione l-antur (corpora ingravescunt), C.; hibernis (<text:span text:style-name="T1">abl. instr.</text:span>) milites, Cs.; aliquem obsidione <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från b.);</text:span> aliquem auxilio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med hjelp),</text:span> Vg.; Apollo salutari arte l-at artus fessos, Hor.; a poena alqm, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förminska, förringa, -klena, -mildra:</text:span></text:span> sumptum, Ter.; <text:soft-page-break/>inconstantiā l-atur auctoritas; laudem alicujus l.; rei atrocitatem l., C.; multa fidem promissa l-ant, Hor.; fenus; facinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(söka mildra</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ursäkta),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättnad, lindringsmedel, hjelp, tröst:</text:span></text:span> in te uno est l-men; miseriarum l-tum; ea res tibi est l-o, C.; curæ l-n, Vg.; (fili) meum post fata l-n, Ppt.; tributi, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättande, lindring, förmildring; -minskning:</text:span></text:span> id est ei magnæ l-i; l. ægritudinum; reperire l-em malis; exspectare nullam l-em ab aliquo; vitiorum l. C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĕvātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tjuf:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĕvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. men.:</text:span> onus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyfta upp, hjelpa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> upp:</text:span> laqueis a-tum ascendere, Sa.; scutis a-ti, Cs.; manu alqm a., Ct.; supercilia, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lindra, lisa, skaffa lisa, upprätta; mildra:</text:span></text:span> ærumnam dictis; sollicitudines; corpus a-tum, C.; notas (censorum) a-re, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĕvāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lisa, upprättelse:</text:span></text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĕvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lindring, lättnad:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlĕvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upplyfta:</text:span></text:span> contignationem et storeas, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätta, lindra:</text:span></text:span> sollicitudines; ægritudinem, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förringa, nedsätta, förswaga, förminska,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i werkligheten l. i andras ögon, wigten l. wärdet af en sak:</text:span> causas offensionum tum evitare, tum e., tum ferre sapientis est; quod est ab aliquo objectum, lepore e. magis quam contentione frangere; risus adversarium impedit, e-at, deterret, C.; auctoritatem, famam alicujus, L.; testimonia, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlĕvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förringande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i rhetor., mots.</text:span> amplificatio): Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĕvis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket lätt, obetydlig, ringa:</text:span></text:span> momentum, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĕvĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: commotus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĕvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter upplyfta:</text:span></text:span> corpus e terra, Ov.; caput, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sakl. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förmildra, lindra, stilla:</text:span></text:span> epistolam aliqua re; satietas aut fastidium r-atur, C.; sitim; famem, Ov.; laborem, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med lefwande obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätta, befria</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lisa, bereda lisa; wederqwicka:</text:span></text:span> animum alicujus, Ter.; metu, curā, molestiis r-ri; æger r-atur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(får lisa, förbättras);</text:span> respublica r-atur, C.; membra sedili, Ov. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlossa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om barnaföderskor):</text:span> Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĕvātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lättande, -nad:</text:span></text:span> oneris: Fronto.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĕvo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyfta upp, hålla uppe:</text:span></text:span> alqm sibi ad pedes stratum s-re, C.; se erigere et s., Cs.; terrā alqm, Vg. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Underlätta, lätta, förmildra:</text:span></text:span> laborem, calamitatem, res adversas alicujus; pericula; offensionem, C.; inopiam alicujus, Cs.; metum, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Understödja, hjelpa:</text:span></text:span> miseros; alqm suo auxilio; causam alicujus, <text:soft-page-break/>C.; Cæsar queritur, quod non ab Hæduis s-etur; alqm re frumentaria s., Cs.; patriam, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĕvātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Understöd:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Levisomnus, Lĕvitas, -viter, Lĕvo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĕvis.<text:line-break/>Lēvitas, Lēvo, Lēvor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lævis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lex,</text:span> lēgis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lag:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. antagande, bestämmande (wal), af</text:span> lego: l-em Græco no - mine putant a suum cuique tribuendo (νέμειν) appellatam, ego nostro a legendo; ut illi æquitatis, sic nos delectus vim in lege ponimus, C.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i politisk men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lag,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl ss. föreslagen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(lagförslag, motion</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till folkförsaml.), som ss. antagen och gällande:</text:span> l. Manilia de imperio Pompeji, C.; l-em scribere, condere, componere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppsätta);</text:span> l-em ferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(föreslå),</text:span> promulgare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offentliggöra, anslå);</text:span> rogare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bringa till omröstning hos folket);</text:span> l-em perferre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få antagen, om motionären);</text:span> l-em jubere, sancire, statuere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(antaga),</text:span> repudiare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förkasta);</text:span> l. est accepta; l-em abrogare, tollere, delere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upphäfwa);</text:span> l-em irritam facere; l-em servare, observare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(iakttaga, hålla);</text:span> l-i obtemperare; l-em negligere, violare, perrumpere; a lege discedere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bryta);</text:span> l-e adstringi, teneri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förpligtas, wara bunden af);</text:span> poenis l-um et judiciorum implicari; l. mollior, durior; annalis, frumentaria; l. Tullia, Porcia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. s. w. (efter motionären);</text:span> l-e agere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lagföra, anställa käromål);</text:span> l-um æra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(koppartaflor),</text:span> C.; l-e experiri, agere cum aliquo, N.; l-e agere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl. lag förfara</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afstraffa),</text:span> L.; l-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af folket stiftade)</text:span> et senatus consulta; l-es et jus prætorium, C.; l-bus licet, conceditur, præfinitum est, N.; l-e cautum est, Pn.; viris l-es dare, Vg.; sine l-e rectum colere, Ov.; sanctarum inscitia l-um, Hor.; corruptissima republica plurimæ leges, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i privaträtten: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Formel, formulär</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ett aftal:</text:span> l. Maniliana venalium vendendorum; l. mancipii (formula venditionis), C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gudomlig, naturlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lag,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i den sedliga l. yttre werlden:</text:span> l. naturalis, divina; l. est naturæ vis - juris atque injuriæ regula; l. est recta et a numine deorum tracta ratio; l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sjelfförswarets)</text:span> non scripta, sed nata - quam ex ipsa natura arripuimus, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lag, regel, form,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarefter ngt göres, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ordning, bestämning:</text:span></text:span> ad hanc l-em formetur oratio; certa l. est in versibus; aliæ in historia l-es observandæ, aliæ in poēmate, C.; numeri l-e soluti; operis (i. e. carminis) l., Hor.; capilli sine l-e sparsi, Ov. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wilkor, öfwerenskommelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (accord); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bestämmelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för hwilken ngt kommer till l. göres; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ställning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwari ngn i följd deraf befinner sig:</text:span> l. censoria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af censorerne bestämdt för en entreprenör);</text:span> hac l-e astringo tibi fidem, C.; pax data Philippo in has l-es est, L.; homines ea l-e nati sumus, ut omnibus telis fortunæ proposita sit vita nostra; ea l-e natus es, ut communis utilitas tua sit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laglig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = s. grundar sig l. har afseende på (positiv) lag:</text:span> quæstio, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagstiftande:</text:span></text:span> Ceres (θεσμοφόρος), Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgĭrŭpa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgĭrŭpio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (rumpo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagbrytare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgislātor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgumlātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagstiftare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. skrifwes hwarje ord för sig):</text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgĭtĭmus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Laglig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagenlig; lag likmätig; lag-gill, i lag bestämd, wederbörlig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. mening:</text:span> jus; potestas; imperium; locus contionis; dies l-us comitiis habendis; numerus; hostis, C.; regnum justum et l-um; ætas l-a ad petendum magistratum, L.; uxor, Mt.; verbis l-is festum indicere, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wederbörlig, riktig; ordinär (stående):</text:span></text:span> (qui) l-um studet fecisse poēma; l-umque sonum (numeri) digito callemus et aure, Hor.; pugiles l-i et ordinarii, Su.; quum ad me venisset, primo illa, quæ erant quotidiana et quasi l-a, inter nos (collocuti sumus), C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har afseende på lag, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lag-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> juridisk:</text:span> controversia, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgĭtĭma</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">laga former l. förhandlingar:</text:span> N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lēgĭtĭme</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lagligt, lagenligt; egentligen:</text:span></text:span> juste et l. imperare, C.; is, qui l. procurator dicitur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Exlex</text:span>, lēgis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri från lagens band; ej bunden af lag:</text:span></text:span> Sulla, C.; e-em esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> legibus teneri), L.; potus et e., Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(Lexĭcon, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordbok).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lexis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ord:</text:span></text:span> Luc., Gramm. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lat.</text:span> dictio, verbum).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lexĭdĭon</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>exovii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Libam . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭbănus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Syrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Libarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libum.<text:line-break/>Libatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libo. <text:line-break/>Libella <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libra.<text:line-break/>Libellio -bellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĭber.<text:line-break/>Libens, Libent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līber,</text:span> ĕra, ĕrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och relativt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">oberoende:</text:span></text:span> terra l-a a prædonibus; l. ab observando homine; l. a sumptu, munere, molestia; l. a delictis; animus terrore, cura l., C.; vir l. metu, Cs.; l. a spe, metu, partibus reipublicæ, Sa.; l. jure belli, intactus inviolatusque; l. religione animus, L.; l. laborum, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer och hwad dem tillhör:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mots. slaf l. fånge:</text:span> qui matre est l-ā, l. est; l. jure Quiritium; servus censu, vindictā, testamento l. fit; genus jocandi ne l-o quidem dignum, C.; corpus l-um, Sa.; l. et ingenuus, census equestrem summam numorum, Hor.; sine discrimine, l. an servus esset, L.; l-a custodia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fri arrest),</text:span> Sa. <text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">politiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> så wäl i det inre som i det yttre = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sjelfständig, oberoende:</text:span></text:span> in omni l-o et pacato populo eloquentia dominatur; qui in l-a civitate se ita instruunt, ut metuantur, iis nihil potest esse dementius; l-a respublica, C.; l-i jam hinc (post reges ejectos) populi Rom. res peragam; si salvam esse velit (Porsenna) Romam, l-am esse patiatur, L.; civitas, N.; civitas l-a et immunis; urbs l-a et pro eximiis suis beneficiis a senatu et a populo Rom. liberata, C.; civitas non modo l-a, sed etiam gentibus imperans, L.; Galliam l-am esse et suis legibus uti senatus voluit, Cs.<text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till sinne, tänkesätt, ord, beteende </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sjelfständig, frisinnad; frimodig, -språkig; obunden, oförbehållsam, oförställd;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i lefwernet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fri, lös; fördomsfri, opartisk;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i philosophisk mening: sedligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fri:</text:span></text:span> hoc l-ores sumus, quod integra nobis est judicandi potestas, C.; sententia; intercessio, Cs.; animus in consulendo l., Sa.; l-a posui vestigia, non aliena meo pressi pede, Hor.; lingua, Pt.; literæ, C.; vox, L.; l-um fastidium, C.; l-rima indignatio, Hor.; dolor, T.; adolescentia l-or, C.; l-a vina, Hor.; animo l-o causam alicujus defendere; præter sapientem l. nemo est, C.; quisnam igitur l.? sapiens, sibi qui imperiosus est, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej upptagen; ledig; fri, öppen, oinskränkt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i yttre och inre men.:</text:span> cælum; pars quæstionum vaga et l-a et late patens, C.; campus, L.; lectulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ungkarls-);</text:span> l-a legatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utan offentligt uppdrag),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = det, hwartill l. hwari ngn har frihet, kan fritt förfoga öfwer, s. står honom fritt:</text:span> uni tibi vexatio sociorum impunita fuit ac l-a; prisca verba poētarum licentiæ l-ora sunt, quam nostræ; l-um tempus, C.; l-um arbitrium mortis, T.; l-a (si) dentur populo suffragia, Juv.<text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om jord l. egendom i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från skatt l. tunga, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skattfri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ograverad):</text:span> agros l-os et immunes arare; nihil rei meæ familiaris l-um est, C. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕri</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Barn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i förhållande till föräldrarne, d. w. s. någons barn, ej i allm. personer af barnaåldren):</text:span> l-is dare operam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afla);</text:span> suscipere, tollere l-os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. upptaga</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">erkänna och upptaga ss. sina b.);</text:span> procreare l-os; habere l-os ex aliqua; habere aliquos in loco l-orum; alicui suos l-os committere, C.; viro, l-is fortunata; l-os quam optimos velle, Sa.; l-os suos obsides dare, Cs.; esse in societate liberûm, quo nihil carius humano generi est; Sabinorum omnis multitudo cum conjugibus et l-is venit, L.; dulces l., Hor (<text:span text:style-name="T1">sing.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bet. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">barn,</text:span></text:span> Js.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>īber, ĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ībĕra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Liber, Libera,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> italiska gudomligheter, identificerade med</text:span> Dionysus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. winets och festglädjens, och</text:span> Proserpina, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom den fruktbärande jordens eller jordalstrens gudomligheter:</text:span> L-um endo cælo merita locaverunt (de Legg. II. §. 19); rapta est L-a, quam eandem Proserpinam vocant, in Sicilia ex Hennensium nemore (in Verr. IV. 106), C.; L. et alma Ceres, Vg. Georg. I. in.; L. pater; jocosus L., Hor.<text:line-break/>2. Ov. Fast. III. 512 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är</text:span> Libera = Ariadne, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Libers</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> maka.</text:span><text:line-break/>Lībĕrălia, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">festdag i romerske calendren (</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Libers</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fest), på hwilken ynglingar anlade</text:span> toga virilis: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som rörer en fri l. frihet:</text:span> causa l., Ter., C.; judicium, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. anstår l. är wärdig en fri menniska:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ädel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så till utseende, s. inre beskaffenhet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ärbar, anständig, hygglig, hederlig:</text:span></text:span> facies; conjugium; ingenium, Ter.; homo pulcher et l., Pt.; adultam virginem domi teneamus sæptam l-i custodia; ea, quæ pertinent ad l-em speciem et dignitatem, moderata sint; quæstus l-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> sordidi); artes; doctrina; homo, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.: hedersam (honnett), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frikostig, rund, rundlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om personer och saker):</text:span> duo sunt genera largorum, quorum alteri prodigi, alteri l-es; homo l-simus et munificentissimus; operā i. e. virtute et industria l-em esse; viaticum; sumptus l., C.; l. ex sociorum fortunis; laudis avidus, pecuniæ l., Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕrālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: sinnelag, beteende, sätt, s. anstår en fri man: (liberalitet) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Humanitet, ädelhet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hygglighet, artighet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">godmodighet:</text:span></text:span> liberos retinere l-e, Ter.; homo non l-e, sed ipsa tristitia et severitate popularis; l-e sua (non suspicantis alios improbos esse) decipi; opes vel ingenii vel fortunæ l-i magis conveniunt, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frikostighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (liberalitet):</text:span> l. in sorores; l-is ratio duplex est: nam aut operā benigne fit indigentibus aut pecuniā; in tali l-e cupiditas rapiendi et auferendi inest, C.; magna apud plebem propter l-em gratia, Cs., Sa.; devincire alqm l-e; tanta fuit l-e, ut -; Attici nec temporaria fuit l. neque callida, N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">concret = skänk:</text:span> decima pars l-is, T.; una aut altera l-e locupletare alqm, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕrālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så som det anstår en fri:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ädelt, hyggligt, hederligt, humant:</text:span></text:span> servire alicui, Ter.; sine amicitia vitam esse nullam (putant omnes homines), si modo velint aliqua ex parte l. vivere; homo ingenuus et l. educatus; l. eruditus, C.; respondit pacem petentibus l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wänligt),</text:span> Cs.; l. genitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af anständig, hederlig härkomst),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frikostigt, rundt, rikligt:</text:span></text:span> l. vivere; l. tractare alqm ex cibariis; large et l., C.; Sulla milites luxuriose et nimis l. habuit, Sa.; sibi indulgere; polliceri, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illībĕrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. ej anstår en fri man: (trälaktig), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oädel, oanständig, simpel, låg; ej förekommande; oartig:</text:span></text:span> facinus; servus non i., Ter.; labor; quæstus; genus jocandi; jocus, C.; cibus, Pn.; in alqm, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illībĕrālĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">simpelt beteende; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Njugghet, knussel:</text:span></text:span> avaritiæ i-isque absit suspicio, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illībĕrālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett sätt, s. ej anstår en fri man: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oädelt, simpelt, oartigt; kargt, knussligt:</text:span></text:span> aspernari aliquam i., Ter.; a patre non i. institutus, C.; (ædes meas) æstimaverunt valde i., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlībĕrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket hygglig:</text:span></text:span> uxor, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlībĕrālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket ädelt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (liberalt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">frikostigt:</text:span></text:span> agere cum aliquo, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fritt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> moveri; ingredi; respirare, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinnelag, ord, lefnadssätt, beteende: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fritt; öppet, oförbehållsamt; utan betänklighet; fritaligt; fritt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">löst, utswäfwande:</text:span></text:span> decernere, Cs.; dare consilium; monere, dicere; loqui asperius et l-ius, C.; l-me profiteri, N.; educari; vivere, Ter.; vivere, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frigöra, befria, lösgöra:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och relativt:</text:span> lingua (inhærens) - scalpello resecta l-atur; alqm ære alieno, curā, culpā, odio, mortis metu; hunc ego a Cæsare l-vi; a calumniis l. alqm, C.; patriam a tyranno; urbem obsidione, ab incendio, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Försätta i frihet, frigifwa; fridöma, frikänna:</text:span></text:span> serviit et se l-vit, C.; servos l-re, Cs.; judex crimine alqm; Milo l-atur non eo consilio profectus esse, (ut Clodium interficeret), C.; l-tus discessit, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer och saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Befria</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från wissa (præstationer) förbindelser till det allmänna:</text:span> vectigales ac stipendiarios l. (= immunes facere); agros, C.; Asiæ portus, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upphäfwa; förklara ogiltig:</text:span></text:span> obsidionem, L.; promissa jure prætoris l-antur, C.<text:line-break/>d. locus l-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i augursspråket) = s. har fri utsigt:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Passera, öfwerfara:</text:span></text:span> flumen, Petr., Hyg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Befrielse; frikännande:</text:span></text:span> molestiæ; culpæ, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībĕrātor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Befriare:</text:span></text:span> patriæ l-es (Brutus et Cassius), C.; urbis, L.; patriæ, N.; Jupiter l., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībertas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och relativt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till l. i ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">oberoende:</text:span></text:span> l. est potestas vivendi, ut velis; l-e frui, cujus proprium est sic vivere, ut velis; tenere omnium rerum l-em; vivendi l-em habere, sibi præcidere, C.; vitæ l.; l-i studere, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. och absolut:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mots. träldom l. fångenskap:</text:span> servum l-e donare, in l-em vindicare, C.; servos ad l-em vocare, Cs.; indici (conjuratorum) l. et civitas data; servos ad l-em Ap. Herdonius vocabat, L.; de l-e et corpore (aleā) contendere, T.; quorum virtuti belli fortuna pepercit, eorundem l-i parcere certum est, Enn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">politisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i det inre (mots.</text:span> dominatio, regnum) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. utåt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(sjelfständighet, oberoende):</text:span></text:span> plebi re, non verbis, danda l.; l-em tueri, recuperare, adimere, opprimere; civibus l-em eripere; a regum et optimatium dominatione in l-em rem populi vindicare, C.; aut serviendum est optimatibus aut per manus l. retinenda, Sa.; l-is immaturæ cupidine regi regnum extorquere; Brutus vindex et custos l-is; non in regno pop. Rom., sed in l-e est, L.; urbem Romam a principio reges habuere: l-em et consulatum Brutus instituit, T.; Romani Gallis l-em erepturi sunt, Cs.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tänkesätt, ord, handlingar, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sjelfständighet, frimodighet, -talighet:</text:span></text:span> (C. Memmii) l. ingenii et odium potentiæ nobilitatis, Sa.; olim res populi Romani memorabantur pari eloquentia et l-e, T.; l. (versuum Fescenninorum) recurrentes accepta per annos lusit amabiliter, Hor.; antiqua comoedia facundissimæ l-is, Qu. <text:line-break/>d. Libertas, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personificerad = frihetens gudinna:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībertus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līberta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (: liberatus = honestus: honoratus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frigifwen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (någons f., d. w. s. i förhållande till sin förre herre, ej i allm. till beteckning af ståndet):</text:span> feci, e servo ut esses l. mihi, Ter.; l. alicujus, C., Qu.; hunc l-a divisit medium, Hor.; clientes l-ique damnatorum - in spem <text:soft-page-break/>erecti; (apud Germanos) l-i non multum supra servos sunt, T. - l-a mea, Pt.; Acte l-a (Neronis), T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībertīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frigifwen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till ståndet, jfr</text:span> libertus), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till, består af frigifne:</text:span> homo, C.; mulier; ordo, L.; l-o patre natus, Hor.; genus l-um, T. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībertīnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībertīna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frigifwen (person):</text:span></text:span> Tib. Gracchus l-os in tribus urbanas transtulit, C.; l-a an ingenua?, Pt.; mundior l-us; classis secunda, l-arum dico, Hor. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Enl.</text:span> Gell. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">war</text:span> l-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i det äldre språket = son af en frigifwen).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collībertus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">frigifwen af samme herre (med-frigifwen):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭber,</text:span> bri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bast:</text:span></text:span> trunci obducuntur l-o, C.; aret in ulmo, Vg.; teneri arborum l-i, Ct.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skrift, skriftligt arbete:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bok</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = helt werk:</text:span> sunt innumerabiles de his rebus l-i; l-um de aliqua re scribere, conscribere, conficere; legere; volvere; pervolutare; edere; corrigere; l. Meno inscribitur, C.; vitas imperatorum in hoc l-o exponemus; l-um Græce conficere; facere de re, N.; vulgare; emittere, Qu.; hic meret æra l. Sosiis, hic et mare transit, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bok</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">del</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett werk:</text:span> voluptatem - concessuram arbitror convictam superiore l-o (de finibus bonorum) dignitati; septem accusationis (Verrinæ) l-i, C. <text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentliga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Urkunder,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. chrönikor, register, religions- l. ritualböcker o. d.:</text:span> l-i lintei; l-i magistratuum, L.; l-i Sibyllini, C.; pontificum l-i, annosa volumina vatum, Hor.; literarum allatarum et missarum l-i (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">officiella concept- l. brefböcker),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bref:</text:span></text:span> l-um gravem multis verbis conscripsit, N.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kejserligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rescript, förordning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbellus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten bok, småskrift</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (brochure):</text:span> illud scripsi in l-o, qui - excidit et pervenit in manus hominum; unus parvus de officio l., C.; sacer, L.; l. (sermonum); garrire l-os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om theaterstycken),</text:span> Hor.; famosi l-i, Su. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">boklåda,</text:span> Catl., Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anteckningsbok, conceptbok,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> anteckningar, concept:</text:span> memoriæ causa in l-um referre alqd, C.; mandatorum mihi l-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(promemoria)</text:span> Brutus dedit, C; memorialis l., Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">officiel </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrifwelse, handling,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oftast </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inlaga, ansökning beswärs- -klago-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">böneskrift;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> men äfwen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stämning, utslag, resolution:</text:span></text:span> ut Buthrotium agrum proscriptum vidimus, Atticus l-um composuit, (quem) ego darem Cæsari; in l-is laudationem decretam mittere, C.; supplicibus l-is lassare alqm, Mt.; l-um porrigere alicui, Su.; l-o citare alqm, Pt.; Sulcius - ambulat et Caprius - rauci male cumque l-is - magnus uterque timor latronibus, Hor.; Augustus in l-is signandis sphinge usus est, Su.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentligt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anslag, kungörelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om auctioner o. dyl.):</text:span> in locis celeberrimis l-os proponere; l-os dejicere; l-i gladiatorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(affischer),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbellio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">notarie:</text:span> Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bokhandlare:</text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. hör till, sysselsätter sig med böcker,) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bok-:</text:span></text:span> taberna <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(boklåda),</text:span> C.; scriptor l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afskrifware),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bok-afskrifware; renskrifware; skrifware</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (handsecreterare):</text:span> notæ (i. e. signa interpunctionis) l-orum, C.; mendum l-i, L.; judicium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utslaget)</text:span> describi ab omnibus l-is - imperavi, C.; legi literas non tuas, sed l-i tui, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bokhandlare:</text:span></text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbrāriŏlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ung, ringa afskrifware; skrifware-gosse:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbrāria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Boklåda:</text:span></text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbrārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bokskrin,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ask, hwari böcker l. skrifter förwaras,</text:span> (scrinium, capsa): exhibe l-um legum vestrarum (Clodii), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbrāriŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: l-is Latinis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afskala</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (eg. bast):</text:span> corticem; radicem, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Liberal . . ., Liberat . . ., Libere, Liberi, Libero, Libert . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Līber.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭbet</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lŭbet), uit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> ĭtum est, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Verb. imperson.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det lyster, det behagar, det faller ngn in; det är ngn en lust, glädje, ett nöje</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i öfwers. med personl. construction: någon har lust, will):</text:span> quod tibi l., idem mihi l., Pt.; si poterit id, quod l-ebit, et l-ebit ei, quod non licet, quid agendum est?; l-et semper discere; l-tum est vobis me ad hanc rem impellere; l-uit mihi de hac re plura dicere, C.; insanire l-et, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt tills. med</text:span> qui, quilibet, quælibet, quid- l. quodlibet = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hwem s. helst,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> se</text:span> Qui.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbens</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lubens), tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">part.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förnöjd, glad, willig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wanl. att öfwers. med adv. l. adverbiala uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gerna, med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till ngns) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förnöjelse, nöje, glädje:</text:span></text:span> te saluto l., Pt.; l-em se facere in nuptiis nati sui; l. benefaxim, Ter.; facti illius gloriam l. agnovit; me l-e id facies; l-simis omnibus porticum demoliti sunt; frequentissimo et l-simo senatu uti; l-simis ceteris alqd consequi; parere l-i animo, C.; tecum vivere amem, tecum abeam l-ens, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gerna, med nöje; med wälbehag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (smak):</text:span> audire alqm; venire; uti equo, quo consuevit, l-ius, quam novo, C.; l. esse ante oculos alicujus, N.; coenare, Cato, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lust, fröjd:</text:span></text:span> pectus porto onustum l-ā, Pt.; conviviorum, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭbentīna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nöjets gudinna, tillnamn för Venus:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbīdo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lubīdo), ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tycke, godtycke, lust, behag, nyck; godtycklighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (samwetslöshet):</text:span> ad l-em fingere, judicare alqd; multa l-e, non ratione gerere; l. judicum; l. in jure dicendo, C.; ex l-e victoria uti; l. victorum, Sa.; prout cuique l. est, siccat calices, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begär, lust, åtrå; lust</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nöje:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. och relat.:</text:span> nauseæ l., Cato; ira est l. ulciscendi; l. procreandi, C.; l. dominandi, reipublicæ capiendæ; l. invasit, tenet alqm; a consueta l-e (pecuniæ capiendæ) animum continere; habere l-em in decoris armis; cibus non l-i est, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sinlig l. köttslig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lusta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wällustigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">begär, begärelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kättja), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wällust:</text:span></text:span> dedere se l-bus; domitas habere l-es; cohibere effrenatas l-es ab aliqua re; nefaria l.; inflammatum ferri l-e, C.; l-e accendi, Sa.; l. tetra, vitiosa, damnosa; l. qualis solet equarum furiare matres, Hor.; in tabellis pingere l-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wällustiga bilder),</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbīdĭnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kättjas; öfwa otukt:</text:span></text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbīdĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Godtycklig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (samwetslös, tyrannisk, egenmäktig):</text:span> sententia (judicis); l-æ reorum liberationes, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sinlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (köttslig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kättjefull, liderlig, wällustig:</text:span></text:span> voluptas; adolescentia<text:span text:style-name="T1">;</text:span> mulier, C.; caper, Hor.; est, reperitur l., N.; dapes, Col.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> eloquentia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(yppig, weklig),</text:span> Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbīdĭnōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Godtyckligt, tyranniskt:</text:span></text:span> populo præesse, C.; consulere in alqm, L., Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liderligt, wällustigt:</text:span></text:span> facere alqd, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbĭta</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nycker, godtyckligheter:</text:span></text:span> exercere sua l-a in alqm, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŭbesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Börja att behaga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> begär börjar att wäckas:</text:span> mihi, Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">börja att känna wälbehag wid ngt,</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭbet</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Collubet) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭbescit</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott brukligt i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pf.</text:span> uit, ĭtum est, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det lyster, faller</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">in, behagar:</text:span></text:span> simul ac c-tum est de te cogitare, occurrit spectrum tuum, C.; pati ea, quæ victoribus c-issent, Sa.; si c-isset -, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭbet</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Perlubet), 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det lyster</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">högeligen</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">någon har stor lust):</text:span> scire, Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭbens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket willig, förnöjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med stort nöje, mycket gerna):</text:span> Pt., C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭbenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket gerna:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlŭbīdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Varr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlŭbium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lust, nyck; nöje:</text:span></text:span> quæ res subito mutavit mores tuos? quod p.?, Ter.; majus, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ībēthra ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lībēthros, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en Muserna helig källa:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>Lībēthrĭdes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: = Musæ: Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Libid . . ., Libita <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭbĭtīna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">begrafningens gudinna, i hwilkens tempel dödsfall anmäldes och allt tillbehör för en begrafning kunde få hyras - deraf oeg. = död, likbår l. -bål; tillbehör för begrafning:</text:span> auctumnus gravis, L-æ quæstus acerbæ; multa pars mei L-am vitabit, Hor.; tanta erat pestilentia, ut L. vix sufficeret, L.; rationes L-æ, Su.; L-am evasit æger, Juv.; l-a struitur papyro, Mt.; qui L-am exercebant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om personer, s. på accord ombesörjde begrafningar; jfr.</text:span> libitinarius), quum rerum suarum usum, tum ministerium gratuitum polliciti sunt, Val. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭbĭtīnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bestyr om begrafningar, (begrafnings-entreprenör):</text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/>Lĭbĭtīnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: porta, Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lībo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i allm. taga, afskilja det första, yttersta, öfwersta af ngt):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i sinl. men.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offra förstlingsoffer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt (med det, som l. hwaraf offras, i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc.</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom förstlingsoffer </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wiga, wälsigna;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra dryckesoffer, libation</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid begynnelse af måltid), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utgjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. dryckesoffer:</text:span> sacerdotes certas fruges publice l-anto, C.; diis dapes, L.; frugem Cereri; mortuo lacrimas, Ov.; in mensas laticum l-vit honorem; munera intemerata l-o focis, pateras Jovi, Vg.; vernas pasco l-tis dapibus (i. e. e quibus et pro quibus l-tum est), Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smaka, läppja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt; i allm. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lätt beröra:</text:span></text:span> dapes; amnem, Vg.; cibi l-ti, Ov.; potio l-ta gustu, T.; cibum digitis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildlig bet.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttaga, -plocka, -draga:</text:span></text:span> ex divinitate animos haustos et l-tos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”emanerade”)</text:span> habemus; ex omni genere urbanitatis facetiarum quendam leporem l-re; ex variis ingeniis excellentissima quæque l.; ex alienis laboribus laudem sibi l., C.; oscula natæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förminska; oskära, kränka:</text:span></text:span> vires non l-tæ, L.; virginitas l-ta, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förstlings-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">begynnelse-offer, dryckesoffer, offergåfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt gudarne af ngt:</text:span> ignibus imponere l-na prima, Vg.; sacrificiorum l-ta; rex quasi l-ta prædarum dona Delphos misit, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förstlingsprof, lärospån:</text:span></text:span> artium, Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gjutoffer:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Taga det första, förstlingen af ngt;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> lätt l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">först beröra; först smaka, pröfwa, försöka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt (inwiga ngt):</text:span> P. Calatinus ex plebe ad novum honorem (tribunatus militaris) d-dum delectus, L.; quisque suas artes (primo die Januarii) d-at agendo, Ov.; quidquid tractaturi sumus, narratione d-bimus, Qu.; cibos d.; plantæ summa æquora, Cd.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttaga, -plocka, borttaga:</text:span></text:span> animos ex mente divina d-tos habemus; flosculos undique carpere et d.; de laude alicujus alqd d., C.; oscula per galeam d., Vg.; de tempore mortis nihil d-re valemus, Lucr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förminska, skada, kränka:</text:span></text:span> pacem animi d., Lucr.; bos truncum cornibus d-bare (al. -brare), Col.; pudicitiam, castitatem alicujus, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Indēlībātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oförminskad; okränkt:</text:span></text:span> opes, Ov.; virgo, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illībātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oförminskad, orörd, oskadd, oförkränkt:</text:span></text:span> divitiæ, C.; imperium, L.; cortex; robur, Col.; foedus, Luc.; gloria, T.; libertas, Js.; virginitas, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælībo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förut smaka på, pröfwa:</text:span></text:span> nectar superis, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlībo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frambära förstlings-, dryckesoffer, offra:</text:span></text:span> vina diis; aquas fictili, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭbo, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i flera romerska</text:span> gentes. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> puteal. Lĭbōniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭbŏnŏtus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sydwest-sydwind:</text:span> Pn., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lībra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wåg; wattenpaß; wåghöjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (plan, niveau):</text:span> alqd in altera l-æ lance ponere; nexum est, quidquid per l-am agitur; testamentum facere sine l-ā et tabulis, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Wågen sås. stjernbild:</text:span> Vg.; æquinoctium l-æ, Pn.; - turris facta ad l-am, Cs.; locus pari l-a cum maris æquore, Col. - calamis Bononiensibus pondus volucre et contra flatus quoque pervicax l-ā <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. håller sig i (samma) niveau, i jemnwigt, utan att sjunka; andre fatta</text:span> l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. nomin.</text:span> = libramen), Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skålpund:</text:span></text:span> corona aurea l-am pondo, L.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett mått för wåta waror:</text:span> olei l., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībella</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wattenpaß:</text:span></text:span> ad l-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wågrätt),</text:span> Varr.; ad normam et l-am fieri, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aß;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fyrk:</text:span></text:span> numi denarii decuma (pars) l., Varr.; ex l-a (= ex asse) heredem (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">universalarfwinge)</text:span> fieri; non l-am dare alicui, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrālis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. wäger ett skålpund; skålpunds-tung:</text:span> l-les asses; l-le pondus, Pn.; frustum l-rium, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrīle</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wåg:</text:span></text:span> Gell. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wågbalk:</text:span></text:span> Fs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrīlia</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slungstenar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af ett skålpunds tyngd):</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrĭpens</text:span>, pendis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (pendo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wågmästare</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den person, som wid ett köp höll wågen, ett bruk från den tid, då metallen ej war myntad, utan wägdes:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Aequĭlībris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wågrät,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> horizontal:</text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Aequĭlībrĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jemnwigt</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lika förhållande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mellan de delar, hwaraf ngt (werlden) består:</text:span> C. de Nat. Deor. I. 119, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwersättning af det grek.</text:span> ἰσονομία <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och förklaradt af</text:span> C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> æqualis tributio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fördelning),</text:span> ibd. I. 50.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Aequĭlībrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jemnwigt; lika förhållande; motswarighet:</text:span></text:span> Sen., Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭlībra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wigt af twå skålpund:</text:span></text:span> farris, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭlībris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. wäger twå skålpund l. håller twenne mått (se</text:span> libra 2., 3.): offa, Pn.; cornu, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Quădrĭlībris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäger fyra skålpund:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Quinquĕlībrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäger fem skålpund:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭlībris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som wäger tre skålpund:</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäga; hålla i jemnwigt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i swäfwande ställning; jemna, afwäga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (nivellera):</text:span> alqd, Vitr.; (indagare) unde terra et quibus l-ta ponderibus, C.; apes se lapillo, Pn.; vela a dubia aura l-antur, Ov.; pavimenta, Cato.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: wäga; öfwerwäga:</text:span> fur es, ait, Pedio. - Pedio quid? crimina rasis l-at in antithetis, Ps.; alqd, Ap.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swänga, swinga; slunga, kasta:</text:span></text:span> cestus; telum; se per nubila, Vg.; <text:soft-page-break/>saxa; miles corpus, Ct.; aquila se ex alto, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swängkraft, -fart:</text:span></text:span> spiculo pinnæ circumdabantur ad l-en, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det s. gifwer kraft l. fart wid wägning, swängning, slungning; (barlast), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tyngd, wigt:</text:span></text:span> l-o plumbi gravatus aries <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(murbräcka),</text:span> L.; tormenti, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afwägning</text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wågrät plan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">yta:</text:span></text:span> extremitas et quasi l. (est), in quo nulla crassitudo sit, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i fråga om wattenledningar: afwägning</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wattnets olika </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höjd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på olika punkter, äfwensom graden af wattnets </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sänkning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sluttning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en wiß sträcka; deraf i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fall, sänkning:</text:span></text:span> aqua si longiore tractu veniet, subeat crebro descendatque, ne l-a pereant; l-um aquæ in centenos pedes sicilici minimum erit, Pn.; l. abditum et cæcum (fontis), Pn. ep. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Jemnwigt:</text:span></text:span> ventorum, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wägning, afwägning, wågrät ställning:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. afwäger en yta l. en punkts höjd i förhållande till en annan), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nivellör:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slungare:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collībro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afmäta:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerwäga, öfwerlägga; betänka sig:</text:span></text:span> amplius d-dum censeo; hoc d-a, dum redeo, Ter.; habere spatium d-di; d-ant, utrum id sequantur, quod honestum esse videant, an se scientes scelere contaminent; d. cum aliquo; d. de aliqua re; re d-ta; ea d-da omnino non sunt, C.; de Avarico; respondit, se diem ad d-dum sumpturum; re d-ta, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sällan) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fråga sig till råds:</text:span></text:span> consilium fidele d-nti dare, C.; d-tibus Pythia respondit, N.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter öfwerläggning </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besluta:</text:span></text:span> d-vi non adesse; certum d-tumque est omnia dicere, C. - d-ta morte ferocior, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fast besluten:</text:span></text:span> nihil illi d-tius est quam me evertere, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībĕrābundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gående i tankar, betänkande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig:</text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerläggning:</text:span></text:span> difficilis; d. consilii capiendi; habere, suscipere rei, de re d-em; introducere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i systemet upptaga);</text:span> adhibere ad d-em; consumere d-em in re; res cadit in d-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blir föremål för -);</text:span> res habet <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(medgifwer, fordrar)</text:span> d-em; disceptationes judiciorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid domstolarne)</text:span> aut d-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i senaten),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībĕrātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som består i öfwerläggning:</text:span> genus causæ, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlībĕrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som öfwerwäger, betänker sig:</text:span> d-i merces duplicata est, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlībro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afwäga; göra wågrät:</text:span></text:span> excelsa, Sen.; opus p-tum, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slunga:</text:span></text:span> fronti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot pannan)</text:span> bipennem, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lībr . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Libra.<text:line-break/>Lĭbrar . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lĭber.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ibs, Lĭbis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (= Libys): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">west-sydwestwind:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭbui, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Gallia Transpadana.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lībum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Lībus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: Non.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kaka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">offerkaka:</text:span></text:span> adorea liba, Vg.; l-a deo fiunt, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lībārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. säljer kakor:</text:span> variæ l-i exclamationes (in via), Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭburnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Liburner, ett folk i Dalmatien, och liburnisk:</text:span> ingens L-us, Juv.; L-i, Vg.; terræ L-æ, Luc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭburna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags snabbseglande skepp:</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>Lĭburnia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Liburnernes land.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭburnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liburnisk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭburnĭca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> = Liburna.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭbys, y̆os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> y̆is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Libyer och libysk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭby̆a, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Libyen (Africa).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭby̆cus, <text:line-break/>Lĭbyssus, <text:line-break/>Lĭbystīnus, <text:line-break/>Lĭby̆us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">libysk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭbystis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">libysk:</text:span> ursa, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭby̆ægyptĭi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Lĭby̆phoenīces, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag blandade af Libyer med Aegyptier l. Phoenicier.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Licens, Licent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Licet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭceo,</text:span> ui, ĭtum, 2.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i act.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara fal,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol. l. för ett wißt pris; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stå till buds, gälla, kosta:</text:span></text:span> servi aliquo pretio, Pt.; quanti hortos l-isse scribis - -, C.; non pluris unius assis pretio, Hor.; parvo pretio l-et, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭceor</text:span>, ĭtus, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjuda, falka på;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wilja köpa, wärdera en wara</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">aliquid pretio aliquo</text:span>): non illicitatorem venditor, non qui contra se l-atur (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bjuder underpris),</text:span> emptor apponet; digito (i. e. d-o sublato) l-ri; l-ti sunt usque eo, quoad se efficere posse arbitrabantur; hortos l-ri, C.; illo l-ente contra l-ri audebat nemo, Cs.; centum Græcos asse (ɔ: plane contemnit), Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcĭtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjuda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på (uppskatta) ngt:</text:span> contra animi mei sententiam, Pt.; tabulam centum talentis, Pn.; capita hostium, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">successivt stegradt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anbud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett pris, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerbjudning (auction):</text:span></text:span> exquisitis palam pretiis et l-e facta, C.; sacerdotia l-e comparare, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭcĭtātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">beställd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerbjudare, stegrare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid en auction:</text:span> i-em apponere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollĭceo</text:span> (Varr.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollĭceor</text:span>, ĭtus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med activ och någongång</text:span> (Ov.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">passiv betydelse), 2.: (af</text:span> por- <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> liceor; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> possideo, pono): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">erbjuda, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utfästa sig till, lofwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (constr. med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">objects-accus., acc. cum inf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och med ensam</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">inf.</text:span>): pretium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(betalning);</text:span> montes auri; dare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att gifwa),</text:span> Ter.; benigne; ultro; contra fecerunt, quam p-ti sunt; alqd alicui de suis <text:soft-page-break/>opibus p.; non minus ei prolixe de <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(angående)</text:span> tua voluntate promisi, quam eram solitus de mea p-ri; alicui alqd pro certo, operam suam; se daturos p-entur, C.; p-entur - imperio populi Romani obtemperare; p-tus est, eam rem sibi curæ futuram, Cs.; p-etur, se Græciam sub regis potestatem redacturum, N.; bene p-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa goda löften);</text:span> montes, maria p-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ordspråk),</text:span> Sa.; certe hinc Romanos fore - p-tus, Vg.; meliora p-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwit bättre löfte om sig);</text:span> quinque dies p-tus sum me rure futurum, Hor.; fides p-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lofwad),</text:span> Ov.; Chauci auxilia p-bantur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollĭcĭtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löfte:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollĭcĭtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ideligen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">frikostigt lofwa:</text:span></text:span> alicui operam suam, Pt.; dare et p-ri multa; largiundo et p-do incendere alqm, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollĭcĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frikostigt lofwande, löfte:</text:span></text:span> multis p-bus aggredi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(söka locka)</text:span> alqm, Sa.; infinitis p-bus incitare alqm, C.; regis p., Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭceor</text:span>, ēri: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjuda emot</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bjuda ett underpris på en wara, endast gißningswis antagen läsart</text:span> (contra reliceatur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i st. f.</text:span> contra se liceatur), C. de Off. III. c. 15.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭcet,</text:span> uit (<text:span text:style-name="T1">fut. ex. conj.</text:span> licessit, Pt.), ĭtum est, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. samma verb. s. det föregående = det står till buds?): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det tillåtes, är tillåtet, står fritt; man får:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med bibehållande af den egentliga bet.:</text:span> l-et me scire?, Ter.; quid magis vituperandum, quam id facere, quod non l-at?; l-re dicimus, quod legibus, quod more majorum institutisque conceditur; id per me tibi, per leges l-et; nemini l-et peccare; l-uit mihi otioso vivere; l-et medios <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(neutrale),</text:span> miseros esse, C.; l-et esse beatis, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">conj.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(han, du) må:</text:span> l-et pauca degustes; sequatur eum l-bit; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">ut</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">conj.</text:span>: non jam l-et mihi, ut meum laborem hominum periculis sublevandis non impertiam, C.; experiare l-et, Vg.; sis l-et felix, ubicunque mavis, Hor.; in servum omnia l-ent, Sen. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med modificerad betydelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det är möjligt, man kan:</text:span></text:span> l-et ora ipsa cernere iratorum - - quorum omnium vultus - mutantur; hæc præscripta servantem l-et magnifice - atque etiam simpliciter vivere; l-et hoc videre in reliquis sensibus; id primum cerni in poētis l-et; non sunt ea bona dicenda, quibus abundantem l-et esse miserrimum, C.; l-et sub paupere tecto vitā reges præcurrere, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. uttryck för medgifwande af en saks sanning l. för ett antagande, närmande sig till en concessiv conjunction med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">conj.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dock alltid af tempus för närwarande tid): han (du, de, I) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Må; om ock, änskönt:</text:span></text:span> quantumvis l-et excellas; veritas l-et defensorem nullum habeat, tamen per se ipsa defenditur, C.; planum tollere nemo curat, l-et illi plurima manet lacrima, Hor.; Phalaris l-et imperet, ut sis falsus - - summum crede nefas animam præferre pudori; tota l-et veteres exornent undique ceræ atria, nobilitas sola est atque unica virtus, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Comp.</text:span> -ior: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fri, lös, obunden, godtycklig, sjelfswåldig:</text:span></text:span> l-ior ille et divitior dithyrambus, C.; Lupercus, Ov.; conversatio cum viris, Sen.; epistola, Pn.; imperium; vita, Val.; <text:soft-page-break/>gressus, Mt.; joci, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcenter</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fritt, utan band; utan ordning, regel; sjelfswåldigt, oförsynt, fräckt:</text:span></text:span> vivere l-ius cum aliquo; (oratio) ingredi libere, non errare l. videatur; l. abuti aliqua re, C.; (sperabat Jugurtha) Romanos remoto metu laxius l-iusque futuros, Sa.; eludere alqm, L.; efflagitare, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">relat. och i indifferent mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (att handla efter eget godtfinnande, ej efter regel l. andras bestämmande):</text:span> magnis et divinis bonis hanc l-am (contra morem consuetudinemque civilem faciendi) assequebantur (Socrates et Aristippus): tantum l-æ dabat gloria (C. Duilio); pueris non omnem l-am ludendi damus; nobis Academia magnam dat l-am, ut, quodcunque maxime probabile occurrat, id nostro jure liceat defendere; l-am vivendi præcidere alicui; largiri alicui l-am; obtinere; possidere, C.; l. injuriæ; permittere belli componendi l-am alicui, Sa.; dabitur l. sumpta pudenter, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i dålig mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Godtycklighet; regel-, laglöshet, sjelfswåld, egenmäktighet, fräckhet:</text:span></text:span> philosophi, C.; deteriores omnes sumus l-ā, Ter.; poena abfuit, l. consecuta est; nisi multorum scelera impunita tulissemus, nunquam ad unum venisset tanta l.; libertas immoderata et l. concionum; omnium rerum infinita et intoleranda l.; l. ad maledicendum, C.; inveterata militum l., N.; refrenare indomitam l-am; lasciva l., Hor.; verborum, Ct.; temporum, Pn.; mentiendi, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcentiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjelfswåldig, godtycklig:</text:span></text:span> miles, T.; l-um est dicere, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭcĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillåten:</text:span></text:span> sermo, Vg.; l-a atque illicita, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭcĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Otillåten, oloflig:</text:span></text:span> hono res; amor, T.; viæ, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭcĭte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælĭcenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Alltför djerft</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sielfswåldigt:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭchădes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">små öar wid Euboea.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭchas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līchen,</text:span> ēnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäxtslag:</text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ref-orm:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭcĭnius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en romersk</text:span> gens. <text:line-break/>Lĭcĭniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭcĭnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillnamn i romerska</text:span> gentes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Licitatio, -citor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liceo.<text:line-break/>Licitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Licet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līcium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Solf,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">solf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sölfwor</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af tråd knutna, mellan wäfbommen och wäfskeden sittande rader af lyckor, genom hwilka (wid uppsättande af en wäf) warptrådarne dragas; af det sätt, hwarpå detta sker, beror wäfwens mönster, liks. på solftrådarnes antal wäfnadens enkelhet l. flerskäftighet); i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lycka, slynga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">trollband</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">trollknut:</text:span></text:span> l-a addere telæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sölfwa, sätta upp en wäf),</text:span> Vg. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(deraf hos</text:span> Eccl. liciatus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sölfwad = börjad);</text:span> l. telæ detractum - inguini adalligare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. en trollkur),</text:span> Pn.; terna l-a triplic i diversa <text:soft-page-break/>colore alicui circumdare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid beswärjelser),</text:span> Vg.; l-a dependent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ss. helgeskänker i Dianas lund)</text:span> longas velantia sæpes, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭlix</text:span>, īcis,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭlix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. (med dubbla l. tredubbla solfrader) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twe-, treskäftig:</text:span></text:span> tunica t., Mt.; lorica b., t. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af dubbla l. tredubbla ringar (l. trådar?),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lictor,</text:span> ōris <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Lictor, lictorer</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">drabanter, som med</text:span> fasces (q. v.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på axlarne gingo (i rad efter hwarandra) l. stodo framför konungarne, när de uppträdde offentligen, äfwensom framför den ene af årets consuler (i tur) och åtskillige andre embetsmän, för att bana wäg åt dem bland folkhopen, hålla ordning i folkförsamlingar och öfwerhufwud werkställa öfwerhetens befallningar, serskildt i fråga om kropps- eller lifsstraff.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">För detta sista ändamål och ss. tecken dertill hade de ock yxor i</text:span> fasces, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wederbörande myndighet egde fullt</text:span> imperium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och dermed</text:span> jus vitæ et necis: anteibant (prætori) l-es cum fascibus duobus, C.; Romulus se l-bus duodecim sumptis augustiorem fecit; i, l., colliga manus, caput obnube, verbera -; l-em consules ad (detrectantem militiam) mittunt; l-es populum summovere jubentur, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lictōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: virga, Fl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭcymnia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liēn,</text:span> ēnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Liēnis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: Ce.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjälte:</text:span></text:span> turget, Cato.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Liēnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjältsjuk:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭentĕrĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bukflöde:</text:span></text:span> Pr isc.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭentĕrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. lider af b.:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ligamen, -mentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Ligo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭgārius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭgāriānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ligatura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Ligo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭgēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: gr. <text:span text:style-name="T1">n. pr.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>iger, ĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭger, ĕris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Gallien, (Loire).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>igii <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lygii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">germaniskt folk.</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lignum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trä</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. ämne), trästycke, -stock; serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wed, bränsle:</text:span></text:span> magnam vim l-orum in flumen jacere, L.; hoc l-o (i. e. equo Trojano) inclusi occultantur Achivi; oleaster, nautis olim venerabile l.; transire præcordia l-o (i. e. hasta), Vg.; l-o incidere leges; tu triste l., tu caducum in domini caput immerentis; mobile l., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om mska),</text:span> Hor.; chirographa supervacui l-i (tabellæ), Juv.; ex viridibus et humidis l-is ignem facere, C.; conferre l-a circum casam, N.; l-a domino in tabulato condito, codicillos oleaginos, Cato; dissolve frigus l-a super <text:soft-page-break/>foco large reponens; dum potes, aridum compone l., Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i frukt:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. sysselsätter sig med trä:</text:span> negotiatio, Cp. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snickare:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ligneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af trä, trä-:</text:span></text:span> materia; soleæ, C.; vasa, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Träaktig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hård, torr):</text:span> putamen, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ligneŏlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af trä</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om arbeten med träsnideri):</text:span> lychnuchus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignĭcīda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i anal. med</text:span> lapicida <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildadt af</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hemta wed:</text:span></text:span> num lignatum mittimur?, Pt.; milites l-andi causa longius progrediebantur, Cs.; ire l-atum, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trähygge</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till wed); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wedhemtning:</text:span></text:span> Cs. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wedskog:</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wedhemtare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för armée):</text:span> Cs., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lignōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Träaktig:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭgo,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spade, hacka:</text:span></text:span> l-bus versare glebas, Hor.; purgare arva longis l-bus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭgo,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda, (hopsätta, ombinda, -linda):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> mula l-atur, Hor.; guttura laqueo; vulnera <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förbinda),</text:span> Ov.; comas, Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> dissociata locis concordi pace l-vit, Ov.; (syllogismos) in catenas l-re, Qu.; legibus alqm, St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭgāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭgāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Band, förband:</text:span></text:span> mitræ l-na, Ppt.; sanguinem inhibere l-e; vitium l., Col. - vulneribus l-ta petere, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭgātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: id.: Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĭgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda, fastbinda, häfta wid:</text:span></text:span> hominem ad palum, C.: vitem palis, ad palum, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förbinda, ombinda:</text:span></text:span> vulnus; oculum, C.; dolia vite siccā, Cato.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda, fängsla, fästa:</text:span></text:span> ancora naves unco morsu; Styx mortuos, Vg.; colorem algă, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda, fästa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid ngn l. ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">binda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hindra):</text:span> alqm alicui (amicæ), Ter.; in aliqua re impediri et a-ri; sine fructu a-ri (amico); nuptiis a-tum habere in potestate, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt l. genom lag </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbinda, -pligta, binda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till, wid ngt (underkasta)</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">ad rem</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T1">re</text:span>): lex omnes a-at; alqm lege, stipulatione, sacris, quæstione nova; verba nec certa lege versus a-ta nec soluta; beneficio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genom wälgerning)</text:span> alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göra förbunden),</text:span> C.; civitas foedere iniquo, L.; ad præcepta, ad certas dicendi leges se a-re, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. se a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> a-ri = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra sig skyldig:</text:span></text:span> furti, Ter., C.; scelere, C.; ad poenam, Qu.; a-tus homo, a-tum nomen alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inwecklad i, ”graverad” af en beskyllning),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fastbindning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om träd):</text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĭgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĭgātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> = alligatio: Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ădallĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fastbinda wid; widhäfta:</text:span></text:span> alqd ad rem, rei, cum re, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭpĕrallĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda ofwanpå:</text:span></text:span> Pn. inc. l.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda omkring; ombinda, -linda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> natam hastæ (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>), Vg.; angui c-tus, C.; stuppā ferrum c., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: (om flera föremål) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hopbinda, sammanbinda;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om ett föremål) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">binda, slå i band,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (medelst band sammanpressa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hopdraga, -fästa:</text:span></text:span> lictor, colliga manus (damnati hominis), C., L.; plura scuta uno ictu pilorum c-antur, Cs.; in fasciculos res aliquas, Pn.; alqm, Ter.; vinculis c-ri, C.; vulnera bitumen, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbinda, förena; sammanfatta; binda, fjättra, hämma:</text:span></text:span> omnes res inter se aptæ et c-tæ sunt; homines inter se sermonis vinculo c-antur; sententiam verbis c.; uno libro multa c.; c-vimus Brutum in Asia; impetum alicujus, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanbindning, -kedjning, -knytning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och oeg. bet.):</text:span> rerum, Vitr.; causarum; societatis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fastbinda, fästa; förbinda:</text:span></text:span> ad palum alqm, C., L.; navem ad ancoras, ad ripam, Cs.; sarmenta in cornibus (boum), N.; grana in linteola, Pn.; vulnus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda på, fastbinda; insnärja, -weckla:</text:span></text:span> aratra juvencis, Hor.; in currus distentum i-at Mettium; post tergum manus i., L.; impeditis locis se et equites i., T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infatta, -foga:</text:span></text:span> scite in aureis poculis alqd; lunæ, solis, errantium (ɔ: planetarum) motus in sphæram i-vit Archimedes, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Infatta, -foga, -blanda:</text:span></text:span> sententias verbis; alqd in orationem; lepores in aliquo dicendi genere; personas tam graves nolunt sermonibus ejusmodi i-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(göras till interlocutörer i philosophiske dialoger),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inweckla, fästa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett förhållande; sersk. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">insnärja, omsnärja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (försåtligt angripa):</text:span> gentem bello i.; non iis condicionibus rex i-bitur, ut bellum movere possit; regis amicitia i-ri, L.; duarum matrimoniis i-ri, Val.; libri angustis disputationibus i-ti, C.; veneno alqm T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda:</text:span></text:span> M. Lepidum multis pignoribus i-tum tenet, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭpĕrillĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda öfwer:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda emellan:</text:span></text:span> St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbinda</text:span></text:span> (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genom band hindra, innesluta o. s. w.):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förbinda; binda för, om, upp:</text:span></text:span> corio obvolutus et o-tus; o-at vulnus, alqm medicus, C.; crus, Pt.; oculos, Ct.; venas, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med personl. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förpligta, -binda, binda, göra förbunden:</text:span></text:span> se sponsione, uno verbo; alqm sacramento militiæ; jurejurando et conscientia o-ri; alqm sibi liberalitate, beneficio o.; tenere alqm o-<text:soft-page-break/>tum; putare se alicui o-tum, C.; is ei o-tior abit, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. obj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pant-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skuldsätta; sätta i pant;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: åtaga sig förbindelse med afs. på ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lofwa, helga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tilldöma åt ngn:</text:span> domum; prædia; fidem suam alicui, C.; fidem pignore, Ct.; prædia alicui, Su.; ergo o-tam redde Jovi dapem; caput votis o., Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblĭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fastbindning:</text:span></text:span> linguæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tungband):</text:span> Js.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Answarande; skuldsättning, pant-sättning, skuldförbindelse:</text:span></text:span> est gravior animi et sententiæ, præsertim pro altero, quam pecuniæ o-io <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att answara för),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælĭgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> framför l. framtill på ngt:</text:span> sarmenta boum cornibus, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda för; förbinda, tillbinda, ombinda:</text:span></text:span> os, C.; vulnus; caput lino, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fängsla, tjusa:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭgo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda, knyta, fästa bakåt, upp; fastbinda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid något (eg i hängande l. lutande ställning):</text:span> funiculus a puppi r-tus scapham trahebat, C.; manus post terga r-re, Su.; Hectorem ad currum r-tum trahit Achilles, C.; navem ad terram; naves ferreis manibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äntra),</text:span> Cs.; classem ab aggere, Vg.; litore navem; comam r-ta <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med håret uppfästadt)</text:span> in comptum nodum, Hor.; catenā alqd; alqm quadrigis, Ov.; alqd in cacumine mali, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> virtus si extrinsecus r-ta pendeat, non video, cur - aut verbis ornanda aut expetenda videatur, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lösa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> recludo): juga manu, Catl.; equi r-ti carpebant gramen, Vg. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppbindande:</text:span></text:span> vitium (ad juga) r-es, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Irrĕlĭgātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ouppbunden:</text:span></text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Binda inunder; uppbinda; gördla; uppgördla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr.</text:span> succingo): ensem lateri, Vg.; vites, Cato; virgo s-ta, Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĭgācŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skört, förkläde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blygdgördel):</text:span> in scenam sine s-o prodit nemo, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĭgar</text:span>, āris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: id.: Ps., Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĭgātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: uvarum, Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Ligula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lingula, Lingua.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭgur, ŭris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span> - <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭgŭres, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ligurier, namn på folkslag i westre delen af norra Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭgŭria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Ligurien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭgŭrīnus, <text:line-break/>Lĭguscus, <text:line-break/>Lĭgustĭcus, <text:line-break/>Lĭgustīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭgustĭcum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en i Ligurien inhemsk blomma:</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭgūrio</text:span> <text:line-break/>(ligurrio), 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> lingo, lingua):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slicka, smaka, läppja (snaska)</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt:</text:span> cum amatore cum <text:soft-page-break/>coenant, l-unt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blott läppja),</text:span> Ter.; apes pungunt, muscæ l-unt, Varr.; jus tepidum; frusta l-re, Hor. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">smaka, läppja på = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lätt röra, befatta sig med, tillgripa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> degusto): quoniam jam dialecticus es et hoc quoque l-is, -; non timide neque lepide - lucra l-iit, devorare - non dubitavit, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gripa efter, wara lysten efter:</text:span> curationem agrariam, C. (?)<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭgūrītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snaskande,) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fråsseri:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭgūrītor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läckermun, -gom:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablĭgūrio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Af-, uppslicka;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> deraf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fråssa upp, i wällust förslösa:</text:span></text:span> patria bona, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablĭgūrītio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblĭgūrio</text:span>, 4.: id.: Enn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Liguscus, -gustĭcum, -gusticus, -gustinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ligur.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭgustrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liguster</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (buske, och deß bär):</text:span> alba l-a cadunt, vaccinia nigra leguntur, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līlium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lilja:</text:span></text:span> breve, Hor.; candida, alba l-a, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skansgraf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i form af en liljekalk:</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līliāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.:</text:span> oleum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af liljor beredd):</text:span> Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līliētum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liljegård, -rabatt:</text:span> Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭly̆bæum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">landtudde och stad på Siciliens nordwestra kust.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭly̆bætānus, <text:line-break/>Lĭly̆bæus, <text:line-break/>Lĭly̆bēĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fil:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. uttryck:</text:span> anum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ring)</text:span> l-ā præterere, Pt.; l. polit opus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck för: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Granskning, utarbetning, filning, polering:</text:span></text:span> unumquemque (Latinorum poētarum) offendit l-æ labor et mora, Hor.; defuit et scriptis ultima l. meis; l-ā mordacius uti, Ov.; scriptum l-ā persequi; l-am intendere scripto, Pn.; in hoc l-æ, in illis sanguinis plus est, Vell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fila, släta, polera:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> <text:line-break/>1. i eg. men.:</text:span> elephantus cornu ad saxa; gemmas, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hyfsa, polera, utarbeta, bilda, utbilda:</text:span></text:span> ars (naturam) l-at; (librum) politius l.; alia est illa subtilitas, quum ipsa veritas l-atur (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">framställes i sin renhet)</text:span> in disputatione; acumen arte l.; ad minuta causarum genera se l., C.; ratio l-at alqd, Qu. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">part. pf.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmātus</text:span>, -ior = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgfällig, fin, correct, grundlig, bildad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mots.</text:span> rudis, horridus, lĕvis; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">syn.</text:span> elegans, subtilis): vir oratione maxime l. et subtilis; subtili et pressa oratione l-ti; genus dicendi l-tius; l-ta tenuitas (orationis); homo urbanitate l-tus, C.; ingenium l-tius (non majus), Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Affila</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = småningom borttaga l. förminska:</text:span> alteri affinxit, de altero (discipulo) l-vit, ut id conformaret in utroque, quod utriusque natura pateretur; annus posterior de tua benefica natura l-vit alqd, C.; <text:soft-page-break/>commoda alicujus obliquo oculo l., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmāte</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">fint, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Grundligt:</text:span></text:span> liber l. scriptus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.</text:span> populariter), C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmātŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förfinad; fin:</text:span></text:span> judicium tuum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Affilad:</text:span></text:span> scobes, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlīmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fila,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> genom filning förfärdiga (liks. ut-, framfila):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> graciles ex ære catenas Volcanus, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utarbeta, -tänka:</text:span></text:span> rationes latiore specie, non ad tenue e-tæ, C.; scriptum, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblīmo</text:span>, 1.: rem patris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försätta, -nöta),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlīmo</text:span>, 1.: speciem oculorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skärpa, göra klar),</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līmax,</text:span> ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m. f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snigel:</text:span></text:span> l., quod in limo vivit, dicta, Varr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">derför om</text:span> meretrices <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Limbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bräm, bord</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (garnering):</text:span> chlamys picto l-o, Vg.; aureus l. obit chlamydem, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djurkretsen,</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(list) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hår-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">pannband; bälte; bord</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett nät:</text:span> frontem velata l-o, Cd.; Grat. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Limbŏlārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. garnerar kläder:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līmen,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tröskel, dörrträ,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfre och undre; ofta metonym. för hela dörröppningen och deß beklädnad, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">dörr:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. uttryck:</text:span> l. inferum superumque salve; cohibete vos intra l., Pt.; exire l-n, Ter.; fores in l-bus privatarum ædium januæ appellantur, C.; amat janua l.; l. marmoreum venerandi amici, Hor.; ad l. consulis mane adesse jussi sunt, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ofta hos poet., i uttryck, der wi tänka på hela huset:</text:span> adire l-a alicujus; interiora domus l-a irrumpere; domos et dulcia l-a mutare, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om skranken på Circus,</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. uttr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tröskel, dörr</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ingång, -träde, gräns, början till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt:</text:span> leti l-e in ipso, Lucr.; in l-e mortis, Catl.; extra l-en Apuliæ, Hor.; in l-e belli, T. - (dialectica) prospicienda tantum et a l-e salutanda <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från tröskeln helsa</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">taga en flygtig öfwerblick af -),</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭnāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: trabes, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlīmĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Föra ut om tröskeln</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dörren, huset, gränsen):</text:span> se urbe, Enn. - ne fidos inter amicos sit, qui dicta foras e-et (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">utsprida),</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līmes,</text:span> ĭtis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twärwäg, rågång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwer l. mellan egor, efter hwilken dessa uppmätas och begränsas från hwarandra:</text:span> semitas et l-es novos in agro fieri non patiatur (villicus), Col.; sues in lutosos l-es volutantur, Varr.; partiri campum l-e, Vg.; populus certis l-bus positus; ultra l-es salis avarus, Hor.; communem - prius cautus humum longo signavit l-e mensor, Ov.; reptare per l-em -, arbusculas numerare, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gränswall</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (mellan riken), spec. romerska rikets befästade gräns mellan Rhen och Donau</text:span> (limes imperii): l-e acto promotisque præsidiis (agri decumates) pars provinciæ habentur, T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">anlagd, upphöjd </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (chaussée), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">militärwäg; wäg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.:</text:span> Germanicus - l-em a Tiberio coeptum scindit; castra in l-e locat, T.; transversis l-bus proficisci; l. in Gymnasium ferens, L.; ducam te lato l-e, Vg.; sectus in obliquum lato curvamine l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om djurkretsen),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Råmärke; gräns:</text:span></text:span> saxum - l. agro positus, Vg.; minus laxum l-em benignitati aperire, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭtāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid (riks-)gränsen belägen l. förlagd:</text:span> ager; miles, Lpd. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭtāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: termini propter iter l-e (= limes) magis teruntur, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afdela; begränsa:</text:span></text:span> vineas cardine, Pn.; quæstionem, Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afgränsning, bestämning:</text:span></text:span> terræ vinealis (i. e. descriptio, qualis terra ad vineam apta sit), Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collīmĭtāneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samgränsande:</text:span></text:span> Sol. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collīmĭtium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samgräns:</text:span></text:span> Sol.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collīmĭto</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collīmĭtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gränsa till, tillsammans:</text:span> Amm., Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Limicola, -migenus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Limus <text:line-break/>L<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span>minaris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Limen.<text:line-break/>Limis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Limus. <text:line-break/>Limit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Limes.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Limnē,</text:span> es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sjö:</text:span></text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/>Limnātis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: templum Dianæ L-dis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på Peloponnesus):</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>īmo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(äng): namn på en förlorad skrift af</text:span> Cic.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmōnĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmōnĭon</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäxtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Limo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lima.<text:line-break/>III. Limo, Limosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Limus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Limpĭdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af st. i</text:span> lympha?): p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar, skär, genomskinlig, ren:</text:span></text:span> lacus, Catl.; vinum l-simum, Col.; vox, gemma, Pn.; aqua l-ior, Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Limpĭdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klara, göra klar:</text:span></text:span> humorem, Mcb.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Limpĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klarhet, genomskinlighet:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Limulus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Limus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Līmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lino?) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dy, gyttja; lera; slam, grums:</text:span></text:span> luta et l-um aggerere, C.; frumenti acervi in vado hæsitabant illiti l-o; profundus l., L.; l. durescit igni, Vg.; princeps l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwaraf Prometheus skapat menniskan),</text:span> Hor.; l. veteri crateræ adhæsit; l-um (vini) ovo columbino colligere, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> l. vitiorum, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭcŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">c.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmĭgĕnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bor l. wäxer i dy:</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmo</text:span>, 1.: caput alicui (limo) l. = limo obducere, Pt. Poen. 1. 2. 80.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gyttjefull, gyttjig:</text:span></text:span> lacus, Vg.; humus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illīmis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(dy-fri), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar:</text:span></text:span> fons, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illīmātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: alvearia limo Punico frondibus i-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(påsmetade?)</text:span> adumbrare (alii: illinitis), Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblīmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwertäcka med gyttja; tillsmeta:</text:span></text:span> Nilus agros Aegypti, C.; sulcos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bild),</text:span> Vg.; copia mentes (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förblindar),</text:span> Cd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Līmus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om blick, öga) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sned, skelande:</text:span></text:span> aspicere, aspectare l-is oculis, Pt., Ter.; l-bus oculis, Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līmŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">smått skelande:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collīmo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">falsk läsart i st. f.</text:span> collineo, q. v.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">III. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Līmus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förkläde:</text:span></text:span> velati l-o, Vg. XII. 120.; l. vestis est genus, quo - ab umbilico usque ad pedes velabantur pudenda poparum; in extremo sui purpuram limam i. e. flexuosam habet: unde nomen - -, Serv. (alii: lino).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭmy̆rē, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Lycien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Linamentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Linum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>indus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Rhodus.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lindĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Line . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Linum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lingo</text:span>, linxi, linctum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slicka:</text:span></text:span> mel, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlingo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afslicka; uppslicka:</text:span></text:span> leo puerum, Lpd.; salem l. (= misere victitare), Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlingo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slicka ut:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublingio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tallrickslickare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ingŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T1">sing.</text:span> -gŏnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: Mt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folkslag.</text:span> Lingŏnĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lingua,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(möjligtwis af</text:span> lingo; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. Gramm.:</text:span> olim dingua, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> lacrima, dacrima): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tunga:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om kroppsdelen i och för sig):</text:span> l. in ore sita est, finita dentibus; efficit sonos distinctos; l. alicujus inhæret <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(han har tungband);</text:span> ejicere l-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uträcka),</text:span> C.; l-am exserere (id.), L.; natura effert motus animi interprete l-ā, Hor.; l-ā hæsitare, titubare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stamma);</text:span> l-am excīdere, evellere alicui, C.; l. trisulca colubri, Vg.; l. fissa, bisulca; l. titubat, torpet, silet, riget, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tunga;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mer l. mindre metonymiskt = munföre, förmåga att tala (dock aldrig om föredragets formella art ss. för ngn person egendomlig); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tal</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">talareförmåga):</text:span> l. celeris et exercitata; l-æ solutio; l. quasi flabellum seditionis; l-am continere, cohibere; vitare l-as hominum; cedant arma togæ, concedat laurea l-æ, C.; l. ventosa, pedes fugaces; Drances l-ā melior, sed bello frigida dextra; mala l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ond tunga),</text:span> Vg.; l-ā quam manu promptior; aliud clausum in pectore, aliud promptum in l-a habere, Sa.; Aetolorum l-as retundere, L.; l. magna (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stormodigt tal);</text:span> l-am causis acuere; l-is favete; est <text:soft-page-break/>animus tibi, sunt mores, est l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(talareförmåga)</text:span> fidesque; l. Catonis et Enni sermonem patrium ditavit, Hor. - l-æ temeritas, intemperantia, Ct.; petulantia, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tunga = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tungomål,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (en nations) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">språk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej en dialect af ett språk, ej heller en författares språk = stil):</text:span> nostra, aliena, Græca, Latina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ej</text:span> Romana); inops, locuples, copiosa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fattigt, rikt språk);</text:span> l-am intelligere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förstå);</text:span> utram tandem l-am nescio (Græcam an Latinam)?; l-ā Latinā optime uti; aliā l-ā loqui, C.; Galli et Belgæ inter se l-ā differunt; uti l-ā aliqua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tala);</text:span> l-æ alicujus scientiam habere, Cs.; civitatis l. conversa est connubio Numidarum; l. barbara, Sa.; doctus sermones utriusque l-æ; l-ā divite Latium beabit (poēta); nec virtute foret - potentius quam l-ā Latium, si non -, Hor.; Latinæ l-æ sciens, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föremål, hwars form liknar tungans:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Landtunga:</text:span></text:span> urbs in l-is sita, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäxtnamn (ox-, hundtunga):</text:span> Cato, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skedblad ss. mått:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den korta ändan af en häfstång:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linguārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tungplikt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (plikt för oförståndigt tal l. löfte; ord ur hwardagsspråket, bildadt i analogi med</text:span> calcearium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">o. dyl.):</text:span> ut postea consideratius loquaris (loquar?), quod dicere solemus, l. dabo, Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linguātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med tunga:</text:span> Anth.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linguax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pratsjuk:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lingŭla</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭgŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Landtunga:</text:span></text:span> Cs. (alii: lingua).<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tunga, kil</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i sko:</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tungan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på wågen:</text:span> Schol. ad Ps.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sked, slef:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Pn.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tapp:</text:span></text:span> paxillorum, quæ transversis foratis perticis inducuntur, Col.<text:line-break/>f. gladioli genus: Næv. apud Varr. et Gell.<text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">munstycke på en flöjt:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>h. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ändan af en häfstång, s. lägges under den tyngd, s. skall lyftas:</text:span> Cato, Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lingŭlāca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pratmakerska:</text:span></text:span> Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en fisk:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lingŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: tubi (aquæductuum): Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linguōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pratsjuk:</text:span></text:span> Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭlinguis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twetungad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har twenne tungomål:</text:span> Bruttates b-es, Enn.; Canusini more b., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twetalig, falsk:</text:span></text:span> Tyrii b-es, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlinguis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mållös:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ej talför,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. saknar talareförmåga:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlinguo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Beröfwa tungan:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭlinguis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tretungad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> os Cerberi, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har l. kan tala tre språk:</text:span> Varr., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Liniger <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Linum.<text:line-break/>Linimentum, -nitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lino.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭno,</text:span> lēvi, lĭtum, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja, bestryka; öfwer-, tillsmeta; öfwerdraga, belägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> l-ere alqd pice, L.; spiramenta (alveariorum) cerā, Vg.; carmina (i. e. membranam) cedro; vinum (ɔ: testam, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sprunda),</text:span> Hor.; faciem, ora luto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sminka);</text:span> auro tecta, Ov.; linire nova dolia gummi, Col.; falces sanguine ursino, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> l. labra alicui = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bedraga,</text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedsmörja, sudla:</text:span></text:span> scriptores carmine foedo splendida facta l-unt, Hor.; lutulenta mula lacernas, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭnīmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja, beläggning:</text:span></text:span> dolii, Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭnītus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Påstrykning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭtūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Påstrykning:</text:span></text:span> Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utstrykning, radering</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (så wäl i abstract mening, som om sjelfwa fläcken l. det raderade stället); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kladd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en skrift (på wax l. med bläck på papper):</text:span> l. nominis, codicis; nomen est, literæ sunt in l-a; l. corrigit, tollit mendum scripturæ, C.; turpem putat inscite metuitque l-am, Hor.; hæc erit e lacrimis facta l. meis, Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭtūrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: (libri) l-i = adversaria, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">kladd, concept,</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bestrykning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allĭno</text:span>, (lēvi), lĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bestryka, belägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> tabulam schedā papyri; dentes aliqua re, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (göra ett streck) wid ngt (ett ställe i en skrift):</text:span> versibus incomptis a-et atrum transversis calamis signum, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja, stryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt på ngn (sätta fläck på, fläcka ned ngt):</text:span> sordes sententiis (judicum) a-ni non posse videbantur, C.; vitia sua alteri a., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlĭno</text:span>, lĭtum, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlĭnio</text:span>, 4.: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringsmörja, -smeta; rundt omkring bestryka, öfwersmörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med (inlägga i) ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> rundt omkring ngt:</text:span> Aegyptii mortuos cerā c-tos servant, C.; oculum pice; vas melle; fimo alveos, Pn.; vulnera aliqua re, Col.; vulneribus (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>) alqd, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om målningar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Botten-, grundstryka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (grunda):</text:span> non eminet pictura, in qua nihil c-tum est, Qu.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. om ett orent uttal:</text:span> simplicem vocis naturam pleniore sono c-ire, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlĭtio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerstrykning:</text:span></text:span> oris, Pn. - marmoribus operosa et in picturæ modum variata c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(färgläggning)</text:span> prætexitur, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭno</text:span>, litum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwersmörja, nedsudla:</text:span></text:span> coeno alqd, Pt.; crines pulvere, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭno</text:span>, lĭtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja, sminka:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ut-, öfwerstryka:</text:span></text:span> literæ, ceræ, C. ep. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Gramm.; Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭno</text:span>, lēvi, lĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Påstryka, -smörja, -smeta; smörja, utbreda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på l. öfwer ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">alicui rei</text:span>); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smörja, bestryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> venustatis color non fuco (<text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span>) i-tus, sed sanguine diffusus, C.; oculis collyria; aurum vestibus i-tum; chartis alqd; bruma nives Albanis agris, Hor.; viscum plumis; aurum tectis, Sen.; salsamenta nassis, Pn.; donum veneno i-tum, L.; navis bitumine i-ta, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span> n: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Påstrykning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭpĕrillĭno</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja ofwanpå; besmörja:</text:span></text:span> butyrum, Pn.; corpus aliqua re, Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlĭno</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mellanrummen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bestryka:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om byggnader: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fogstryka:</text:span></text:span> muros bitumine, Ct.; cæmenta luto, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om skrifter: stryka, skrifwa mellan ord l. rader, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerstryka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (interpolera, förfalska):</text:span> codex i-tus; tabulæ corruptæ et i-tæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblĭno</text:span>, lēvi (līvi), lĭtum, 3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblĭnio</text:span>, 4.: Col.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smeta, klena till</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">för; tillstoppa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwersmeta, -smörja, -stryka:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. mening:</text:span> amphoram, Cato; rimam, Mt.; stomachum dulcibus cibis, Pn.; homines unguentis; (tabula) coeno o-ta, C.; villa tabulis pictis o-ta; aves se visco, Varr.; gladius sanguine o-tus, Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerhölja, -lasta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">färga; fläcka, besudla, nedsmutsa:</text:span></text:span> crebræ exornationes o-tam reddunt orationem; facetiæ o-tæ Latio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med latinsk färg);</text:span> se parricidio, externis moribus; vita libidine o-ta; omnia sunt stultitia o-ta, C.; atris carminibus alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sätta fläck på någons rykte),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>b. os alicui o-re = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">draga wid näsan,</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭno</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭnio</text:span>), lĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerstryka, smörja:</text:span></text:span> ulcera pice, Col.; sanguinis crudelitate p-tus (Chrysogonus), C. (inc. l.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælĭno</text:span>, lĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framtill bestryka:</text:span></text:span> villas tectorio, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭno</text:span>, lēvi, lĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upptaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öppna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt tillsmetadt, tillstoppadt, förwaradt:</text:span> dolia relevi, Ter.; sedem angustam servataque mella apes r-unt, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublĭno</text:span>, lēvi, lĭtum, 3.: (-nītus, Pt.): <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stryka inunder; bottenstryka (grunda); lätt belägga, bestryka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt:</text:span> bracteis argentum vivum; alqd atramento, Pn.; materiam calce <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rappa),</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>b. s. os alicui = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">narra, draga wid näsan,</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Subterlĭno</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Undertill bestryka:</text:span></text:span> plantas ægri, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭperlĭno</text:span>, lĭtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja, besmörja ofwanpå, -till:</text:span></text:span> radix bibitur, aliquando s-itur, Pn.; alqd aliqua re, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Linos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Linus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linquo,</text:span> līqui, (lictum), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna, öfwergifwa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men. = gå ifrån, lemna qwar l. i sticket:</text:span> terram, quam servaverat, C.; patriæ fines et dulcia l-imus arva; l-i pollutum hospitium, Vg.; l-da tellus et domus et placens uxor, Hor.; herum in obsidione, Pt.; l-itur ut - = restat ut -, Lucr. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta fara l. wara</text:span> (= omittere): l-amus igitur hæc -, C.; dona præsentis cape lætus horæ et l-e severa; nil intentatum liquēre, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. (= deficio) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om krafter, andedrägt, medwetande: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swika, öfwergifwa:</text:span></text:span> l-i animo; l-ente spiritu, animo, Ct.; nervi l-unt alqm; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swimma),</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlinquo</text:span>, līqui, lictum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwergifwa, swika) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swika sin pligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förbindelse; fela</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (egentl. men ej ensamt, af underlåtenhet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förgå sig, förbryta sig:</text:span></text:span> miles in bello propter metum hostium, C.; Prisci Latini adversus populum Romanum fecerunt, d-runt, L.; d. in aliqua re, erga alqm, Pt.; artem vivendi professus d-it in vita; facilius in aliis videmus, si quid d-itur, C.; eorum auctoritate Calpurnius ea, quæ d-isset, munita fore sperabat; iracundiā d. alqd, Sa.; paulum d-it amicus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlictum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fel, förseelse, förbrytelse:</text:span></text:span> quæ parva d-a sunt, ab iis est diligentius declinandum; oportebat d-o dolere, correctione gaudere; quo d. majus est, eo poena tardior, C.; d-a reprehendere, corrigere; d-i conscientia; d-i gratiam facere, Sa.; d. committere, Cs., N.; d-a majorum immeritus lues, Romane -; pati d-a alicujus; defendere d., quam vertere, malle; sunt d-a tamen, quibus ignovisse velimus, Hor.; d-a fateri, Ov.; d. morte luere, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwergifwande):</text:span> solis d. (= defectus), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">solförmörkelse,</text:span> Pn. - id mihi et parentis et libertatis d-o siet (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förlust af),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭquus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭcuus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Felande, felaktig:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlinquo</text:span>, līqui, lictum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna qwar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid bortgående) l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">efter sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ej taga med):</text:span> alicui arrhaboni alqd, Ter.; fratrem in provincia, C.; præsidium castris; alqm ad exercitum; hostem post se, Cs.; alqm custodem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till waktare)</text:span> pontis r., N.; quid secum ferrent, quid r-rent, obliti, L.; paucis r-tis vela damus; cui parvus Iulus, cui pater et conjunx - r-or?, Vg.; fugi r-ta non bene parmula; porcis alqd comedendum r-re; mihi turpe r-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bli efter),</text:span> Hor.; scutum r-isse præcipuum flagitium, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid sin död </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna efter sig, efterlemna:</text:span></text:span> S. Peducæus, qui hunc filium r-iquit; heredem aliquem testamento; alqd testamento alicui r.; filio patrimonium satis amplum; æs alienum; monumentum audaciæ suæ; id Cato scriptum r-quit, C.; liberos; heredium, regnum filio; scriptum aliquid; famam sui, N.; quantam (majores) rempublicam r-rint, disseram; pater nos duos fratres r-quit, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna öfrig;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bli öfrig, återstå:</text:span></text:span> aliquantum spatii in medio r-tum est; ne libertatis quidem retinendæ spes r-itur; locum vituperandi, precibus r.; ei nihil r-itur nisi fuga; r-itur, ut - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det återstår att göra eller den utwägen återstår, att -);</text:span> r-itur, ut tria sint genera causarum (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den slutsatsen är den enda, s. kan göras);</text:span> quid tu Epicuro r-isti <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwad förtjenst har du medgifwit),</text:span> nisi te intelligere, quid dicat?, C.; nihil nobis r-runt præter miseram animam; Catilina se cum paucis r-tum vidit, Sa.; r-batur una per Sequanos via, Cs.; nihil est tibi, amice, r-tum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af dig lemnadt ogjordt),</text:span> Vg.; nihil deorum honoribus r-tum (esse), quum se templis et effigie numinum coli vellet, T.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna något</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ngn = lemna ngn i besittning af ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">medgifwa, öfwerlåta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt någon:</text:span> hostibus cruentam victoriam r., Sa.; urbem direptioni, C.; facultatem sui colligendi alicui r., Cs.; fana apris habitanda r., Hor.<text:line-break/>5. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = gå ifrån ngn l. ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwergifwa;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lemna i sticket:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. mening:</text:span> r-ta urbe rura peragro, C.; Italiam, N.; Britanniam; domos; loca superiora, Cs.; domos tectaque, L.; signa, Sa.; Ilio r-to; tectum domini r.; color ossa r-it, Hor.; fessos ventus cum sole r-it; calor ossa, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna, låta wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett tillstånd:</text:span> alqd in medio r.; alqm in egestate, alqm insepultum r., C.; hoc ut incompertum in medium r-am, T.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna, öfwergifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">låta wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fara; swika; afstå från</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">upphöra med, sätta åsido, lemna oberördt, ohämnadt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. d.:</text:span> obsessionem oppidi; an hæc persequeretur, vivendi artem r-ret?; r. amicitiam, studium, spem, consuetudinem, jus suum; nomen oratoris ei r-dum est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(afstå från anspråk på);</text:span> causam communem non solum r., sed etiam prodere; quis est, qui vim - factam r-i putet oportere?; injurias suas r.; r-amus hæc, quæ habent cognitionem facilem, C.; omnibus rebus r-tis, Cs.; negotia r.; amata r-re pernix, Hor. γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">medgifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (m.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc. c. inf.</text:span>): Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwergifwande:</text:span></text:span> reipublicæ r. ac desperatio, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlictus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span> -ui: r-ui esse = relinqui, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åsidosättas:</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭquus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(relicuus, Pt.; <text:line-break/>rellicuus, Lucr.), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfrig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">factiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfrig, öfwerblifwen, återstående:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> detractis de homine sensibus r-i nihil est; quod fanum est, in quo ullum ornamentum r. sit?; quid est huic r-i?; hos belli calamitas r-os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lemnat öfr.)</text:span> fecit; nihil alicui r-i facere de bonis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lemna öfrigt för ngn);</text:span> nullum officii onus r-um facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lemna ouppfylld);</text:span> r-um est, ut scribam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(återstår att -),</text:span> C.; nihil r-i facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(försöka allt);</text:span> nihil est ei r-i; r-um facere alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lemna ngn öfrig</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i lifwet),</text:span> Cs.; vix decima parte r-a; nisi vindicatum erit in noxios, quid r-um erit, nisi ut illis, qui id fecere, obedientes vivamus?, Sa.; quotus quisque r., qui rempubl. vidisset?, T. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭquum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rest, återstod:</text:span></text:span> r. persolvere; addendo et deducendo videre, quæ summa r-i fiat; breve vitæ r-um, C.; solliciti r. noctis egere, L. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭqua</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rester</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (restantier), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">återstod</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en skuld:</text:span> maxime me angit ratio r-orum meorum; superioris lustri r-a, C.; colonorum r-a, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: öfrig = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillkommande, framtida:</text:span></text:span> non de r-a et sperata gloria laboramus, sed de parta dimicamus; spe r-æ tranquillitatis <text:soft-page-break/>præsentes fluctus fugio, C.; r-am ætatem a re publica procul habere decrevi, Sa.; in tempus r-um, in r-um, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för framtiden,</text:span> C., Cs., Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfrig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i motsats till den l. de nämnde delarne af ett helt eller arterna af ett slag) (den, de andre):</text:span> de tribus r-is (officii fontibus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mots. till</text:span> prudentia) latissime patet -; his sententiis nihil post mortem pertinere ad quemquam potest: r-orum sententiæ spem afferunt -; in quibusdam neque pecuniæ modus est - nec libidinum - nec r-arum cupiditatum; natura formam nostram r-amque figuram, in qua esset species honesta, eam posuit in promptu; (sapientem) in r-a Græcia neminem, Athenis unum fuisse accepimus; de r-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för öfrigt, hwad det öfriga beträffar)</text:span> tibi persuadeas -; de r-o nostra culpa erit, si non - impetraverimus, C.; hoc est miserior Sequanorum fortuna, quam r-orum, quod -, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭquiæ</text:span> <text:line-break/>(relliquiæ), ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwer-, qwarlefwor; lemningar, återstod,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> det som återstår af l. efter ngt, det s. någon lemnat öfrigt (om concreta och abstracta, sakliga och personl. subject):</text:span> r. coenarum; cibi r., quas natura respuit (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">excrement);</text:span> C. Marii apud Anienem sitæ r. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lik);</text:span> pristinæ fortunæ r. miseræ et afflictæ; r. conjurationis, flagitiorum; avi r-as persequi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fullborda, hwad han lemnat öfrigt),</text:span> C.; r. exercitus, Cs.; cladis r. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter nederlaget),</text:span> L.; Xerxes magnas habebat copiarum r-as, N.; tenues pristini moris, Ct.; colere suorum r-as; Troes r. Danaûm atque immitis Achilli (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. desse lemnat öfrige),</text:span> Vg.; accisæ (exercitus Variani) r.; r-as alienas et suorum humo tegere, T.; r-as legere, mari mergere, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭquo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlĭquor</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">restera med en skuld:</text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dērĕlinquo</text:span>, līqui, lictum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> utan hjelp, wård (på bar backe, i sticket), utan afseende; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwergifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> destituo): habere aliquam pro d-ta, Pt.; d. arationes; seremus in inculto d-toque solo; ab omni fortuna et spe d-tus, C.; Jugurtham Massinissa, quod ortus ex concubina erat, privatum d-erat, Sa.; navis ab æstu d-ta, Cs.; castra d., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dērĕlictio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwergifwande, swikande:</text:span></text:span> communis utilitatis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dērĕlictus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span> ui: habere rem d-ui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwergifwa),</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Linteamen, -tearius, -teatus, -teo, -teolum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Linteus, Linum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linter,</text:span> tris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.,</text:span> rarius <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ekstock, båt, färja:</text:span></text:span> l-bus convehere alqd aliquo, C.; l. incitata remis, Cs.; (mulā ligatā) l-em non procedere sentimus, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tråg, ho:</text:span></text:span> arbore cavare l-es, Vg.; plenæ in l-bus uvæ, Tib.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lintrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Färjkarl:</text:span></text:span> Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lintrĭcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līnum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lin:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott ss. ämne:</text:span> reticulum tenuissimo l-o, C.; l-i inopia et ejus usus inscientia, Cs.; l-i seges, Vg.; l-i semen; l. tundere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bryta);</text:span> pectere, carminare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(häckla);</text:span> nere, in fila ducere; l. crudum, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt, som är af lin, ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tråd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarmed bref förseglas; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">linneduk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-</text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">klädnad; segelduk; tåg; nät, mettråd:</text:span></text:span> tabellæ proferebantur, l. incidimus, C.; l-o velari, Vg.; l-a tendere, Sen.; vela deducere torto l-o; nodosa tollite l-a (venatores), Ov.; pelago trahere l-a, Vg.; piscator moderatur arundine l., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līnāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linneduk, -klut; linneskaf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (charpie):</text:span> Pn., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līneus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är af lin, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linne-:</text:span></text:span> vincula, Vg.; vestis, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf:</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līnea</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linnetråd:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> gallinæ pedem longā l-ā ligare, Col.; l-æ plagarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trådar, maskor i nät),</text:span> Pn.; l. margaritarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(perlband),</text:span> Ulp. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Metref:</text:span></text:span> mittere l-am, Pt.; l. trahit piscem, Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rättesnöre, täljetråd</text:span></text:span> (fabrorum): perpendiculo et l-ā uti, C. - ad l-am, rectis l-is, rectā l-ā ferri, demitti, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(snör-, lodrätt),</text:span> C., Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linie:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i geometrien och målarekonsten m. m.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linie, streck, drag:</text:span></text:span> l-am cinere ducere; l-æ, quæ emittuntur e centro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(radier),</text:span> Pn.; velut primis l-is designare alqd <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl. = göra utkast till ngt);</text:span> nulla dies sine l-ā, Qu. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gränslinie, -rand, -streck:</text:span></text:span> peccare est tamquam transsilire l-as, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om den </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rand,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarigenom målet på rännarbanan betecknades:</text:span> alba l. in utrumque podium producta, Cassiod. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf bildl.:</text:span> mors ultima l. rerum, Hor.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om de </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Streck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ränder,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarigenom de olika åskådareplatserna på circus l. theatren åtskildes:</text:span> cogit nos l. jungi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om grannar på circus),</text:span> Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf bildl.:</text:span> extremā l-ā amare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i sista rummet, ss. den minst gynnade)</text:span> haud nil est, Ter. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slägtlinie:</text:span></text:span> ascendens; descendens, Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līneālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af linier:</text:span> ambitus, Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līneāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.: pictura, Pn.; ratio, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līneo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med rättesnöre teckna, upprita; draga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (streck):</text:span> navis bene l-ta, Pt.; radios, Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līneāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linie:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mathematisk mening:</text:span> in geometria l-a, formæ, intervalla; l. est longitudo latitudine carens, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i konsten:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Teckning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i motsats till uttryck, färgläggning m. m.:</text:span> æris temperatio et operum l-a, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> Catonis l-is, nisi pigmentorum flos et color, nihil defuit, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ansigtsdrag:</text:span></text:span> l-a oris; l-a hominis, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.</text:span> animi l-a pulcriora sunt quam corporis, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collīneo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Collīnio), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kasta i rak rigtning; kasta rätt; rigta:</text:span></text:span> sagittam, hastam aliquo; est, qui totum diem jaculans non aliquando c-et?, C.; oculos aliquo, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīneo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra en grundteckning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af något, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i utkast:</text:span> imaginem in pariete carbone, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līneŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten linie:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līnĭger</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linneklädd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om Isis’ prester):</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af linnewäf, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linne-:</text:span></text:span> vestis, C.; thorax, N.; libri, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linnewäf, -tyg:</text:span></text:span> colare alqd l-o, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(torke-kläde), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Näsduk:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Segel:</text:span></text:span> non sunt tibi integra, Hor.; certum est dare l-a retro, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linneduk:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: negotiatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(linnehandel),</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lärftskrämare:</text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linneklädd:</text:span></text:span> L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Linnewäfware:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Linteŏlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Litet linkläde:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭnus <text:line-break/>(Lĭnos), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ĭpăra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en ö.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lĭpăræus, <text:line-break/>Lĭpărensis, <text:line-break/>Lĭpărītānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lippus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ögon: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rinnande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. har rinnande, inflammerade ögon; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">surögd, ögonsjuk:</text:span></text:span> oculus, Pt.; l. inungit collyria oculis; inungitur, Hor.; oculi acres, quamquam l-i, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck:</text:span> tua mala l-us pervides, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om andra ting: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Drypande:</text:span></text:span> ficus, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lippio</text:span>, 4.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hafwa rinnande ögon, ögoninflammation:</text:span></text:span> C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> fauces fame, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lippĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ögonsyra, -inflammation:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlippĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket surögd:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭqueo,</text:span> (līqui), lĭcui, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">flyta, wara flytande):</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> blott i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">part. præs.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flytande, klar:</text:span></text:span> fluvius; vina lĭquentia fundam, Vg.; res l-tes Varr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. (blott i 3 person. och blott med pronominalt subj.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det är klart, tydligt; säkert</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med omwänd construction: hafwa l. hafwa kommit till wißhet om ngt -); spec. i domstols-språket: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">det är utredt, utrönt:</text:span></text:span> omnia nunc l-ent; de hac re mihi non l-et, Pt.; si quid habes, quod l-eat, scribe; Protagoras negat se habere de diis, quod l-eat; - cui neutrum licuerit, nec esse deos nec non esse, C.; judices non l-re, sibi l-re dixerunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquĕfăcio</text:span>, fēci, factum, 3., <text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med.) -</text:span> fīo, factus, fĭĕri: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra flytande, bringa till smältning, smälta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> omentum pingue in flamma l-ens, Catl.; (nix) calore l-ta; æra legum l-ta, C.; sevum l-fieri, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Komma att försmälta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">att domna, täras bort:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -</text:span> quos nullæ lætitiæ languidis l-unt voluptatibus, C.; pectora curis l-fiunt, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭquĕfactus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samman-, uppsmält:</text:span></text:span> venenum in potione, C.; glacies, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illĭquĕfactus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insmält,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ljuft) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inströmmande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> influo): ad perfundendum animum tamquam i-æ voluptates, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquesco</text:span>, lĭcui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälta</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bli flytande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> nix, L.; cera igni; chalybs fornace, Vg. - aqua <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(klarar sig),</text:span> Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälta bort; swinna hän, domna hän:</text:span></text:span> fortuna, Ov.; voluptate l-re et fluere mollitiā, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭquesco</text:span>, līqui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bli flytande, smälta:</text:span></text:span> alqd in pice, Col.; aurum c-isset, Varr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> lacrimis, Front.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭquesco</text:span>, lĭcui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälta upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bort; försmälta, -rinna:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> nix d-uit, Ov.; poma cum musto, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> alacritate futili gestientem d., C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Condēlĭquesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Alldeles försmälta:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlĭquesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smälta ut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utpressas):</text:span> olea, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flytande, rinnande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om watten) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">spegelklar:</text:span></text:span> aqua bona et l-a, Cato; mel; fontes, Vg.; odores, Hor.; venter, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för öga l. öra </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar, ren, skär:</text:span></text:span> āer, Vg.; tempestas cæli l-sima, Lucr.; color; vox, Hor. - lux, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinne, känslor, stämning o. d.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ren, ogrumlad, ostörd, lugn:</text:span></text:span> voluptas, C., Lucr.; homo; animus l. et tranquillus, Pt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sinnelag: klar = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ärlig:</text:span></text:span> ita prompta fides, ut, quidquid inde haurias, purum et l-um te haurire sentias, C.; parum l-a fides, Val.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om framställning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar, ren</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (correcthet i förening med ledighet och tydlighet):</text:span> oratio pura sic, ut nihil l-ius; genus dicendi non l-um, fusum, profluens, sed exile, aridum, concisum, minutum, C.; scriptor vemens et l. puroque simillimus amni, Hor.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klar = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tydlig, utrönt, utredd:</text:span></text:span> veritas ad l-um explorata, L.; res ad l-um perducta, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klart:</text:span></text:span> serenus, Gell.; l-ius cernere, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquĭdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klarhet:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquĭdiuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet mera klar:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquĭdo</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rent ut; bestämdt; med säkerhet:</text:span></text:span> dicere; negare, C.; judicare l-ius de aliqua re, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭquĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket klar:</text:span></text:span> Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra flytande, bringa till smältning, smälta;</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">medialt = smälta):</text:span> guttæ l-tæ ardore solis, C. poēt.; nives l-antur, Mt.; tela l-re, Luc.; alvum, Ce. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klara, rena</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (distillera):</text:span> vina l-es, Hor.; mella l-ta, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smältbar:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sås, lake:</text:span></text:span> Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smältning:</text:span></text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭquo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aftappa; klara:</text:span></text:span> vinum in alia vasa d., Col.; turbida, Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.</text:span> (delico, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förklara sig; yppa:</text:span></text:span> quid istic sibi vult sermo? d-ca, Titin.; tu me dixisse d-ces?, Pt. Mil. 844.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlĭquo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Låta utströmma:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klara, rena:</text:span></text:span> vinum, Col.; fons e-tus, Sen.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: om toner: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utgjuta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (framqwillra):</text:span> plorabile alqd, Ps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭquor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flytande tillstånd:</text:span></text:span> frigus et calor, concretio et l., C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flytande ämne wätska</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (watten, win o. s. w.):</text:span> perlucidi amnium l-es, C.; de patera fundere novum l-em, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līquor</text:span>, līqui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flyta; wara flytande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> atro l-untur sanguine guttæ, Vg.; līquentia mella, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förgå, swinna hän:</text:span></text:span> res (familiaris), Pt.; ætas, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭquiæ</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭciæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ränna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (takränna, afloppsdike):</text:span> Col., Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collĭciāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: tegula, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭquia</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Dēlĭcia), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Takränna:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭciāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A</text:span>:. tegula, Cato. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlĭciātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedd med -:</text:span> Paul. Diac.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlĭquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflöde:</text:span></text:span> Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭquĭrītĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (v. gr., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. söt rot): lakrits:</text:span> Veg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wret, rygg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bredare), mellan fåror på en åker (jfr</text:span> porca): Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līrātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wretwis, i fåror:</text:span> serere, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mylla</text:span></text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerplöja en redan besådd åker:</text:span> tabula aratro annexa, operiente semina, Varr.; Pn.; = delirare, Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wriden, tokig, afwita, fånig, fjollig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i synn. om gamle, s. gå i barndom (se</text:span> deliratio) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. om wanwett ss. slöhet och löjlighet):</text:span> senex d.; anus d-a, C.; mulier dolosa senem d-um temperat; d. amensque; scriptor d. inersque; mater d-a, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yra:</text:span></text:span> Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wika ur (fåran) spåret:</text:span> Aus.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fara will; taga fel; wara wriden, fjollig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gå i barndom); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">yra; handla tokigt; galnas:</text:span></text:span> Empedocles an Stertinii d-at acumen?, Hor.; senex, Ter.; d-re et mente captum esse, C.; mentis compote matre filius d-at, Su.; morbo d-re, Lucr.; quidquid d-ant reges, plectuntur Achivi, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīrāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tokighet, galenskap</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i concret men.):</text:span> d-a loqui, Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlīrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tokighet, fjollighet:</text:span></text:span> senilis stultitia d. appellatur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perdēlīrus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket afwita</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tokig:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>īris, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Latium.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līrœ</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr.</text:span> λῆροι, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dumheter):</text:span> Pt. Poen. 1. 19.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līs,</text:span> lītis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>stlis, Qu.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twist:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> l. l-em parit, serit, Pt.; philosophi in l-bus ætates conterunt, C.; inter aliquos componere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bilägga)</text:span> l-es, Vg., Hor.; l-ium cupidos animos lenit albescens capillus, Hor.; verba generant l-em, Qu.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rättegångstwist, proceß, sak, mål:</text:span></text:span> l-es sequi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(söka, kasta sig i),</text:span> Ter.; l-es privatæ, l-es capitis; l-es habere cum aliquo; l-bus distineri; bona sua l-e repetere; l-em alicui intendere; l-em inferre in alqm; l-em obtinere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(winna);</text:span> l-em amittere, perdere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förlora);</text:span> l-em orare (= causam dicere), C.; pendens l.; adhuc sub judice l. est; judice aliquo secantur l-es, Hor.; ire in l-em, Ov.; l. hereditaria; l-em suscipere, Qu. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mer och mindre metonymiskt = den sak, hwarom processen föres, det omtwistade, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twisteämnet:</text:span></text:span> alienæ l-is interceptor; in suam rem l-em vertere, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">isynn. i uttrycket:</text:span> æstimare l-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om rätten) = bestämma </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">pliktsumman,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. den anklagade skall erlägga: deraf</text:span> æstimata lis = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plikt, böter, skadestånd:</text:span></text:span> l-es severe æstimatæ, C.; Miltiades pecuniā multatus est eaque l. L talentis æstimata est; l-em æstimatam populo solvere non potuit, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twista, träta, disputera; processa:</text:span></text:span> inter se de aliqua re, Pt.; cum aliquo pro aliquo; mira sum alacritate ad l-dum; l-re se simulans blanditur (callidus assentator); l. et turpibus jndiciis conflictari, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĭgātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">En twistande,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> proceßförande:</text:span> Qu., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĭgātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Proceß:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĭgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twist, träta:</text:span></text:span> l. nascitur; l. contrahere cum aliquo, Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĭgiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trätsam, twistesjuk, proceßlysten:</text:span></text:span> homines l-i; loquaciter l-us, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Full af twister:</text:span></text:span> disputatio satis l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(”polemisk”),</text:span> C.; fora, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omtwistad, twistig, stridig:</text:span></text:span> prædiolum parvum et l-um, C.; ager, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlītĭgo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Häftigt träta, gräla:</text:span></text:span> tumido ore, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>issus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Dalmatien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Litamen, -tatio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lito.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lītĕra</text:span> <text:line-break/>(littera), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bokstaf;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skrift, skrifter, literatur:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bokstaf;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(alphabet), bokstäfwer; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skrift</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ord):</text:span> l-am (<text:span text:style-name="T1">K</text:span>) ad caput (calumniatori) affigere; nolo l-as exprimi putidius, nolo obscurari; lenis appellatio l-arum; formæ unius et viginti l-arum; maximæ, minutæ l-æ; nomen scribitur sex l-is; in consilio ac mente scriptoris, non in verbis ac l-is vis legis posita est; aucupia verborum et tendiculæ l-arum; ad l-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(efter orden);</text:span> l-is consignare, mandare, commendare alqd <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skriftligen uppteckna);</text:span> scire l-as <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kunna läsa och skrifwa);</text:span> hic liber non parum continet l-arum, C.; tabulæ Græcis l-is confectæ, Cs.; vellem nescire l-as, Su.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. och oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. (<text:span text:style-name="T1">sing.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Handstil:</text:span></text:span> similitudo tuæ l-æ, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> =<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrifwelse, bref</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tills. med sådana verb, s. skicka, få o. dyl.):</text:span> l-as ad alqm scribere; conficere; consignare; obsignare; ad alqm mittere; (tabellario) dare; l-as alicujus elicere, exspectare; l-æ afferuntur, veniunt alicui ab aliquo; per l-as queri, invitare alqm; l-as alicujus, ab aliquo accipere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(få);</text:span> l-as aperire, C.; l-as resolvere, L.; l-as reddere, remittere alicui; l-is comperire; l-is certiorem facere alqm; ex l-is scire; liber l-arum missarum et allatarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(brefl. conceptbok);</text:span> unæ, binæ l-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett, twå bref);</text:span> l-æ humanæ, jucundæ, suaves, facetæ, disertæ, amabiles, inanes, frigidæ, acerbæ, minaces, odiosæ, veteres, recentes, C.; l-is colere alqm; has l-as Ephoris tradidit, N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">officiella </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrifter,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> offentliga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">handlingar:</text:span></text:span> l-as publicas in ærario conditas proferre; l-æ societatis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ett bolags):</text:span> l-æ publicanorum, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrifter</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett wißt språk; ett folks </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">språk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i skrift); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">literatur:</text:span></text:span> eruditi Græcis l-is, contemnentes Latinas; abest historia l-is nostris; genus hoc scriptionis nondum satis l-is nostris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på wårt språk)</text:span> illustratum est, C.; Græcas l-as discere, Sa.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">literatur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. studiigren</text:span> (γράμματα, γραμματική), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">språkstudier, grammatik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till sina 2 delar:</text:span> recte loquendi scientia et poētarum enarratio, Qu.), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">philologi:</text:span></text:span> loquendi elegantia, quamquam expolitur scientiā l-arum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(grammatik; wetenskapliga språkstudier),</text:span> tamen augetur legendis oratoribus et poētis; alterum (i. e. Latine loquendi facultas) traditur l-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(språkläran)</text:span> et doctrina puerili; ad dialecticam adjunxit l-arum scientiam et loquendi elegantiam; hoc studium l-arum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(öfwersättning af</text:span> γραμματική), quod profitentur ii, qui vocantur grammatici; quid tibi - l-æ, quid historia poētarumque evolutio voluptatis affert?; homo non solum philosophiā, sed etiam l-is perpolitus; primo pauca de l-is (collocuti sumus), deinde (de philosophia), C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skrifter, böcker, literatur;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">literära, bokliga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lärda sysselsättningar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">studier; bokwett, literär bildning, beläsenhet:</text:span></text:span> nulla ars l-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ur böcker)</text:span> sine interprete percipi potest; jampridem tuæ conticuerunt l-æ; illæ l-æ conticuerunt, senatoriæ et forenses; ea studia, quæ in reconditis artibus et in quadam varietate l-arum versantur; l-as nescire <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sakna studier);</text:span> l-is studere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(studera);</text:span> l-is deditus; l-is dare operam; l-arum cupidus, studiosus, expers, rudis; l-is doctus, politus, eruditus; erant in eo plurimæ l-æ, neque eæ vulgares, sed reconditæ; homo non communium l-arum, C.; l-as amare, attingere; l-is tempus dare; Hannibal non nihil tempus tribuit l-is. Nam aliquot ejus libri sunt Græco sermone confecti, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för läsning och skrifning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Elementar-:</text:span></text:span> ludus, Pn., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">underwisning i elementen:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lärare i de första elementen af språkkunskap; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språklärare, skolmästare;</text:span></text:span> Sulla l., Catl.; Cato <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i förklenande bet. om en berömd grammatiker),</text:span> Su.; alter l., alter literas sciens, id est, alter docens, alter doctus, Gell. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> Su. Gramm. 12).<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrātōria</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ord anförda af</text:span> Qu. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för att wisa suffixens olika betydelse.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrātūra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skriftsystem, alphabet; skrift:</text:span></text:span> Græca, T.; nitida, Cp.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skrifter, bokwäsen i rent materiel men.:</text:span> l. constat ex notis <text:soft-page-break/>literarum et ex eo, in quo imprimuntur notæ, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwersättning af</text:span> grammatice <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en literators fack):</text:span> Qu., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tecknad med bokstäfwer:</text:span> urna; homo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(brännmärkt),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. lärt att läsa, har gått i skola; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Studerad, boksynt, beläsen, (lärd,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till yrket), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">literärt bildad:</text:span></text:span> servi, C.; homines l-i et historici; eques Romanus non infacetus et satis l.; mediocriter l., C.; l-or, Sen.; l-simus, C. <text:line-break/>c. otium l-um, (quod in literis consumitur) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt studier egnadt</text:span>, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett sätt, s. wisar förmåga att läsa och skrifwa, eller studier: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språkriktigt: med lärdom, beläsenhet:</text:span></text:span> rationes scriptæ scite et l.; belle et l. dicta; perbene Latine loqui et l-ius quam ceteri, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Efter bokstafwen; med egentligt uttryck:</text:span></text:span> l. respondissem (me civem Romanum esse) an tacuissem?, C. (de Har. resp. VIII.).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītĕrŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten bokstaf:</text:span></text:span> minuta; vacillans, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Litet bref:</text:span></text:span> hoc l-arum ad te exaravi, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språk, språkliga studier:</text:span></text:span> Chrysippus (servus), quem ego propter l-arum nescio quid libenter vidi, discessit a puero, C.; (servus) l-is Græcis imbutus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. kan läsa litet grekiska),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Literatur, böcker, studier, skrifter:</text:span></text:span> eodem utor perfugio, quo tibi utendum censeo, l-is nostris; meæ l-æ oblanguerunt, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illītĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oskrifwen:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ostuderad, ej literärt bildad, olärd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om pers. och saker):</text:span> vir bonus et non i.; incidunt in sermone multa - nec i-a nec insulsa, C.; epistolæ i-æ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblītĕro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utstryka, utplåna:</text:span></text:span> nomina, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utplåna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ur minnet (sitt l. andras), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">minnet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bringa i förgätenhet:</text:span></text:span> quum voluntas eorum a me offensa esset, publici beneficii memoria privatam offensionem o-runt; id (in Cæsare) et tum ferendum fuit et maximis rebus, quas gessit, o-tum est, C.; famam rei o-re, res o-ri in animo meo minime potest; vetustate, silentio res o-atur, L.; Cæsar advectus ad vicesimanos hoc illud tempus dicit o-dæ seditionis esse, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblītĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerlemnande åt glömskan, glömska:</text:span></text:span> æris (fundendi), Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlītĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket boksynt, studerad:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>īternum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Campanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Līternus, <text:line-break/>Līternīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭthostrōtus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med stenar belagd, med mosaikgolf:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭthostrōtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mosaikgolf:</text:span> Varr., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Liticen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lituus.<text:line-break/>Litig . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭto,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offra lyckligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">under goda förebud</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utifrån l. funna i sjelfwa offerdjuret); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">offra</text:span></text:span> (alicui deo) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">till behag; (med offer) försona;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om offret sjelf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lyckas; utfalla gynnsamt:</text:span></text:span> semper sacrificare, nec unquam l-re, Pt.; hostiā pulcherrime l.; aliis diis l-atur, aliis non l-atur; l-emus Lentulo (quasi deo), parentemus Catilinæ, C C.; egregie l.; l-ato instruunt aciem, L.; sanguine quærendi reditus animāque l-dum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till försoning måste offras)</text:span> Argolicā, Vg.; Jovi Otho non potuit l-re, Su.; molā salsā l-re, Pn.; sacra l., Ov.; victima non l-at, Mt.; sacrificio non l-ante, Su. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> statuæ (Domitiani eversæ) publico gaudio l-runt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fallit offer för),</text:span> Pn.; do lori alqd, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭtāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offer:</text:span></text:span> St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭtātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyckosam offring, offring med goda tecken:</text:span></text:span> hostiæ sine l-e læsæ; sacrificare hostiis usque ad l-em, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offra med lycklig utgång:</text:span></text:span> diis p-re; primis hostiis p-tum est, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Litor . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lītus.<text:line-break/>Littera <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med härledningar se</text:span> Litera.<text:line-break/>Littor . . ., Littus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lītus.<text:line-break/>Litura, -turarius, Lĭtus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lino.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lītus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(littus), ŏris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Strand:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid haf:</text:span> l. est, qua fluctus eluit; amoenitates orarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kust)</text:span> et l-um, C.; l-a - patriæ portusque relinquo; jacet ingens l-e truncus, Vg.; premere l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla in till);</text:span> l. maris obstrepentis Bajis; l-a gementis Bospori, Hor.; electio l-um (i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af landtställe wid kusten),</text:span> T.; insula (Capreæ) uno l-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sträcka af kusten)</text:span> aditur, Su.<text:line-break/>b. l. (Tiberis), Vg.; (fluminis), C.; (lacus), Catl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītŏrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: vota facere l-bus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(strandens, stranden skyddande)</text:span> diis, Catl.; mulli <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. gå wid stranden),</text:span> Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītŏreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är wid l. på stranden, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Strandens, strand-:</text:span></text:span> aves; ilex, Vg.; domus, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lītŏrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid stranden:</text:span> mare, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lĭtuus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokig staf</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. bars af</text:span> augures, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">augurs-staf</text:span></text:span> (incurvus et leviter a summo inflexus bacillus): l. insigne auguratus, C.; baculus sine nodo aduncus, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krökt blåsinstrument, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trumpet, stridslur:</text:span></text:span> l-o tubæ permixtus sonitus, Hor.; equus patitur l-um, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lĭtĭcen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> lituus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> cano <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Varro): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trumpetare:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Līveo,</text:span> ēre <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līvesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blifwa blågrå, blyfärgad:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> l-ent catenis brachia, Ppt.; l-ens plumbum, Vg.; pruna l-tia; crura, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blifwa afundsjuk, afundas, mißunna:</text:span></text:span> alicui, T.; rei, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līvēdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blånad:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blågrå, blå:</text:span></text:span> l-a brachia armis; l-i auctumni racemi; dens, Hor.; vada l-a (i. e. mare), Vg.; cortex, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afundsjuk, tadelsjuk,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (”gulblek”), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skadeglad:</text:span></text:span> invidi et malevoli et l-i, C.; l. et mordax; non ego - - tuos patiar labores carpere l-as obliviones, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līvĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blått:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līvĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något afundsjuk:</text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublīvĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blåaktig:</text:span></text:span> Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Līvor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blyfärg, swartblå färg, blånad:</text:span></text:span> corpus mortui l-e decoloratum, C.; oliva contrahit l-em; uvaque conspecta l-em ducit ab uva; tumidi l-es, Juv. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afund, mißunnsamhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (serdeles mot förtjensten), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tadelsjuka, förtal:</text:span></text:span> malevolentia et l-e impediuntur (ne de nobis vere judicent), C.; pascitur in vivis l., post fata quiescit; l. edax, Ov.; ambitionem scriptoris facile averseris: obtrectatio et l. pronis auribus accipiuntur, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>īvius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn, i literaturen berömdt genom</text:span> Livius Andronicus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Roms förste konstskald, och historieskrifwaren</text:span> T. Livius, † 17 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">e. Chr.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Līviānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Livor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Liveo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lix,</text:span> līcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lut:</text:span></text:span> Varr.; humor cineri admixtus, Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lixīvus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lixīvius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utlutad:</text:span></text:span> cinis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lixīvum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lixīvia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lixīvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lut:</text:span></text:span> Col., Pall.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lixa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Non. lixa = aqua, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf = wattenbärare; besl. med</text:span> elixus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fältkock, marketentare; troßfolk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid en armée:</text:span> l-æ modo profectus est consul sine insignibus, sine lictoribus, L.; ex l-is coquorum, pistorum scenicorumque major numerus fuit, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lixŭlæ,</text:span> ārum <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags kakor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringlor:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Loca . . ., Locellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under</text:span> Loculus), Locito, Loco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Locus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ŏcri, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grekiskt folk i Hellas och Stor-Grekland.</text:span><text:line-break/>Lŏcris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Locrernes land l. locrisk qwinna.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lŏcrensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Locul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Locus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŏcŭples,</text:span> ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besutten, förmögen, rik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (egentl. på fastighet enl.:</text:span> ex pecore et locorum possessionibus - pecuniosi et l-tes vocabantur, C.; l-tes dicebant loci h. e. agri plenos, Pn.):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor:</text:span> mulier copiosa et l.; l-ores et meliores cives; egens in l-em armatur, C.; prædā l-em fieri, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om samhällen, hus m. m.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik, wäl försedd; rik</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">dyrbar:</text:span></text:span> <text:soft-page-break/>civitas; domus; villa, C.; regio, N. - urbs l-sima, C.; l. frugibus annus, Hor.; - copiæ, C.; munera, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rik; rikt utrustad:</text:span></text:span> lingua Latina l-ior, quam Græca; Lysias oratione l.; rebus jejunior, l. oratio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> copiosus); l-ior hominum natura ad beate vivendum, quam deorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wittnes-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gill, wederhäftig (god</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. wittne l. borgen), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fullgiltig, trowärdig, pålitlig:</text:span></text:span> num l-ores quærimus testes?; testes l-simi; Pythagoras et Plato l-simi auctores; tabellarius l. et fidelis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcŭplēte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikt, rikligen:</text:span></text:span> Aur. V., Fr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcŭplēto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra besutten, rik; rikta,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wäl </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förse, utrusta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med (i yttre och inre bet.):</text:span> sapientem l-at ipsa natura; civitatem l.; fortunis, veste, argento alqm l., C.; Africam armis, equis, viris l.; prædā l-ri, N.; Scævolæ artem (juris scientiam) quum indotatam et incomptam videres, verborum eam dote l-asti et ornasti; eloquentiam graviorum artium instrumento l-asti, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŏcŭplēto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rikta:</text:span></text:span> se, Ter.; rem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rhetoriskt förstora, utsmycka),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŏcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> loci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> loca <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(se nedanföre): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställe, rum, plats, ort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: i nästan alla de swenska ordens bemärkelser, t. ex.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rummet, rymd) in abstr.; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rum, ställe, punkt, plats,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afs. på läge, afstånd, rörelse:</text:span> ubi corpus agitatur, l.; dum agitatur, tempus, ubi quidque consistit, l. (dicitur); l-a naturæ prima duo, cælum et terra, Varr.; naturalis motus omnium ponderum e regione inferiorem l-um petentium; medius l. mundi universi; stellæ infixæ certis l-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mots. till</text:span> errantes); ex inferiori l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid domstol ss. sakförare),</text:span> ex æquo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i senaten),</text:span> ex superiore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(från</text:span> rostra) loqui, C.; sepulcra distantia l-is, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (utrymme), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plats,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå ngt rymmes (får rum, plats):</text:span> gratiosi scribæ sunt in dando et cedendo l-o, C.; l. est et pluribus umbris, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plats</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på theater l. wid skådespel i allm.:</text:span> in magno consessu (seni) nusquam l. datus est, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställe, plats,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt l. med afseende på deß lämplighet för ngt, serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plats,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fast) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">terrain</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för en här, äfwensom deß </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ståndpunkt, ställning, position;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en fäktandes </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ställning, position:</text:span></text:span> ordo (est) compositio rerum aptis et accommodatis l-is; temporis, l-i, hominum rationem non habere; num hic l. non idoneus videtur?, C.; colloquio diem, tempus, l-um deligere, Sa., Cs.; urbi condendæ l-um eligere, L.; detur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(må bestämmas)</text:span> l. et hora; l-um immeritum inique causari; verba movere l-o, Hor.; Datis - non æquum l-um videbat suis; alienissimo sibi l-o, contra opportunissimo hostibus - conflixit, N.; l. pugnæ; l. adversus, idoneus, Sa.; l-um capere castris, Sa., L.; iniquitas, asperitas l-i, Sa.; l. communiendo præsidio idoneus; sua invicta arma nec l-o nec tempore ullo credebant sustineri posse, L.; in l-o manere, Sa.; l-o cedere, Sa., L., Cs.; l-um tenere; se l-o tenere; l-o pelli, Cs.; l-o dejici, Cs., Hor.; Catilina l-o depulsus est, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i geographisk men.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> loci, loca, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oftast = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ort, bygd, nejd, trakt, land, trakter,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt med afseende på belägenhet, naturskönhet l. naturbeskaffenhet; abstr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">läge</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (localitet):</text:span> l-i maritimi remoti a mari, plani montuosi, salubres pestilentes, culti inculti, celebres deserti; l-is ipsis delectamur, silvestribus etiam et <text:soft-page-break/>montuosis, in quibus diutius commorati sumus, C.; l-a (Galliæ) patentia et frumentaria, Cs.; Medi - proximos nostro mari l-os occupavere - - et quia sæpe temptantes agros alia, deinde alia l-a petiverant, semet ipsi Nomadas appellavere; Jugurtha oppidum Capsam aliosque l-os munitos amiserat; l-a amoena, arida, saltuosa; facies l-i, Sa.; Rætos l-a ipsa efferarunt; Evander - multis ante tempestatibus ea tenuit l-a (ubi Roma condita est), L.; l-os diversos pariter invadere, T.; l-us effusi late maris arbiter; gratus l. (Athenæ), Hor.; Helvetii l-i natura undique continentur; oppidum natura l-i muniebatur, Cs.; (Corinthum sustulerunt nostri, - credo -,) ne posset aliquando ad bellum faciendum l. ipse adhortari, C.; l-i majestas (Capitolii), L.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställe, plats, del</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en stad (offentlig plats), ett hus, tomt o. d.;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> loci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> loca: festivus l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om theatren),</text:span> Pt.; oppidum l-is communibus monumentisque decorare, C.; Romæ per omnes l-os conventusque de factis consulis agitari, Sa.; quidlibet indutus celeberrima per l-a vadit, Hor.; l. sacer, profanus; primus l. ædium, N.; l. circo designatus est; infima urbis l-a; multa sacrificia l-aque sacris faciendis dedicavit, L.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i mnemoniken:</text:span> loci = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställen, punkter:</text:span> iis, qui (memoriam) exercent, l-i capiendi sunt (multi, illustres, explicati, modicis intervallis) et ea, quæ memoria tenere volunt, - in his l-is collocanda, C.<text:line-break/>g. l-i muliebres, ubi nascendi initia consistunt, Varr., C.; l-a (id.), Lucr. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rum,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. ngt upptager l. s. lemnas åt l. står öppet för ngt, deraf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">möjlighet, tillfälle, anledning:</text:span></text:span> non est jam lenitati l.; sermoni obtrectatorum, defensioni, precibus, dubitationi l-um non relinquere; promerendi et referendi beneficii in alqm l-um habere; docendi l-um habere, C.; l. probandæ virtutis, Cs.; l. peccato est, Sa. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Punkt (stånd-, tid-punkt),</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå en sak befinner sig, deß </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ställning, belägenhet:</text:span></text:span> res est perbono, meliore, difficili, pejore l-o; rem deducere in eum l-um, ut - -; eo l-i est res nostra, C.; ibidem l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på samma punkt),</text:span> Pt.; in eum l-um ventum est, Cs.; quo res summa l-o?, Vg.; stare eodem l-o, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid:</text:span> interea l-i, postea l-i; adhuc l-orum, ad id l-orum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hittills, dittills),</text:span> Pt., Sa. - l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> in l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på sin plats) = i rätt tid, i </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tid:</text:span> in l-o laudo, Ter.; l-o quærere alquid, C.; dulce est desipere in l-o, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rum</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ordnings-), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plats, ställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ställe), s. ngn intager; spec.: (samhälls-) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ställning, stånd, rang:</text:span></text:span> tenere principem l-um in aliqua re, C. - l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> in l-o alicujus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> alicujus rei = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i någons ställe (ej: i stället för) = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">såsom, liksom:</text:span></text:span> l-o fratris diligere aliquem, Ter.; ille mihi in liberorum l-o esse debebat; in parentis l-o colere alqm; me habebat eodem l-o, quo generum; alqd l-o præmii petere; in l-o maledicti ponere; in l-o injuriæ numerare, C.; l-um amicitiæ tenere apud alqm; illi legationis principem l-um obtinebant; in pristinum l-um gratiæ restituere alqm, Cs.; - in summum l-um civitatis ascendere<text:span text:style-name="T1">;</text:span> homines inferiori l-o; esse equestri l-o; l-um honestissimum obtinere, C.; alqm l-o movere, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afsätta,</text:span> Cs.; tenere secundum l-um imperii; obtinere l-um legati apud alqm; habere alqm scribæ l-o, N.; natus, ortus honesto, nobili, summo, obscuro, infimo l-o, C., Cs., N.; <text:soft-page-break/>ignobilis l-o, T.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ställe, punkt i böcker l. i framställning (dock ej så, att ett från en förf. hemtadt uttryck, en mening, en tirad ss. sådan kallas en</text:span> l.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> e.): de amicitia alio l-o dictum est; erit jam proprius (de his rebus) dicendi l-us; hoc l-o (accusationis) si id tibi sumis -, C.; hoc l-o non prætereunda est Lacedæmoniorum gravitas, N.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Punkt, sida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af en sak, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">omständighet, hänseende; - punkt, hufwudpunkt, moment</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (afdelning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stycke</text:span></text:span> (membrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af innehållet) af ett ämne l. en wetenskap:</text:span> facillime ad res injustas impellitur, ut quisque altissimo ingenio est, gloriæ cupiditate. Qui l. est sane lubricus; alter est l. cautionis, ut - -; uno l-o melior est condicio externæ, quam domesticæ victoriæ; res multis l-is repudianda; huic l-o consulite, judices; l. longe et late patens; omnes philosophiæ l-os tractatos habere; tertius ille l. est relictus orationis de ambitus criminibus; - l-os quosdam (Platonis) transferre, C.; l-a jam recitata revolvimus irrevocati, Hor. - loci communes = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">allmänna ämnen, betraktelser; sentenser</text:span> (de virtute, de utilitate, de honore et cet.: C. de Or. III. §. 106 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ff.).</text:span> <text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. i topiken</text:span> = fons et sedes argumenti (τόπος) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">källa för bewiset, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bewisningspunkt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = de olika synpunkter l. sidor (ss. lagens, brukets, likhetens m. fl.), hwarifrån den sak, man förswarar l. bestrider, kan betraktas:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till stället hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Local:</text:span></text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcālĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">biljettförsäljare:</text:span> Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcārium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">betalning för rum (logis):</text:span> in tabernis, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Locellus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se under</text:span> Loculus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga, ställa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (gifwa ngt sin plats någorstädes) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (postera, anlägga): </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> statuam ad ædem Telluris; castra aliquo loco, C.; castra in campo, castellum in monte, Cs.; milites in munimentis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(posterar),</text:span> Sa.; castra a Fidenis M passuum l-at, L.; tu nunc Carthaginis altæ fundamenta l-as; urbem sedesque Teucrorum Antenor; regina se mediam l-vit, Vg.; in purpurea veste (hospitem) l-vit, Hor.; fundamenta in loco stabili, Pn.; milites in prora; equites ab utroque cornu; alqd super ripam, Ct.; in exordio l., Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> gifwa ngt en plats (factiskt l. i omdöme); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nedlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">egna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sina tankar, sitt arbete åt ngt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anwända; bewisa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn ngt (jfr</text:span> colloco); <text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span>: l-tum esse = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stödja sig på, bero på, bestå i</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">syn.</text:span> positum, situm esse): in amplissimo gradu dignitatis l. alqm; virtutem ita l-etis, ut ea excepta nihil amicitia præstabilius esse putetis; mentem, operam, studium, tempus in aliqua re, C.; benefacta male l-ta malefacta arbitror, Enn.; honos ut bene l-tus in ea familia mansit aliquamdiu; beneficia apud gratos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> b.), L.; civitas in fide Catonis l-ta est; prudentia est l-ta in delectu bonorum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> penningar på renta, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">låna:</text:span></text:span> nummum nemini l. queo, Pt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Borthyra, -arrendera;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bort-tinga, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-pakta, lemna på beting, bortauctionera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett arbete, en leverans o. d. åt den minstbjudande (mots. i båda fallen</text:span> conduco): fundum l. (colono); ædes alicui, Gell.; <text:soft-page-break/>opus faciendum; statuas demoliendas; cibaria anseribus (præbenda) l., C.; vestimenta exercitui, L.; cadavera (in sepulcrum) portanda conservus l-bat, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortgifta:</text:span></text:span> virginem alicui in matrimonium, Pt.; in matrimonio certo l. alqm, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställning:</text:span></text:span> verborum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Borthyrande; borttingande:</text:span></text:span> prædiorum, L.; porticus - l-e consulum reficiebatur, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Borttingare</text:span></text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den, för hwilken och på hwilkens bekostnad ngt göres:</text:span> funeris, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utarrendera:</text:span></text:span> agellum, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hyra bort:</text:span></text:span> domum, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga, ställa, sätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i ordning, på </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sin</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> plats: jfr</text:span> constituo, compono): <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> (virginem ancillæ) in lectum, Ter.; vasa in tabernam, Pt.; columnas e regione c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uppställa);</text:span> suo quidque in loco; in cubili alqm; tabernaculum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(upprätta)</text:span> in campo; tabulas bene pictas in bono lumine (Cæsar); insidias alicui, C.; turrim in muros; aurigæ currus ita c-ant, ut (pugnantes) receptum ad suos habeant, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en här, en trupp, skans o. d.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förlägga, uppställa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (postera), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lägga:</text:span></text:span> exercitum in hibernis; auxilia in summo jugo, legiones pro vallo; præsidium alicubi, Cs.; præsidia in litore, N.; classem Miseni, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bosätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (inlogera), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">insätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (upptaga) i (till) besittning af -:</text:span> se Athenis c.; comites apud hospites, C.; in agris (colonos), N.; Bojos in suis finibus Hædui c-nt, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ord: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställa, hopställa</text:span></text:span> (ut neve vastius diducantur neu concurrant aspere): C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i skick, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ordna:</text:span></text:span> rem militarem, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställa, försätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en wiß ställning:</text:span> rem alicujus in tuto c., Ter.; in hoc statu te fortuna; Herculem fama hominum, beneficiorum memor in numero deorum c-vit, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedlägga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anwända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">egna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ngt:</text:span> in doctrina omne studium suum; se totum in re exquirenda; patrimonium in salute reipublicæ; beneficia apud alqm c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bewisa ngn),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lägga, nedlägga, anse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ligga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">grunda, bygga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förhoppning) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">på;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> c-tum esse = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ligga:</text:span></text:span> acutarum graviumque vocum judicium natura in auribus nostris c-vit; spem rei in re c.; virtus ita summum bonum est, ut omnia ab altera parte c-ta vix minimi momenti instar habeant; hæc sunt posita ante oculos, c-ta in usu quotidiano, C. <text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. om penningar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsätta, nedlägga, placera, anwända:</text:span></text:span> pecuniam bene, in prædiis; pecuniæ non solum quærendæ, sed etiam c-dæ modus est, C.; pecunias fenore, Su.<text:line-break/>g. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortgifta:</text:span></text:span> nuptum aliquam, Pt., Cs.; aliquam alicui; aliquam in matrimonium, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.,</text:span> N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŏcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ställning; upp-, sammanställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (anordning):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. och i allm.:</text:span> videtur eadem; vis ordinis et c-is fore; siderum, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanställning, ordställning:</text:span></text:span> c-is est componere et struere verba sic, ut neve asper eorum concursus neve hiulcus sit, sed quadammodo coagmentatus et levis, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bewisens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sammanställning, anordning:</text:span></text:span> locorum: C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortgiftande:</text:span></text:span> in c-e filiarum juvare alqm, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uthyra, -arrendera, -auctionera:</text:span></text:span> fundum, C.; boves, Col.; funus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lemna på beting),</text:span> Pn. - gens Judæorum quam cara diis esset, docuit, quod est victa, quod e-ta (= in provinciæ formam redacta, vectigalia conducentibus publicanis), C. Flacc. cap. 28.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illŏcābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som ej kan blifwa bortgift:</text:span></text:span> virgo grandis, cassa dote, i., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Borthyra, borttinga:</text:span></text:span> operam, Js.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sätta framför:</text:span></text:span> Cap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlŏco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter borttinga:</text:span></text:span> Ulp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet ställe, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläck:</text:span></text:span> in cella l., Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet förwaringsrum, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Låda, skrin:</text:span></text:span> condi l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(likkista),</text:span> Pn.; l. argenteus, Js. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ett </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skrin, schatull, låda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med smårum, fack:</text:span> in ludum ibant suspensi lævo tabulam l-osque lacerto; nummos in l-os demittere, Hor.; eburni l-i, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcellus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet skrin l. afdelning; fack deraf:</text:span> Mt., Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcŭlāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förwaringsrum med fack l. hyllor (ss. fågelbur, bokhyllor):</text:span> Sen., Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afdelad i rum, fack:</text:span> arcula, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. har många smårum l. afdelningar:</text:span> putamen, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōcusta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gräshoppa:</text:span></text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags fisk:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Locut . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Loquor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōdix,</text:span> īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lakan</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (l. sängtäcke?):</text:span> sub l-e; de l-e paranda attonitus, Juv. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōdīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŏgos,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ord, tal:</text:span></text:span> Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">prat:</text:span></text:span> Ter. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">infall:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">berättelse, fabel:</text:span></text:span> Sen. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förnuft:</text:span></text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgăoedĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: metrum l-um = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">versmått, der lyriske och episke versfötter äro blandade med hwarandra (ss. i</text:span> metrum Alcaicum): Gramm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgĭca</text:span>, ae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgĭca</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tankelära, logik, logikens satser</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lat.</text:span> ratio disserendi): C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgīon</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgēon</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den delen af </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">scenen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarifrån skådespelaren talade</text:span> (pulpitum): Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rentekammare, räkenskaper,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> conjectur</text:span> C. Fam. V. 20. 6. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Klotz</text:span> edd).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏgŏdædălĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">talarekonst:</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōlīgo,</text:span> ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bläckfisk:</text:span></text:span> sucus nigræ l-is (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swart afund),</text:span> Hor., Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōlīguncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŏlium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en art ogräs, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klint, swingel, ren-repe:</text:span></text:span> infelix, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ansågs skadlig för ögonen:</text:span> careant l-is oculos vitiantibus agri, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf</text:span> l-o victitare, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en ögonsjuk:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏliāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af swingel:</text:span> farina, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏliārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för swingel:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ollius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lolliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lomentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ondĭnium, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Britannien (London).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Longæv . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Longus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Longănon,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(longano, <text:line-break/>longabo, <text:line-break/>longavo, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>):<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ändtarm:</text:span></text:span> Veg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Korf:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Longe, Longiloquium, Longinqu . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Longus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ongīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Cassia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Longipes, Longit . . ., Longiusculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Longus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Longobardi = Langobardi.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ongŭla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">volskisk stad.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Longulus, Longur . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Longus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Longus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.:</text:span> p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång, widsträckt:</text:span></text:span> Polio pede l-ior fuit, quam quisquam l-simus, C.; is est septem pedes l-us, Pn.; l-am viam conficere; alqd l-o intervallo interjecto videre, C.; agmen l-simum, Cs.; navis l-a, N.; area quattuor pedum l-a, Col.; hasta; vestis; atria; porticus; latus l-um; l-æ terræ, Vg.; l-i agri fluctus, Vg., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">poet. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aflägsen; widsträckt, lång,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om resor långt bort</text:span> (= longinquus): oræ, Sil.; l-a tibi exsilia et l-um maris æquor arandum, Vg.; l-um iter, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med afseende på tid: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = långwarig, s. förefaller lång, långsam; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">aflägsen,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> widsträckt</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om planer m. m., som afse lång (fram-)tid</text:span>]: l-um tempus, l-a ætas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lif);</text:span> horæ, quibus exspectabam, l-<text:soft-page-break/>æ videbantur; quia l-ius fiebat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det hade blifwit för långt, neml. att wänta),</text:span> per litteras eadem dixi; dixit nihil sibi fuisse l-ius, quam <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hans wäntan)</text:span> ut me videret, C.; mora; in l-orem diem differre alqd, Cs.; caritas soli, cui l-o tempore assuescitur, L.; l-a hiems; dies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tid):</text:span> collecta ex l-o rabies; in l-um causando dūcis amores, Vg.; l-a bella, militia, senectus, certamina; nec cultura placet l-or annua; dies l-a videtur opus debentibus; vitæ summa brevis spem nos vetat inchoare l-am; spe l-us <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. hoppas lång framtid)</text:span> senex, Hor.; Sejanus peritia morum Tiberii odia in l-um jaciens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sådde för framtiden);</text:span> l-um videbatur arcessere tormenta; princeps l-ā potentiā; experientia, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt om toner, stafwelser: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång, utdragen:</text:span></text:span> syllaba, C., Hor.; l-as in fletum ducit voces (bubo), Vg.; sonus continuo spiritu trahitur in l-um, Pn.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång, widlyftig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om framställning (i tal l. skrift) l. deß ämne, om den talande l. skrifwande o. d.:</text:span> ea ipsa, quæ dixi, sentio fuisse l-ora, C.; l. sermo; l-a oratio, C., Cs.; nolo l-us esse; l-ores hoc loco sumus, quam necesse est; l-um est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(det wore för w.)</text:span> et non necessarium commemorare, C.; l-o effata carmine, L.; l-a fabula; l-æ rationes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beräkningar);</text:span> l-a negotia clientium, Hor. - l-a est injuria, l-æ ambages, sed summa sequar fastigia rerum, Vg.; sermo l-ior, T. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Länge; för lång tid:</text:span></text:span> haud l. lætabere; l. vale, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longævus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: (ævum): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gammal, åldrig:</text:span></text:span> parens, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longævitas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longe</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: långt, långt borta, långt bort, långt ifrån:</text:span> l. abesse, abire, discedere; l. a domo bellare; est l. hinc in saltum; l. lateque peregrinari, C.; Belgæ a cultu provinciæ l-sime absunt; l-ius prodire; l. iis populi Romani fraternum nomen afuturum (dixit Ariovistus), Cs.; l. resonare; l. audire, Vg.; fuge l.; trans Tiberim l. cubat; l. sonans Aufidus, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm. i bildl. uttryck: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt, wida:</text:span></text:span> is errat l., Ter.; l. repetita defensio; sint sane tria illa genera bonorum, dum corporis (bona) jaceant humi, illa autem divina l. lateque se pandant cælumque contingant, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid verb, s. (oegentl.) utmärka ett afstånd, framskridande i tid:</text:span> tempus dandi muneris l. abest; l-ius vitam producere; l-ius provectus (in ætate), C.; tempus quam l-sime ducere, N.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andra förbindelser: i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">comp.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om fortwaro i tiden: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Längre;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">posit.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">långt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">långt efter:</text:span></text:span> l-ius anno in uno loco remanere non licet; l-ius tolerare famem, Cs.; l-ius eos debere non passus est, N.; l-ius morari, Hor.; non l.; non l. post = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ej länge l. långt derefter,</text:span> Vg., Gell. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Widlyftigt:</text:span></text:span> hæc dixi l-ius, quam instituta ratio postulabat, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt, wida,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i fråga om afstånd i qvalitet l. grad, (olikhet l. öfwerlägsenhet):</text:span> eæ facultates l. sunt diversæ; l. alia condicio; l. secus; l. multumque præstare; ab illa perfectione ipse l. absum, C.; l. aliud est virgines rapere, aliud pugnare cum viris; l. ante alias insignis pulcritudine, L.; l. dissimilis noto sucus; l. mea discrepat ratio; a vulgo (vulgi moribus) l. lateque remotus, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt wid</text:span> <text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T1">comp.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(långt, wida) och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">superl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ojemförligt, alra):</text:span> l. lateque maximus, l. lateque plurimum; l. princeps, C.; l. nobilissimus, Cs.; l. melior, Vg.; l. antiquissimum ratus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longĭlŏquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt tal, snack:</text:span></text:span> Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longinquus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt borta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fjerran warande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (l. boende); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">s. kommit långtifrån; aflägsen:</text:span></text:span> locus; hostis; homines, C.; loca l-ora; natio; civitas, Cs.; arva l-a, Hor.; legatio tam l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(så långt bort),</text:span> L.; mons l.; e l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på afstånd),</text:span> Pn.; (majestatis) major e l-o reverentia, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om tid: som är från en aflägsen tid, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gammal; långwarig, lång; aflägsen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om framtiden l. det, s. afser framtiden):</text:span> observatio, C.; monumenta, Pn.; sermo, T.; dolor; digressus, C.; morbus, L.; oppugnatio, Cs.; tantum ævi mutare valet l-a vetustas, Vg.; id l-um est <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för långt),</text:span> Pt.; spes l-i temporis, C.; spes l-a et sera, T.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i eg. men.:</text:span> linea, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longinque</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt borta:</text:span></text:span> Gell.; loqui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gammaldags? långtråkigt?),</text:span> Fr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longinquĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aflägsenhet:</text:span></text:span> loci, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långwarighet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lång tid:</text:span></text:span> dolorum l.; medicinam affert l. et dies, C. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Längd:</text:span></text:span> itineris, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlonginquus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket lång</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (långtråkig):</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longĭpes</text:span>, ĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långfotad:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långt, wida:</text:span></text:span> errare, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Längd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i rum och tid), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(widlyftighet):</text:span></text:span> linea est l. latitudine carens; l. itineris, diei, noctis, narrationis; syllabarum l-es, C.; per totam Italiæ l-em, L.; in l-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på längden)</text:span> patere, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longiuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något för lång:</text:span></text:span> versus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något (temligen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång:</text:span></text:span> iter sane l-um, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longŭrius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lång stång:</text:span></text:span> Cs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Longŭrio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lång karl (”stake”):</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblongus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Långlagd, aflång:</text:span></text:span> scutula, T.; figura, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblongŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlongus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket lång:</text:span></text:span> via; intervallum temporis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlonge</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. est (paratum) = perdiu: Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælongus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Owanligt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ofantligt lång:</text:span></text:span> hasta, L.; homo, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælongo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">göra -:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lopas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lepas.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŏquor,</text:span> lŏcūtus (lŏquūtus), 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sjelfwa talförmågan (jfr</text:span> Varr. l. l. VI. 56.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och med afseende på olikhet i tungomål och deras bruk, i uttal, uttryckssätt, ton</text:span>]:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bruka ett språk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uttrycka sig:</text:span></text:span> non conamur docere <text:soft-page-break/>eum dicere, qui l-i nesciat; hanc etiam pecudes, si l-i possent, dicerent voluptatem; Latine, Græce l.; poētas quasi alia quadam lingua l-tos non conor attingere; l. presse et leniter, bene, perbene, recte, male, inquinate, præclare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(allt med afs. på sjelfwa språkets renhet);</text:span> l-di consuetudo; l-di elegantia; (de elocutione) præcipitur primum, ut pure et Latine <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(språkriktigt)</text:span> l-amur, deinde ut plane et dilucide, tum ut ornate, post ut ad rerum dignitatem apte et quasi decore; populariter; vere et libere; ad veritatem; ad voluntatem alicujus l.; cum gravitate; asperius de aliquo; cum utrisque, ne inter se cupide agerent; pro aliquo; pro aliqua re, C.; quod in animo habet, l-do efferre, Varr.; suppliciter l.; cum alliquo; l-tus est pro his <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förde ordet),</text:span> Cs.; facete, breviter, acute, N.; l. ad alqm; sic ore l-ta est, Vg.; rotundo ore; (penes usum) arbitrium est et jus et norma l-di; dulce; secum; ne quarta l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på scenen)</text:span> persona laboret, Hor.; de nare l., Ps.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc. obj.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. neutra af pronomina och adj.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala, utsäga, uttala; framsäga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (declamera); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">föra i munnen tala om; säga:</text:span></text:span> paucula; rem ipsam aperte, Ter.; pugnantia l-eris, C,; haud ignota l-or, Vg.; dii me finxerunt pauca l-entem; dicenda tacenda l-tus; alterna l.; male mandata l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på scenen);</text:span> verba l-or socianda chordis; annosa volumina vatum dictitat Albano Musas in monte l-tas, Hor.; merum bellum, mera scelera l-i, C.; reges atque tetrarchas, omnia magna l-ens,; proelia, Hor.; quos l-eris?; alicui nomen suum, Pt.; Jupiter - hospitibus nam te dare jura l-untur, Vg.; me - majores pennas nido extendisse l-ēris, Hor.; l-bantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(man, folket sade),</text:span> N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om sakliga subject, i personificerande l. hyperboliska uttryck:</text:span> res ipsa pro me l-itur; infantes pueri, mutæ etiam bestiæ pæne l-untur, nihil esse bonum præter voluptatem; dum latine loquentur literæ, quercus huic loco non deerit, quæ Mariana dicatur; oculi, quemadmodum animo affecti simus, l-untur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(uttala),</text:span> C.; Mænalus argutumque nemus pinosque l-entes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(susande, hwiskande),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Talande, tal (språk):</text:span></text:span> l., reticentia, mæstitia, hilaritas; omnis l. oratio est; l. emendata et latina, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttal:</text:span></text:span> a Græcæ l-is similitudine dilatandis literis se abstrahere, C.; recta, Qu.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ord</text:span></text:span> (λέξις): Qu.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">uttryck (”construction”):</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcūtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. talar:</text:span> sermonis exotici, Ap.; levis, Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcūtŭlejus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pratmakare:</text:span></text:span> Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏcūtus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Talande, tal:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquax</text:span>, ācis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språksam, pratsam; talträngd, pratsjuk:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: om mskor:</text:span> senectus est naturā l-ior; adolescens l., C.; in dicendo odiosus et l.; Græculus otiosus et l.; stultitia, C.; l. est, qui nimium loquitur, Varr.; l-es vitet, si sapiat, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. om andra subj.:</text:span> epistola, C.; ranæ; nidus, Vg.; avis, Ov.; lymphæ fontis l-es, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquācĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språksamhet, pratsamhet, -sjuka:</text:span></text:span> facit l. mea longiores epistolas; Græci alicujus l. sine usu, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquācĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språksamt, mångordigt, talträngdt:</text:span></text:span> scribetur <text:soft-page-break/>tibi l. situs agri, Hor.; l. litigiosus, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquācŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquella</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lŏquēla), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tal, talande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (språk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ord:</text:span></text:span> nutricis blanda et infracta l., Lucr.; Graja - Getico victa l-a sono est, Ov.; fundere ore l-as, Vg.; l-am quidam verbum dixerunt, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquellāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: præpositio l. = inseparabilis, Prob.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tungfärdighet:</text:span></text:span> aliud est l., aliud eloquentia, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŏquĭtor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala, prata:</text:span></text:span> male alicui, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŏquor</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adlŏquor), cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala till ngn, tilltala:</text:span></text:span> blande alqm, Pt.; nemo eum a-i voluit, C.; milites imperator <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(talade till),</text:span> Su.; extremum hoc te a-or, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: tröstande tilltala:</text:span> a-tum mulieres ire ajunt, quum eunt consolandi causa, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltal, tal</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngn:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŏquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tilltalande; wänligt, tröstande, uppmuntrande tilltal, tröst:</text:span></text:span> benigno a-o, comitate invitandi fortunam adjuvare, L.; a-o sustinere alqm, Ov.; vinum cantusque ægrimoniæ dulcia a-a, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Antĕlŏquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">företräde i tal, första ordet:</text:span> Mcb.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">företal,</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlŏquor</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">omskrifwa, uttrycka genom omskrifning:</text:span> Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omskrifning:</text:span></text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn l. med hwarandra; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">språkas, samtala:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>: hoc uno maxime præstamus feris, quod c-imur inter nos; cum aliquo; per literas; multum inter se de republica, C.; Cæsar per interpretem cum Gallis c-tus est; ex equis c., Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">obj.-acc.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för personen:</text:span> c. alqm, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för saken:</text:span> de iis rebus, quas tecum c-i volo, annuum tempus mihi des, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samtalande, samtal:</text:span></text:span> (ut deos esse credamus) non c. hominum aut consensus effecit; venire in c-em cum aliquo; familiarissimæ c-es, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŏquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Samtal, -språk:</text:span></text:span> in solitudine secum loqui solebat, ut c-o alterius non egeret; c-a amicorum absentium epistolæ sunt; c-a rerum leviorum; venire in c-um cum aliquo; habere, facere c. cum aliquo; c-o locum deligere, diem dicere, C.; decernere, Sa.; frui deorum c-o, Vg. - in c-o cum aliquo verba facere, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala ut, uttala, yttra sig; tala; i ord framställa, utföra, uttrycka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. i mots. till tiga, fördölja, blott tänka):</text:span> e-ar an sileam?, Vg.; e-ere, quæso, uno verbo rem, Pt.; uterque (venditor et emptor), si ad e-dum venerit, non plus quam semel e-atur; fieri potest, ut recte quis sentiat et id, quod sentit, <text:soft-page-break/>polite e. non possit; e. copiose melius est quam sine eloquentia vel acutissime cogitare; acute et cito reperire, distincte disponere, graviter - pronunciare, firme meminisse, ornate et suaviter e-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de</text:span> 5 partes eloquentiæ), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏquens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Talande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till stum):</text:span> conformatio (προσωποποιία) est, quum - res muta - fit e., C.<text:line-break/>b. p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wältalig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af natur och genom wetenskaplig utbildning):</text:span> disertos se vidisse multos, e-em neminem; Crassus e. et idem juris peritus fuit; omnium videor mihi - e-simos audisse Tib. et C. Sempronios, C.; e-ior, Qu.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏquentius</text:span>, -issime, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏcūtĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Talare-:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sås. en</text:span> pars. eloquentiæ): partes (rhetoricæ) hæ: inventio, dispositio, e., memoria, pro - nunciatio: - e. est idoneorum verborum et sententiarum ad inventionem accommodatio: C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏcūtōria</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏcūtrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(talarekonst):</text:span> Qu. II. 14. 2.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏquentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wältalighet, talareförmåga, -konst:</text:span></text:span> e. est copiose loquens sapientia; quum prudentiā, tum e-ā præstare; satis habere e-æ; Athenis et nata et alta est e., C.; Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŏquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Språkframställning; stil, föredrag; talareförmåga:</text:span></text:span> et tulit e. insolitum facundia præceps (tragoediæ Græcæ), Hor.; nectere vocale e. canoris modis, Juv.; Cælius - animo e-oque Curioni simillimus, Vell.; suavitas e-i Platonis, Pn.; Ulysses e-o vincit Nestora, Ov.; e-o periit Cicero, Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pĕrēlŏquens</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket wältalig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Falla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">i talet:</text:span></text:span> sicine mihi i-eris, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tala, säga emot, falla i talet, afbryta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> tu - et o-are et colloquare velim; exspectatio vestra mihi o-i videtur, C.; o-i jusseras, Pt.; pastores primo - alter alteri obstrepere: (deinde) coërciti a lictore - o-i desistunt, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">låta ljuda emot</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Instämma i, beledsaga ngt</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">rei</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">aliquid</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">musik, sång:</text:span> Orpheus numeris o-itur septem discrimina vocum, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblŏcūtor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. talar, säger emot:</text:span> non sum o. alteri, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Säga förut</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ss. inledning:</text:span></text:span> vix hæc erat p-tus, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælŏcūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Säga fram, uttala, nämna öppet, förkunna:</text:span></text:span> versus vetat artem pudere p-i, quam factites, C.; quam rem oratum veni, p-ar, Pt.; cogitata, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förutsäga:</text:span></text:span> Ppt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlŏquium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sats:</text:span></text:span> Gell.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utslag,</text:span></text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlŏquor</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: eloqui ac r. dicuntur in fanis Sabinis, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Translŏquor</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trālŏquor</text:span>, cūtus, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttala:</text:span></text:span> impuritias alicujus, Pt. Ps. 411.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōra</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrea</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swag must af pressade drufwors skal:</text:span> Pt. Varr., Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rem, läder-remsa:</text:span></text:span> l-o caput equi substringere, N. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. ss.</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Töm, tygel:</text:span></text:span> l-a dare, remittere, Vg., Ov.; fluitantia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slappa);</text:span> parce stimulis et fortius utere l-is, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gissel; piska:</text:span></text:span> l-is cædere alqm, C.; operiri l-is ad necem, Ter. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gördel:</text:span></text:span> Mt.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Säng-gjord:</text:span></text:span> l. lecti, Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Remtyg, rem:</text:span></text:span> Js. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Profoß:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med remmar bunden:</text:span></text:span> juga, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōreus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af remmar, läder-remsor:</text:span> funis, Cato. - faciam ego vestra latera l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(randiga, af slag),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrīca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. harnesk af läderremmar:</text:span> pectorale ex loris corii crudi, Varr.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bröstharnesk, pansar:</text:span></text:span> aēnea, C.; lintea, N.; l-am consertam hamis auroque trilicem, Vg.; l-æ Hiberæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bröstwärn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på wallar; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utanwerk:</text:span></text:span> Cs., T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hägn, omhägnad:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rappning:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrīco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kläda i pansar:</text:span></text:span> milites l-ti, Cs.; coriis se l-re, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rappa, kalkslå:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrīcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rappning, beläggning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med murbruk:</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlōrīco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rifwa upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sönder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngns klädnad:</text:span> tunicam alicujus, C.; panni d-ti, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrīcŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Litet bröstwärn:</text:span></text:span> Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lōrĭpes</text:span>, ĕdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med krokige fötter:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dĭlōris</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Trĭlōris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: vestis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med 2, 3 ränder l. bräm:</text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lotio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōtium,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">watten ur kroppen, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Urin;</text:span></text:span> Cato, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lotura <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lavo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lōtus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(lotos), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>): v. gr.:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lotusträd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> och ngt, s. är gjordt deraf:</text:span> Pn.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flöjt af</text:span> l., Ov.,<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en liljewäxt:</text:span> Vg., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ōtŏphăgus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lotus-ätarne (ett folk i Africa):</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>oxĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den i gåtor talande, tillnamn för Apollo:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ua, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en romersk gudomlighet.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lubens, Lubet, Lubido <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. m. se</text:span> Libet.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūbrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> lābor?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hwarpå man glider l. som glider) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hal, glatt, slipprig, glidande</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (snabbt rinnande, rullande; lättrörlig):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> via præceps et l-a; via l-a, qua quis insistere aut ingredi sine casu aliquo aut prolapsione vix possit, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i bild);</text:span> glacies, L.; anguis; l-a terga anguis, Vg.; conchylia, Hor.; terra, Tib.; via, Ppt.; oculos fecit natura l-os <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rullande),</text:span> C.; Simois, Hor.; piscis, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slipprig, osäker, betänklig, kinkig, äfwentyrlig, farlig; bedräglig:</text:span></text:span> ætas incerta et l-a; ipsa consuetudo assentiendi periculosa est et l-a; l-um genus orationis adolescenti, non acriter intelligenti; facillime ad res injustas impellitur, ut quisque altissimo animo est, gloriæ cupiditate. Qui locus est sane l., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūbrĭcum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slipprigt ställe, s. mark, slipprighet:</text:span></text:span> per l-a surgere, Vg.; viarum l-a, T.; vitia sunt in l-o incitataque semel proclive labuntur, C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">slipprig, kinkig punkt:</text:span></text:span> ætatis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūbrĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra glatt, hal:</text:span></text:span> Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Lucca) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūcensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcā, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> = Lucanus: bos, L. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(elephant),</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcānus,<text:line-break/>a. A = Lucanicus.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt cognomen.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcāni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Italien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūcānia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Lūcānĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcānĭca</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Köttkorf:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūcar,</text:span> āris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skådespelares arvode,</text:span> T. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Paul. Diac. ”quod erogabatur ab iis, qui lucos possidebant.”)</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcejus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Luccejus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lucellum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lucrum.<text:line-break/>Lucensis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luca.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūceo,</text:span> luxi, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa, skina:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> lumen l-et alicui, Enn.; stella (luna) luce alienā l-et, C.; l-ent aurea fulcra genialibus toris; rara per occultos l-bat semita calles; l-ens lunæ globus, Vg. - faces, lymphæ l-entes, Ov.; focus igne, Tib. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">impers.</text:span> lucet = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">det är ljust, dager:</text:span></text:span> non satis l-bat; coepit l-re, C., Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara klar, tydlig; lysa, stråla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fram):</text:span> res argumentis l-et; <text:soft-page-break/>æquitas l-et ipsa per se: dubitatio cogitationem significat injuriæ, C.; virtus l-et in tenebris splendetque per se semper; ingenii quædam forma in Horten - sio l-bat, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span>: facem alicui <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lysa ngn med - -),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcerna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lampa:</text:span></text:span> lumen l-æ; adhibere l-am; deserit me l.; eādem l-a <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid samma l.)</text:span> scribere, C.; l-am accendere, exstingnere, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcesco</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lūcisco), ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Inch.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljusna, skina;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wanl. impers.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">det dagas, ljusnar:</text:span></text:span> sol, Vg.; C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, lysande, skinande:</text:span></text:span> l-a tela diei, Lucr.; fratres Helenæ, l-a sidera, Hor.; lilium, Ppt.; gemma; domus l-ior, Ov.; nox, Pn.; l-simus, Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar, tydlig:</text:span></text:span> cui lecta potenter erit res, nec facundia deseret hunc nec l. ordo, Hor.; narratio; imitator, Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klart, tydligt:</text:span></text:span> definire l. breviterque, C.; l. apparet, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælūcĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket klar, skinande:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublūcĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något klar:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lucifer, -fuga, -fugus, Lucu <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lux.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭbrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: quod lucet in umbra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(litet bål):</text:span> Isid.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭbro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Arbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wid ljus) om natten; nattetid </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utarbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förfärdiga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> o. d.:</text:span> ancillæ, L.; opus l-tum, l-am, C.; farinam; viam, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭbrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nattarbete</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i abstr. och concret bet.):</text:span> detraxi l-es, C.; vespertina; antelucana, Pn.; agere alqd in l-e, per l-em, Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭbrātiuncŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Gell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭbrātōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: lecticula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för nattarbete),</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlūcŭbro</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlūcŭbror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid ljus, wid nattlampan </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Arbeta, utarbeta:</text:span></text:span> orationes elaboratæ diligenter et tamquam e-tæ; epistolam e-tus eram, C.; alqd, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Luculentus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lux.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: (lucmen): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= ngt, s. lyser, upplyser:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, sken;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ljus, strålar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från en lysande kropp:</text:span> solis l-e luna collustratur; varietas l-um lunæ; obscuratur luce solis l. lucernæ, C.; l-a solis, Ov.; largior hic campos æther et l-e vestit purpureo, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Glans:</text:span></text:span> l. juventæ purpureum, Vg.; ferri, St.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om det ljus spridande föremålet sjelf = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, lampa, fackla.</text:span></text:span> l. de suo l-e accendere, Enn.; noctu l-e apposito animadvertit; l. in tenebris præferre alicui; l-i oleum instillare, C.; accensis l-bus, Cs.; famulas ad l-a longo exercet penso; fumea l-a, Vg.; ad, sub l-a prima; librum cum l-e poscere, Hor.; l. exstinguere, Ct.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ljus, s. råder någorstädes:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Belysning, dager,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwari ngt befinner sig; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ljus</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i en målning:</text:span> tabulas bene pictas in bono l-e collocare, C.; umbra et l., Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dagens, lifwets ljus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">dag; lif:</text:span></text:span> obscuro etiam l-e, Sa.; secundo l-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på andre dagen),</text:span> C.; quarto, supremo l-e; cassus l-e (= luce carens = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">död),</text:span> Vg.; l-e adempto animam fundere; l-a relinquere, Lucr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det, hwarigenom l. hwarifrån ngt får ljus:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Syn, öga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (blick), (i synn. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span>): Democritus l-bus amissis alba ab atris discernere non poterat, C.; oculorum l-a amittere, N.; Cyclopi l. ademptum; l. torvum; natantia l-a; l-a (Mercurius) morte resolvit, Vg.; reddere alicui adempta l-a; placido l-e videre alqm, Hor.; orbus altero l-e, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öppning för ljus i en byggnad, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fönster,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fönster-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utsigt:</text:span></text:span> l-bus alicujus obstruere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bygga för);</text:span> l-a mutari putabat, cuicumque parti cæli officeretur, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> duo l-a ab animo ad oculos perforata, C. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttr. för wägleda (oeg.), ingifwa hopp, rädda, hjelpa o. d.:</text:span> memoriæ l. afferre; civibus l. ingenii et consilii sui porrigere et tendere; deus menti præfert l., C.; scire licet, hunc quondam l. rebus nostris dubiis futurum præsidiumque regiæ afflictæ, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till beteckning af ngt glänsande, skönt, utmärkt; concret: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">prydnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stjerna), sirat; serskildt: framställningens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">prydnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rhetorisk figur, bild, wändning):</text:span> quum virtus extulit et ostendit l. suum -, exardescit amicitia; l. probitatis et virtutis in aliquo perspicere videri; alterum ille exstitisset l. civitatis (nisi imbecilla valetudine esset); hoc l. consulatus sui fore putabat; quasi in ornatu disposita quædam insignia et l-a; Origines Catonis - quod l. eloquentiæ non habent?; Catonis l-bus obstruxit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> l. 3. b.) posteriorum quasi altius exaggerata oratio; l. verborum et sententiarum; l-a, quæ Græci σχήματα appellant, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Syn, öga:</text:span></text:span> mentis l-bus officit altitudo fortunæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmĭnāre</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fönster:</text:span></text:span> Cato, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Låta lysa, upplysa:</text:span></text:span> Ap. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmĭnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: male l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med dålig syn),</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som har mycket ljus: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, lysande:</text:span></text:span> ædificium, Vitr.; pars <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(parti)</text:span> orationis quasi l-a, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūmĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upplysa, förklara:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūmĭnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mörk,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. sker i mörkret:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūmĭno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upplysa, lysa upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> a sole luna i-atur; corona gemmis i-ta, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> orationem sententiis verborumque conformationibus i-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smycka),</text:span> C.; horum fidem perfidia Mitylenæorum i-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ställer i klarare ljus);</text:span> dies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tiden)</text:span> virtutem alicujus i-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förklarar);</text:span> is orbem eloquentiā, Vell.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūmĭnāte</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med glans, prydlighet:</text:span></text:span> et rebus et verbis i. dicere, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lux</text:span>, lūcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. råder någorstädes, sprides från, öfwer ngt):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> solis; lychnorum; id est l-e clarius, C.; lunæ maligna l.; dant clara incendia l-em erranti, Vg.; ex fumo dare l-em, Hor.; l. siderea, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> nulla sententia illustris est sine l-e verborum, C.; rebus parum claris dare l-em, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ögonens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus:</text:span></text:span> adempta, Ov.; effossa, St. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dagsljus, dagning, dager:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i och för sig:</text:span> noctu scribere alqd ingressum l. oppressit; prima l-e in campum currere; ante l-em galli canunt; l-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid ljusan dag)</text:span> palam in foro saltare, C.; luci, cum luci, Pt., C.; l. oritur, appetit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gryr);</text:span> sub l-em <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mot dagningen);</text:span> a prima l-e, Cs.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. tidsafdelning):</text:span> centesima l. est ab - -, C.; l. crastina, tertia, ultima <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lifwets siste d.),</text:span> Vg.; l. oritur gratissima; l-es festæ, profestæ, Hor.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, dag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ljusets werld,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (det ljusa) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lifwet:</text:span></text:span> l. hujus vitæ; suscipi in l-em; omnes dico miseros esse, qui hac l-e careant; piratis l-is usuram diuturnam dare; finis hujus l-is, C.; nobis quum semel occidit brevis l., nox est perpetua - una dormienda, Catl.; l-em perosi projecere animas; l-em invisam abrumpere; l-e carentes (= mortui), Vg.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i smekande uttryck:</text:span> mea l. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mitt lif:</text:span> C., Ppt.<text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, dag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = offentlighet (werlden); bemärkthet, anseende:</text:span> non ille (Fabius) in l-e modo atque in oculis civium magnus, sed intus domique præstantior; forensis l.; illa commentatio inclusa in veritatis l-em proferenda est; is vestram familiam ex tenebris in l-em evocavit, C.<text:line-break/>δ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.: ljus = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hjelp, frälsning:</text:span></text:span> l-em afferre reipublicæ, C.; l. affulsit civitati, L.<text:line-break/>II. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt, s. lyser, sprider ljus:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> l-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om stjernor),</text:span> C. poēt.; o l. immensi publica mundi, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> hæc urbs, l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sol)</text:span> orbis terrarum et urbs omnium gentium; historia l. veritatis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sanningens fackla),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcū</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af ett obr.</text:span> lucus = lux <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> noctu): cum primo l-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i första ljusningen),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljusbringande:</text:span></text:span> Diana, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcĭfer</text:span>, fĕri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Morgonstjerna; dag:</text:span></text:span> C., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcĭfŭga</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcĭfŭgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljusskygg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i eg. och oeg. bet.):</text:span> blattæ, Vg.; homines difficiles, l-i, maledici, C.; l-æ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= nattswärmare),</text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, lysande:</text:span></text:span> vestibulum, Pt.; caminus, C.; ignis, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skön:</text:span></text:span> femina, Pt.; forma, Ter.; verba, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förnäm, präktig, rik:</text:span></text:span> matrimonium; patrimonium; navigium, C.; homo; familia, Pt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Herrlig, förträfflig, utmärkt, ypperlig:</text:span></text:span> facinus; dies Pt.; plagam l-am <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(iron.)</text:span> accipere; scriptor; patronus; auctor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sagesman, </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">auctoritet),</text:span> C.; oratio, Sa.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭlente</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭlenter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skönt; förträffligt, ypperligt:</text:span></text:span> texere opus l-ter, C.; vendere l-ter, Pt.; l-te dicere, scribere, scire Græce, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Antĕlūcānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är l. sker </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">före dager:</text:span></text:span> tempus industria, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublūcānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mot dagningen:</text:span> tempora, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allūceo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(adlūceo), xi, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa emot</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> fortuna tibi faculam lucrificam a-re vult, Pt.; igniculus tibi a-xit, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlūceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa, skina omkring:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">klart, rikt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa, stråla, wara upplyst, stå i ljus, stråla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af -, absol. och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">re</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">a re</text:span>: sol longe lateque; c-et cælum omnibus (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>); templum fulgore candelabri; mare a sole; lacteus orbis, C.; jam mare turbari trabibus sævasque videbis c-re faces; moenia c-ent flammis Elissæ, Vg.; tota acies flammis, L.; castra, Ct.; agri floribus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara klar, tydlig:</text:span></text:span> res coepit d-re patribus, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūcesco</text:span>, luxi, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dagas, gry, bli ljust:</text:span></text:span> omnem crede diem tibi d-xisse supremum, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">impers.</text:span>: quum jam d-ret -, C. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> d-xit rerum genitalis origo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om werldens l. tingens morgon</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skapelse),</text:span> Lucr.; discussa est caligo, d-xit, videmus omnia, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūcĭdus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ljus, klar:</text:span></text:span> pallor, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar, tydlig:</text:span></text:span> expositio d-a; narratio d-ior; d-ora facere omnia, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūcĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klart, tydligt:</text:span></text:span> flagrare, Pn.; dicere; explicare, C.; docere, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūcĭdo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra tydlig; klart beteckna:</text:span></text:span> rem, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūcŭlum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dagning, gryning:</text:span></text:span> d-o, primo d-o venire, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūcŭlat</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">impers.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Det dagas:</text:span></text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlūceo</text:span>, xi, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framlysa, lysa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fram ur, bland hopen, sin omgifning):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> circus inter flammas e-ens, quem vos orbem lacteum nuncupatis, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framlysa:</text:span></text:span> in ipso joco alqd probi ingenii lumen e-eat; in puero ingenium - e-et; tenuitas ejus, quo magis occultatur, eo magit e-et, C.; ex his id e-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(är klart),</text:span> N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa:</text:span></text:span> in foro atque in causis; sanctitas ejus, C.; ille virtutibus e-xit, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa på:</text:span></text:span> pix capiti alicujus, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūcesco</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Illūcisco), luxi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Börja lysa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på l. öfwer; (om ljuset, dagen) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppgå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öfwer, för), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gry, dagas:</text:span></text:span> alqm luce clara (sol), Pt.; dies i-xit, i-scet, C.; <text:span text:style-name="T1">impers.</text:span>: ubi i-xit,. L.; quem potes recordari in vita tibi i-isse <text:soft-page-break/>diem lætiorem?, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> populo Romano auctoritas consulis repente in tantis tenebris i-xit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(framglänste för -),</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlūceo</text:span>, xi, 2.:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlūcesco</text:span>, xi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa, ljusna, skina</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emellan:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> nocte i-xit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(impers.), det ljusnade emellan (igenom mörkret),</text:span> L.; in succino - animalia i-cent, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Synas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> emellan, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">framstå:</text:span></text:span> loci dissimiles - comparandi sunt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mnemoniken),</text:span> ut distincte i. possint, C. - ordines, quibus inter gradus dignitatis alqd i-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(någon skilnad synes),</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara genomskinlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gles:</text:span></text:span> rara est acies i-etque corona non tam spissa viris, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlūceo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pellūceo</text:span>, xi, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa, skina igenom:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> color ovi (si contra lumen tenetur), Pn.; fibra, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> honestum decorumque ex his virtutibus maxime p-et, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara genomskinlig:</text:span></text:span> p-es quasi laterna Punica, Pt.; - <text:span text:style-name="T1">part.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlūcens</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomskinlig:</text:span></text:span> æther tenuis et p. est, C.; amictus, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> mollis et p. oratio, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlūcĭdus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(pellūcĭdus), -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klar, genomskinlig:</text:span></text:span> stella; membranæ oculorum, C.; p-ior vitro, Hor.; fons, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlūcĭdĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomskinlighet:</text:span></text:span> Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlūcĭdŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: lapis, Cat.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælūceo</text:span>, xi, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lysa, bära ljus framför, lysa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn (på wäg):</text:span> faces p-ent, Mt.; servus, Su.; facinori ignis, Phdr. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> amicitia bona spe p-et in posterum, C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(andre läsa</text:span> bonam spem); lumen vitæ alicujus p-o, Aus.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerglänsa:</text:span></text:span> nullus in orbe locus Bajis p-et amoenis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Prælucidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se under</text:span> Lucidus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlūceo</text:span>, xi, 2.: natura sena per diem, sena per noctem signa proluxit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(låtit framlysa;</text:span> alii: produxit), Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlūceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gifwa återsken, skina, glimma; stråla:</text:span></text:span> Sigea igni freta lata r-ent, Vg.; stella r-ens, C.; flamma, L.; vestis, Ov.; favilla, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlūcesco</text:span>, luxi, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter börja lysa, framskina, -glänsa:</text:span></text:span> solis imago, Ov.; dies cæco, T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">impers.,</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublūceo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Framskimra inunder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wid randen af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt; i bottnen </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skimra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> aries s-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under wintergatan),</text:span> C. poēt.; crepuscula s-ent <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid horizonten);</text:span> candida ora mixto rubore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> sub candore rubens luna), Ov.; in foliis violæ s-et purpura nigræ, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Sublucanus, Sublucidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se under</text:span> Lux <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Lucidus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Translūceo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(trāluceo), ēre:<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Skina öfwer), reflecteras:</text:span></text:span> speculo in speculum imago, Lucr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skina, synas igenom:</text:span></text:span> in aquis corpus, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara genomskinlig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (kunna ses igenom):</text:span> vitra; gemmæ, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Translūcĭdus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(tralūcĭdus), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomskinlig:</text:span></text:span> membrana: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcĕres (Ov.), <text:line-break/>Lŭcĕres (Ppt.), um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jemte</text:span> Ramnes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Tities) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en af Romarnes äldsta</text:span> tribus: L. <text:line-break/>Lūcĕrenses, ium, id. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcĕria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Apulien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūcĕrīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lucerna, Lucesco, Lucide, -cidus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luceo.<text:line-break/>Lucifer, Lucifug . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lux, Luceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcīlius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūcīliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcīna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mångudinnan:</text:span> C.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">barnsbördens gudinna (Juno):</text:span> casta fave, L-a, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = barnsbörd:</text:span> poēt. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcius (L.), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt prænomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lucrativus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lucror, Lucrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcrētĭlis, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Sabinum.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcrētius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Lūcrētia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerska (slägt-)namn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcrīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sjö i Campanien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūcrīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūcrīnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lucri . . ., Lucror, Lucrosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lucrum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŭcrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af affär, speculation), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förtjenst, winning, behållning:</text:span></text:span> l. facere, Pt.; aut damnum aut certe non magnum l. faciunt decumani; multum, tantum l-i facere; l-i facere alqd (se lucrifacio) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> l-i dare alicui aliquantum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa ss. ren winst, behållning);</text:span> imperat Verres Agyrinensibus, ut decumas ipsi publice accipiant, Apronio - l-i dent tritici medimnum XXXIII milia et præterea HS LX.; dat de l-o, nihil detrahit de vivo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(capitalet),</text:span> C.; deputare alqd esse in l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(räkna för winst),</text:span> Ter.; in l-is ponere, C.; l-o apponere, Hor.; ad l. omnia revocare; facere l. ex aliqua re; id est alicui l-o; emendi aut vendendi quæstu et l-o duci; l-i causa facere alqd, C.; periculosum, Phdr.; sordidum, Qu.; de l-o vivere = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lefwa på nåd,</text:span> C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">meton. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">winningslystnad, penningebegär; skatter:</text:span></text:span> contagia l-i, Hor.; l-i pallida tabes, Luc.; - quum Saturnus regna haberet, omne l. tenebris alta premebat humus, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcellum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Liten winst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (”den kära winsten”):</text:span> l. facere, C.; quid pure tranquillat, honos an dulco l.?, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrīfăcio</text:span> (lucri facio), 3. (<text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> lucrifio): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winna; få i winst, behållning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oftast = (taga ss. god pris) orättmätigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">slå under sig; </text:span></text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">undan-, försnilla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> omnis illa ex ærario pecunia, quam his oportuit civitatibus pro frumento dari, l-facta est (a Verre); in una emptione C modii tritici l-fiunt, C.; alqd l-fecit, Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. nomen <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tillegna sig),</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>b. = impune ferre = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">undgå straff för ngt:</text:span> maleficium, Cs.; injuriam, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrĭfĭcābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winstgifwande:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrĭfŭga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som skyr winst; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slösare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrĭcrĭpĕta</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (peto): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. fikar efter winning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winningslysten:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt på ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">få i winst:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> locupletes suum perdunt, debitores l-antur alienum; stipendium; auri pondus X, C.; nomen ab domita Africa (Africanus - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blott</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> namnet),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. indicia veteris infamiæ l-etur (Verres = tacita ferat, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">må han få dem förtigna),</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrātīvus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är winst l. behållning; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Insparad:</text:span></text:span> tempus, Front.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcrōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Winstgifwande, indrägtig:</text:span></text:span> voluptas, Ov.; fraus, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lucta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottning:</text:span></text:span> Hyg., Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(arch.</text:span> <text:line-break/>lucto, Ter.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottas, nappas:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentligaste men.:</text:span> exerceri l-do, N.; Olympiis l.; viribus ad l-dum valere, C.; l-antis ungue secari, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">brottas = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Streta, spjerna, sträfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (trängas) med ngt l. mot ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">möda, anstränga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(strida, fäkta, kämpa),</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">syn.</text:span> nitor): inter se adversis l-antur cornibus hædi; l-antes ventos - Aeolus frenat; l-antes juvenci <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sträfwa med plogen);</text:span> in lento l-antur marmore <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wattnet)</text:span> tonsæ; l-atur eripere telum; anima l-ans <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(en döendes),</text:span> Vg.; in turba l. (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">trängas);</text:span> funera plaustris, Hor.; oscula l-anti auferre; Typhōeus l-atur remoliri pondera terræ, Ov.; cum nodis, Ct.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck: brottas, (kifwas), streta emot, kämpa, strida:</text:span> non l-bor tecum, Crasse, amplius, C.; (illos) fertilitate frui, se in pestilenti atque arido solo l-ri, L.; cum ardore et siccitate regionis l., Ct.; non l-or de nomine hujus mensis, Ov.; contra fortunam, Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottning; ansträngning:</text:span></text:span> Cp.; (ita substitit unda), remo ut l. abesset, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctātio</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottning, -tande (nappatag); stretande, ansträngning:</text:span></text:span> cursus, pugilatio, l., curricula equorum, C.; tetra ibi (Hannibalis exercitui) l. erat, lubrica glacie non recipiente vestigium, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. (= strid):</text:span> tibi cum Diodoro, valente dialectico, magna in hac causa l. est, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottare:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Qu. - (vinum) dolosus l. est, pedes captat, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottning:</text:span></text:span> est ei impar l. contra alqm, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Alluctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Colluctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottas, streta, sträfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt (i eg. och oeg. bet.):</text:span> latrones c-antes, Ap.; cum veneno, Pn.; cum agro, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Colluctātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottning, sträfwande, stretande:</text:span></text:span> boum inter se, Col.; c. animam agentis, Sen.; cum verbis c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för att få dem fram);</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēluctor</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlucto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottas, kämpa;</text:span></text:span> cum Antæo Hercules; cum ærumnis, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēluctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Streta, sträfwa, arbeta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tränga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sig) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ut, fram,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> igenom:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>: per impedimenta, Sen.; aqua e-bitur omnis, Vg.; Tiberius velut e-antium verborum (fuit), T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tränga, bryta sig wäg genom):</text:span> tot et tam validæ manus (fugientibus) e-dæ erant, L.; vix quieto agmine nives (e-bantur); locorum difficultates e., T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēluctābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomtränglig:</text:span></text:span> locus nec pediti nec navigio e., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ĭnēluctābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ogenomtränglig, oöfwerwinnelig, oundwiklig:</text:span></text:span> coenum, St.; venit summa dies et i-e tempus Dardaniæ; i-e fatum, Vg.; fatorum vis, Vell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illuctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottas på</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (arbeta sig fram):</text:span> verba teneris labris, St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Obluctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brottas, streta, sträfwa emot:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> genibus adversæ o-or arenæ, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> oblivioni; difficultatibus, Ct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕluctor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Rĕlucto, Ap.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spjerna, streta, sträfwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (bakut, baklänges) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">emot:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> dracones (aquilæ) r-antes, Hor.; multa, Vg.; vestigia r-antis cernebantur, T.; producentibus (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>) verecunde, Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> precibus, Ct.; quum quidam postularent, ut de ratione dicendi alqd componerem, diu sum r-tus, Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Luctamen, Luctat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luctor, Lucta. <text:line-break/>Luctifer, Luctific . . ., Luctisonus, Luctuosus, -ose, Luctus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lugeo.<text:line-break/>Lucu, Lucub . . ., Luculent . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūcullus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en rom.</text:span> gens. <text:line-break/>Lūcullēus, <text:line-break/>Lūculliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Luculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lucus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŭcŭmo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lucmo, <text:line-break/>Lycmon, Ppt.), ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">etrurisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höfding:</text:span></text:span> Serv. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">n. pr.</text:span> (= Tarquinius Priscus): L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŭcuns</text:span>, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭcuncŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bakwerk:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Petr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lund</text:span></text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wårdad, rödjad (jfr</text:span> colluco) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skog, i mots. till wild; wanl. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">offerlund, helig lund]:</text:span></text:span> l. ille - agnoscitur sæpe a me lectus in Mario; domus habet l-um; Albani tumuli atque l-i; l. Vestæ, C.; duo l-i (in Capitolio); l. (Junonis) frequenti silva, proceris arboribus sæptus, læta in medio pascua habuit; l. Camenarum; l. Ferentinæ, L.; l. in urbe fuit media; l. Dianæ, Egeriæ, sacer; in alto l-o considunt catervæ avium, Vg.; umbrosis l-is immolare Fauno; præceps Anio et Tiburni l., Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūcŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwista</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> träd; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rödja, göra uthuggning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i skog:</text:span> arborem, Col.; lucum, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlūco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwista, utgallra:</text:span></text:span> ramorum densitatem, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlūcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublūco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ned-, undertill qwista:</text:span> Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūdo,</text:span> lūsi, lūsum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka, spela:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. om hwad s. göres för nöje, tidsfördrif l. kroppens öfning:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor, barn och äldre: leka; spela:</text:span> puer ludum l-it, Ter.; pueris non omnem l-di licentiam damus, sed eam, quæ ab honestis actionibus non sit aliena; l-di modus est retinendus, C.; puerorum mores inter l-dum facillime cognoscuntur, Qu.; l-entes pueri dicunt: rex eris, si recte facies, Hor.; tesseris, Ter.; pilā; XII scriptis; aleā, C.; trocho; par impar, Hor.; aleam, Su. (poēt.); proelia latronum, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om djur och döda föremål (leka):</text:span> piscis in undis, Ter.; agni, Lucr.; cygni l-unt stridentibus alis, Vg.; exsultim equa; herboso campo pecus; fortuna ludum insolentem, Hor.; l-it Mæandrus in undis, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wapenlekar på Campus </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(fäkta):</text:span></text:span> videant, ad l-dum an ad pugnandum sint arma sumpturi, C.; l-re qui nescit, campestribus abstinet armis, indoctusque pilæ discive trochive quiescit, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppträda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid skådespel:</text:span> notatum est, ludis circensibus - ursos et elephantos l-isse, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intrans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om dans och musik (ss lek): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (dansa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">spela; jollra:</text:span></text:span> Fauni feræque in numerum; versu Syracosio Thalia; l-re quæ vellem, calamo permisit agresti; carmina l-re, Vg.; inter virgines; si quid tecum lusimus (lyra) -, Hor. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: leka = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämta, skalkas,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (rasa), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra ngt på lek; leka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skämta bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förspilla):</text:span> non l-isse pudet, sed non incidere ludum; l-is et bibis impudens; hæc ego l. (carmina), Hor.; operam, Ter.; otium, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. l. <text:span text:style-name="T1">aliquem</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra spe af, drifwa gäck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">drifwa, gäckas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med, (utskratta):</text:span> Sophistas a Socrate lusos videmus; l-imur ab homine non tam faceto, quam ad scribendi licentiam libero; Crassus totam causam atque disputationem lusit; omnium irrisione l-i, C.; mox ubi lusit satis (Venus Europam) -, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Narras; leka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bedraga, gäcka</text:span></text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">aliquem</text:span>): l-entem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på lek)</text:span> minari alicui, C.; credite, non ludo, crudeles, tollite claudum, Hor.; quam multa (haruspicum responsa) l-runt <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bedragit</text:span> ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slagit fel),</text:span> C.; virginem, Ter.; vana spe lusit amantem; etiam tu natum l-is <text:soft-page-break/>vanis imaginibus, Vg.; an me l-it amabilis insania?, Hor.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spela, föreställa:</text:span></text:span> bonum civem, C. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭbrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i oeg. bet.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leksak, -werk, -boll; narrwerk, gyckelwerk, -bild,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (narraktighet):</text:span> Bias hæc l-a fortunæ (ɔ: opes et divitias) ne sua quidem putavit, C.; Brutus a Tarquiniis Delphos ductus, l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(driftämne, narr)</text:span> verius, quam comes, L.; foliis ne carmina manda, ne turbata volent, rapidis l-a ventis, Vg.; tu (navis), nisi ventis debes l-um, cave, Hor.; l-a religionum, oculorum, L.; hæc l-a ridiculaque sunt, Lucr.; l-a naturæ (pumili), Su. - esse alicui l-o; haberi l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förhånas),</text:span> C., Ter., Sa., L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hån, spe, gäckeri,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hånlig, wanärande behandling:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> l-o lædi ab aliquo; filii l-o et despectui paternis inimicis erant oppositi, C.; Remus l-o fratris muros transsiluit; per l-um auditi et dimissi legati, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kränkning:</text:span></text:span> Ct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭbrīōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hånande, hånfull:</text:span></text:span> Gell., Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭbriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭbundus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lekande:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">under lek och skämt:</text:span></text:span> milites Beneventum venere l-i, L.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lätt, s. en lek):</text:span> l-um conficere alqd, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭcer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">obr.),</text:span> cra, crum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: s. sker, öfwas till tidsfördrif l. på lek, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lekande, skämtsam:</text:span></text:span> exercitatio; ars l-a armorum; l-i sermones, C.; l-æ artes, T.; <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭcra</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lekar, tidsfördrif:</text:span></text:span> nunc etiam versus et cetera l-a pono, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. hör till skådespel, spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">scenisk, skådespelare-:</text:span></text:span> certamen, L., Sen.; valeat res l-a (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">scenen),</text:span> Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭcrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skådespel:</text:span></text:span> l. fuit equi pugilesque ex Etruria acciti; l. celebrare, L.; l. Isthmiorum, Olympiorum, Ct., L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭcre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på lek:</text:span> Enn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭcror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämta:</text:span></text:span> Fr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lek, spel:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tidsfördrif, lek;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> spel:</text:span> puer fatigatus l-o, Hor.; pueri intenti l-o (turbinis), Vg.; venatu invigilant pueri -: flectere l-us equos et spicula tendere cornu, Vg.; ad pilam se aut ad talos conferunt aut etiam novum sibi - excogitant in otio l-um; l. talarius; epularum et l-orum voluptates, C.; l. in artem vertit, L.; post hoc (ɔ: coenam) l. erat culpā potare magistrā; gratia regum Pieriis tentata modis l-usque repertus et longorum operum finis, Hor.; l-o proelia texere, belli simulacra ciere, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om kropps-, wapenöfningar (isynn. på Marsfältet); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wapenlek:</text:span></text:span> l-o campestri tunicatum uti, C.; l-um alicujus utrumque pollice laudare, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hit hör:</text:span> heu longo satiate ludo, Hor. Carm. I. 2. 37.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wanl. i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offentliga </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lekar, spel, skådespel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. ursprungl. bestodo i kroppsrörelser och wapenlek):</text:span> l-os apparare, facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= bekosta);</text:span> l-is delectari, commoveri; quinquennalis l-orum (Olympicorum) celebritas, C.; l-os Neptuno sollennes parare; l-os opulentius facere; l-os ex instauratione parare; l-os instaurare; l-os committere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(börja);</text:span> l-is mane <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skådespelsdagen);</text:span> l-i amplissimi, magnificentissimi; l-i scenici instituti, L.; l-os spectare, N., Hor.; Iliaci l-i; veteres ineunt proscenia l-i, Vg.; l-i (scenici) cum strepitu spectantur; l-i (seculares) ter die totiesque nocte frequentes, Hor.; l-os cele brare, Ct.; diem annuis l-is celebrare; Nero l-os instituit juvenalium vocabulo, T.; l-os edere, Pn., Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lek,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om folkfester, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">folknöjen, -förlustelser</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på fri- l. festdagar:</text:span> dies festus - l-um et lasciviam magis quum formidinem ostentabat, Sa.; publicus urbis l. (ɔ: feriæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid Augusti ankomst till Rom),</text:span> Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf wäl äfwen: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fridag, ledighet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från arbete:</text:span> l. datus est argentariis, Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> ludum dare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. men.</text:span> II. b.)<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lek,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i uttr. för ngt lätt l. ringa:</text:span> omnium ceterarum rerum oratio l. est homini non hebeti; his jusjurandum jocus, testimonium l. est, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lek = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämt; nöje; frihet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att roa sig, slå sig lös (jfr</text:span> I. 2. c.): vertere seria l-o; amoto quæramus seria l-o, Hor.; per l-um et jocum evertere alqm; dare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(unna)</text:span> l-um (juventuti), C.<text:span text:style-name="T1">;</text:span> frui l-o ætatis, L.; anni mihi eripuere l-um; non lusisse pudet, sed non incidere l-um; amori dare l-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lemna den frihet),</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gäckeri, drift, spe,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (skalkstycke) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">spratt:</text:span></text:span> l-os facere, reddere alicui, Ter.; l-um, l-os facere, habere, dimittere alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa till narr),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>III. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfningsplats, skola:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gladiatorsskola, fäktskola</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> I. 2. a.): gladiatores, quos Cæsar in l-o habebat, Cs.; l-um gladiatorium ædificare, Su.; spectatum satis et donatum jam rude - quæris - antiquo includere l-o; l. Aemilius, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skola</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för bokliga konster, musik m. m.:</text:span> doctus in eodem l-o, Ter.; l. fidicinus; in l-um ire, Pt.<text:span text:style-name="T1">;</text:span> Dionysius - Corinthi l-um aperuit; in l-um discendi, non lusionis, ducere alqm, C.; in l-o cognoscere alqm, N.; l-i magister <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> magister l-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skollärare),</text:span> C., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfăcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hafwa till narr; lura:</text:span></text:span> alqm de aliqua, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfĭcor</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(leka =) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krångla, konstra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (chicanera):</text:span> latitare et l-re <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en tredskande gäldenär);</text:span> aperte calumniari et l-ri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om anklagare),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka med ngn, hafwa till narr; gäckas, drifwa spe</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">narra, förwilla:</text:span></text:span> alqm l-re, l-ri, Pt.; pacis morā consulem l-re; incerto proelio l-ti (<text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span>), Sa.; an quidquam superbius quam l-ri (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dep.</text:span>) sic omne nomen Latinum?, L.; ut puerorum ætas improvida l-etur - (<text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span>) (dulci mellis liquore), Lucr.; patres et plebem ficta cunctatione l-tur (Tiberius), T. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med sakl. obj.: gäcka = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra om intet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillintetgöra werkan af:</text:span></text:span> ii (redemptores), qui priorem locationem l-ti erant (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">krånglat sig ifrån);</text:span> Archimedes ea, quæ Romani ingenti mole agebant, l-batur, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kränka:</text:span></text:span> virginem, Ter.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfĭcābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: ludus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">egnad att narra</text:span></text:span> (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäl anlagdt spratt),</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfĭcātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gäckeri, konster, konstgrepp,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (krångel, </text:span><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">chican):</text:span> omni mora, l-e, calumnia senatus auctoritas impediebatur, C.; hostis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(subj.);</text:span> veri <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(obj.),</text:span> L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfĭcātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som drifwer gäck med, lurar ngn:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdĭfĭcātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span> ui, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: l-ui habere alqm <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till narr),</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlūdĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Drifwa gäck med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skådespelare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i widsträcktaste men., så wäl scenisk, s. dansare l. gladiator:</text:span> l-us, non solum spectator, C.; l-nes ex Etruria acciti ad tibicinis modos saltantes, haud indecoros motus more Tusco dabant, L.; l-us gladiator erat, Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūdia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skådespelerska (äfwen = skådespelares hustru l. älskarinna):</text:span> Mt., Juv.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lek, spel:</text:span></text:span> ludus discendi, non l-is; ex multis l-bus nobis talos relinquant, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūsĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūsor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spelare:</text:span></text:span> Ov., Juv. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som jollrar om, besjunger ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sångare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> jfr</text:span> ludo I. 2. c.: tenerorum l. amorum (Naso), Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämtare, begabbare:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūsōrius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som hör till spelare l. spel:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som sker på lek l. skämt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lekande, skämtsam:</text:span></text:span> Pn., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span> 4.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lek, spel:</text:span></text:span> aleæ, Calenlorum, Pn., Sn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämt, joller;</text:span></text:span> Luperci per l-m et lasciviam discurrebant, L. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Älskogslek, (kärlek):</text:span></text:span> apti lusibus anni, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablūdo</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afwika, wara olik:</text:span></text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (emot) med ngn l. ngt</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wänligt närma sig, mysa, le emot ngn; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">smeka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> ad mulierem, Ter.; (ad mulierem) velut ad notam infans, Js.; alicui, Phdr.; delphinus natantibus, Pn. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka mot,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om döda subj., ss. om wågen l. winden, s. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">swallar, slår, böljr</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> mot (smeker) stranden l. kinden:</text:span> mare terram appetens litoribus a-it, C.; fluctus salis alqd a-unt, Catl.; undæ a-entes, Ov., Pn.; auster, Val. Fl.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> prosperitas alicui, Sen.; aliquis philosophiæ, Val.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämta med, skämta, säga på skämt; skämtande häntyda</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (alludera) på ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>): Galba a-ens varie et copiose contra jus dicere, C.; nec plura a-ens, Vg.; versibus Homeri, Val.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allūdio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämta:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Antĕlūdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förespel:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka tillsammans:</text:span></text:span> paribus (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>), Hor. - plumæ in aquæ natantes, <text:soft-page-break/>Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spela under täcket:</text:span></text:span> cum aliquo, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lek</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> tillsammans; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hemligt, brottsligt förstånd,</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hemligt förstånd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn:</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collūsor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Medspelare:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. står i hemligt förstånd:</text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spela ut, till slut:</text:span></text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swinka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> söka sno sig undan, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krångla:</text:span></text:span> primo rem differre - deinde - nihil agere et d., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Narra, gäcka:</text:span></text:span> dolis alqm, Ter.; pati se d-i ab aliquo, C.; corvum hiantem, Hor.; terra prius falso partu d-et arantes, Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūdia</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Paus</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppehåll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i lek (fäktning):</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spela ifrån, af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn; i spel öfwerwinna ngn:</text:span> palmas alicui, Ppt.; militem in alea (Curc.); anulum te e-sit, Pt. Curc. 630.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fäktning wika undan </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Parera):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> quasi rudibus e., C.; rigidos cæstus motu, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.</text:span> = <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Listigt undwika; leka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bringa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på skam; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">narra, gäcka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngn, ngns rörelser, bemödanden o. d.):</text:span> cervus canes cursu e-it, Phdr.; sequentem, Vg.; magnas accusatoris minas; exspectationem; illam scientiam hac e-tis, C.; alqm fallaciā, Cs.; ultionem, verba alicujus, T.; Davus Chremeta senem, Hor.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Håna, göra spe af, begabba:</text:span></text:span> e-et, quum te victum senserit, Ter.; quamdiu nos etiam furor iste e-et?; e-imur facetius ab eo, quam putamus; vicissim alqm, C.; Cynicum Aristippus e-bat, Hor.; mores, instituta, res gestas (Romanorum Macedones), L.<text:line-break/>γ. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka:</text:span></text:span> quæ est ista ars e-entis ingenio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. leker med sin fyndighet, brukar den till lek, sophismer),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om hafwet: (leka) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spola upp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på stranden:</text:span> litus est, qua mare e-it, C. (alii: alludit); Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka på,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med:</text:span> chartis i-o, ubi quid datur otii, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span>: auro i-sæ vestes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lekfullt, sinnrikt stickade med -),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med (lek) okynne </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skada, förgripa sig på, skända; skämta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> bort, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på spel:</text:span> frondi uri et capreæ, Vg.; fortunis, dignitati, existimationi alicujus, C.; matri alicujus; corpus Vari (Germanus quidam); corpori, T.; vitam filii, Ter.; pecuniæ, Su.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Håna, förnärma, begabba, förlöjliga, göra narr af:</text:span></text:span> in alqm, C., Ter.; in aliquo, Ter.; certant (Trojani) i-re capto, Vg.; fortuna gaudet rebus humanis i., Hor.; miseros i-i nolunt; ab accusatoribus i-i; artem, præcepta rhetorum, C.<text:line-break/>4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Narra, bedraga:</text:span></text:span> i-sis Cretensibus ad Prusiam pervenit, N.; i-si pedes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af krafterna swikne)</text:span> vitiosum ferre recusant corpus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūdio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skämta med</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngn:</text:span> Gell. I. 7. 3.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begabberi</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ironi):</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblūdo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Leka,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fryntligt skämta (mot) med ngn:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spela öfwer</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. före; bildl.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förbereda sig till, öfwa sig:</text:span></text:span> Nero in peculiari theatro Pompejano <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för uppträdande på Pompeji theater)</text:span> p-bat, Pn.; Mariana rabies intra urbem quasi p-rat, Fl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prælūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: quasi p. pugnæ, Pn. ep.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlūdo</text:span>, si, sum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Inleda en fäktning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">börja leken; förbereda:</text:span></text:span> ipsis sententiis, quibus (<text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span>) p-runt, etiam pugnare possunt, C.; (taurus) ad pugnam sparsā p-it arenā, Vg.; per has mortalis ævi moras illi meliori et longiori vitæ p-itur, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlūdium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlūsio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förfäktning, -spel:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕlūdo</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gäcka igen, beswara gäckeri med g.:</text:span> jocos, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Luella <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lues,</text:span> em, e, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Farsot, pest, pest-smitta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i luft m. m.):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> tabida membris, corrupto cæli tractu, - arboribusque satisque venit l.; l. udo sublapsa veneno (colubri) pertemptat sensus, Vg.; dira, Ov.; terræ cælique l., Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> hæc l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om person)</text:span> ludos polluit, C.; l. (belli), T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ugdūnum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Gallien (Lyon).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lugdūnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūgeo,</text:span> xi, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sörja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en död (med tårar, åthäfwor, klädedrägt):</text:span> varia genera l-di, pædores, muliebres lacerationes genarum, pectoris, feminum, capitis percussiones; Clodii mortem æquo animo ferre nemo potest: l-et senatus - -; mortem alicujus, C.; matronæ Brutum annum, ut parentem, luxere, L.; nunc cassum lumine (Palamedem) l-ent, Vg.; matres Iliæ Hectorem luxere, Hor. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Bentl.);</text:span> fratrem, Ov.; pullo l-entes vellere lanæ, Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Begråta, sörja, beklaga:</text:span></text:span> fortunam, occasum reipublicæ; quid ego nunc non l-eam vitam hominum?, C.; l-ntes campi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liks. cittâ dolente, om helwetet hos Dante),</text:span> Vg.; vita l-da, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorg:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwer död: sorg, sorgeklagan, -tid, -drägt:</text:span> l. est ægritudo ex ejus, qui carus fuerit, interitu acerbo; Telamon iratus furere l-u filii videbatur; l-um tollit diuturnitas, C.; esse in l-u <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hafwa sorg),</text:span> Cs., L.; l. triginta diebus finitus est, L.; l-um sororis læto cultu mutare, T.; absint funere l-us, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorg, klagan, jemmer:</text:span></text:span> l-um ex re percipere, haurire; incidere in maximos l-us; esse in maximis l-bus; manere in l-u; confici, affligi l-u; l-um abstergere; l-u afficere alqm; l-um levare, C.; l. ubique, pavor et plurima mortis imago, Vg.; vos, quibus est virtus, muliebrem tollite l-um, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgbringande, sorglig:</text:span></text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.: clades, C. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctĭfĭcābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgsen:</text:span></text:span> Pac. ap. C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctĭsŏnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: vagitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sorgligt ljudande),</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorglig, jemmerfull; af sorg uppfylld</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerhopad:</text:span></text:span> dies l. reipublicæ; preces; prædicatio; exitium l-simum, C.; di multa neglecti dedere Hesperiæ mala l-osæ, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luctuōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: Varr.; l-ius, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perluctuōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket sorglig:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūgŭbris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till sorg hörande, sorg uttryckande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorge-; sorglig:</text:span></text:span> vestis, Ter.; ejulatio; sordes; carmen; ornatus, C.; domus, L.; præcipe l-es cantus, Melpomene, Hor.; vultus; verba, Ov.; res, C.; vagitus, Lucr.; bellum, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūgŭbria</text:span>, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgekläder:</text:span></text:span> induere; ponere, Ov.; sumere, Ppt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūgŭbre</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: Pt., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlūgeo</text:span>, xi, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wederbörligen sörja, sörja ut:</text:span></text:span> patriam e-xi jam et gravius quam mater unicum filium, C.; quum e-runt, purpuram sumunt, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Törne:</text:span></text:span> Fs.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Törne-:</text:span></text:span> falx, Varr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūmectum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">törnekratt:</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lumbrīcus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Regnmask; tarmmask:</text:span></text:span> sues effodiunt l-os; l-i nocent intestinis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lumbus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Länd:</text:span></text:span> viri, C.; muli, Hor.; leporis, Pn. = genitalia, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lumbāgo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">länd-, höftlamhet:</text:span> Fs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lumbĭfrăgium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ländbrott:</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lumbŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: suis, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlumbis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ländbruten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-lam:</text:span></text:span> perdix, Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kraftlös:</text:span></text:span> carmen, Ps. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlumbo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēbātus</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ländbruten; bruten:</text:span></text:span> quadrupes; radix, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stympa:</text:span></text:span> ne minutos numeros sequens concidat d-etque sententias, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlumbis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ländbruten;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kraftlös:</text:span></text:span> fractus et e. orator, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lumectum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luma.<text:line-break/>Lumen, Lumin . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūna</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (=luc-(i)-na <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> luceo, Cic.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Måne:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> l. accretione et decretione luminis - signat dies; l. laborat, C.; nova, plena l., Cs.; dimidia, dimidiata, Cato, Varr.; l. bicornis regina siderum; l. fulget, micat cælo sereno; pura mari renidet; l-a nascente; l-a imminente, Hor.; l. prima, crescens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i ny),</text:span> decrescens, senescens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i nedan),</text:span> deficiens <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmörkad);</text:span> l. pernox; l-æ coitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fullmåne),</text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personificerad: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mångudinnan:</text:span></text:span> C., poēt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">plur.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mån-phaser; månader:</text:span></text:span> l-æ sequentes ordine, Vg.; damna tamen celeres reparant cælestia l-æ, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Månsken; månljus natt:</text:span></text:span> per l-am oblati (sunt nobis) Hypanis Dymasque; roscida l., Vg.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halfmåne,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. prydnad på de romerske senatorernes stöflar:</text:span> Juv.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūnāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">månens, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mån-:</text:span></text:span> cursus, C.; currus, Ov.; dies, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halfmånformigt böja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kröka:</text:span></text:span> arcum, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūnātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Halfmånformig:</text:span></text:span> pelta, Vg.; lignum; cornu, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūnŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liten måne, ett slags damsmycke:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Månguden:</text:span></text:span> Cp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūnis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utan månsken, mörk:</text:span></text:span> nox, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūnius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlūnis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: nox <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nytändning):</text:span> Amm. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interlūnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nytändning:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūna, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Etrurien:</text:span> L., Ps. <text:line-break/>Lūnensis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luo,</text:span> lui, (luiturus, Cd.), 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twätta, skölja:</text:span></text:span> magna Græcia luitur profundo Ionio, Sil.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i relig. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> försoningsoffer; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rena:</text:span></text:span> l. per caprum, Qu.; insontes errore, Vfl.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gälda, betala:</text:span></text:span> æs alienum, Ct.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plikta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">umgälla, försona:</text:span></text:span> Paulus temeritatem collegæ sua morte; Lucretia stuprum voluntaria morte; sanguine innocentium hominum libido Verris luitur, C.; noxam pecuniā; scelus supplicio; peccata, L.; nemo stolidum consilium capite, Ct.; poenā commissă, peccata, Vg.; delicta majorum immeritus lues, Hor.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> capite l., L.; morte l., Vg. - pericula publica, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försona = afwända,</text:span> L.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (straff, till försoning):</text:span> poenas ob peccata, peccati, C., Hor.; supplicium, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luella</text:span> <text:line-break/>(luēla), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Plikt, bot:</text:span></text:span> sceleris, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span>: Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Abluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twätta, skölja ren; twätta, skölja af, bort:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> pedes; ita jactantur fluctibus (parricidæ), ut nunquam a-antur, C.; ova a-ta, Varr.; me flumine vivo, Vg.; pluviæ tempestates pulvinos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rabatter)</text:span> a-unt, Varr.; maculas e veste, Pn.; a-tā cæde (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blodet),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aftwå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (stundom genom symbolisk twagning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bortskölja, borttaga, -jaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ett ondt:</text:span> spargit - lauro rorante capillos et ”ablue præteriti perjuria temporis” inquit, Ov.; animi placatione a-itur perturbatio, C.; nigras sibi a-it umbras (terra, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i dagningen);</text:span> sitim a., Lucr.; maculam veteris industriæ laudabili otio, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ablūtio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twagning:</text:span></text:span> corporis, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Alluo</text:span>, ui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(spola upp), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flyta inwid, skölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hafwet stranden):</text:span> mare a-it, Vg.; unda coloniam a-it; moenia urbis a mari a-untur, C. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> Massilia barbariæ fluctibus a-itur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Uppsjö), öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> Romæ mira a. fuit, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŭvio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upplandning, -slamning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (land, s. tillkommit genom öfwerswämning):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Allŭvius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: ager, Agrim.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumluo</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringskölja, -flyta:</text:span></text:span> mari c-itur terra, L.; Rhenus tergum et latera insulæ, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlŭvio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Land-, öbildning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> genom uppsköljning från alla sidor:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Colluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skölja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (helt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwer, skölja ren:</text:span></text:span> amphoram, Cato; dentes; os c-tum, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŭvies</text:span>, ēi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŭvio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: sammanflöde</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rännsten, ränna;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> collectivt: samlad massa af orenlighet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sopor, dynga, pöl:</text:span></text:span> sues c-em potant, Pn.; c. fluit, Jct.; c-es cortis et ædificii; balineorum; coenum et fermentata c-es pestes vere emittit, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwirrad blandning, sammanblandning, förwirring; oredig massa, wirrwarr;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om mskor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afskum, slödder, pack:</text:span></text:span> homo ex omnium scelerum c-ne natus, C.; c-nem gentium et perturbationem auspiciorum afferre, L.; in ea, quæ perspicitur futura, c-ie (cum Cæsare) regnare; o præclarum diem, quum ex hac turba et c-ne (vitæ humanæ) discedam, C.; rerum c-o, L.; Drusi c-o, C.; Athenienses c-es nationum; c-em istam (servorum) non nisi metu coërcueris, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skölja åtskils, bortskölja; upplösa:</text:span></text:span> pluvia sata læta boumque labores, Vg.; aqua lateres, Cs.; aceto insignem bacam, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Späda upp, ut:</text:span></text:span> vinum aquā, Mt.; mella Falerno, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Bortskölja), förjaga; förswaga, -minska:</text:span></text:span> cura mero d-itur, Ov.; nebulas Titan, Sil.; molestias; auctoritatem, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wederlägga:</text:span></text:span> crimen; res leves, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Reda, utreda:</text:span></text:span> Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">part. pf.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūtus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppblötad, utspädd, swag, fadd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till smaken:</text:span> solum, Pn.; d-ius potare, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tydlig:</text:span> Amm.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlūtum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utspädd wätska:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlŭvium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortsköljning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (söndersköljning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerswämning;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> äfwen om en allmän öfwerswämning: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">syndaflod:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> flumen d-em meditatur agris, Hor.; imbribus glebæ ad d-em revocantur, Lucr.; tellurem effundit in undas d-o miscens, Vg.; d-um et conflagratio (mundi), Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förstöring:</text:span></text:span> d-um illud (i. e. excidium Trojæ), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīlŭvio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerswämma:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twätta, skölja ren; twätta bort, bortskölja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> corpus, Ov.; aquam, Col.; sanguinem; maculas vestium, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortskölja, aftwå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> fläck på samwete l. rykte:</text:span> maculas furtorum et flagitiorum innocentium sanguine; sordes suas (ɔ: infamiam) severitate judicandi; labem animi, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">twätta bort = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utplåna:</text:span></text:span> tales amicitiæ remissione usus sunt e-dæ, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Swira</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fråssa upp:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; stagna Mæotidis (i. e. aves <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">derifrån),</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlūtus</text:span>, -ior, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utspädd, fadd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till smaken:</text:span> irriguo nihil est e-ius horto, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēlŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utsköljning, utflöde, aflopp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af orenlighet; concr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">dy, dyngpöl, cloak:</text:span></text:span> ventris, Lucil.; oppida crebris ad e-em cuniculis cavata, Pn.; e-em siccandam conducere, Juv.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerswämning;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> öfwerswämmadt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wattenflöde:</text:span></text:span> sal provenit e-e maris arescente undā, T.; in proxima e-e (al.: alluvie) pueros exponunt, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utskärning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af land, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">jordras</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> genom öfwerswämmadt watten: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bråddjup, klyfta:</text:span></text:span> Ct.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upplösning, förderf:</text:span></text:span> labes et e. civitatis, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ē</text:span><text:bookmark text:name="_GoBack"/><text:span text:style-name="T2">lŭvio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utskärning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af watten, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> e-es exustionesque terræ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūtĭlis</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Illūtĭbĭlis), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oaftwättlig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> som ej genom twättning kan utplånas:</text:span> odor, Pt. Men. I. 2. 37.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illūtĭbarbus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Med smutsigt skägg:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Illŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppsjö, öfwerswämning, öfwerswämmadt watten:</text:span></text:span> aquarum i. principio rerum terras obrutas tenuit, Js.; in placida i-e spirantem (mulierem inveniunt), T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dy, gyttja, smuts:</text:span></text:span> currus i-e hærebant, Ct.; ancillula immunda i-e, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Interluo</text:span>, ui, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skölja, flyta emellan:</text:span></text:span> arva et urbes pontus i-it, Vg.; fretum Capreas et Surrentum, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twätta emellan,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> under en handling:</text:span> manus, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perluo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(pelluo), ui, ūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerskölja, twå, twätta, bada:</text:span></text:span> Cs., Hor., Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Polluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.: (por-luo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> polliceor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> liceor, possideo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> sedeo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beskölja,) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besudla, orena, besmitta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i physisk mening:</text:span> ore dapes, Vg.; afflatu urbes, Ov.; cuncta sanie, odore, contactu p., T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i religiös och moralisk mening: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Orena, oskära, ohelga, wanhelga, befläcka, kränka, skända</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (förgripa sig på):</text:span> cæremonias <text:soft-page-break/>incesto stupro p-it (Clodius); sacra p-ta et violata; jura scelere p.; ludos flagitio, C.; sacra profanaque; avaritia omnia p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förgriper sig på);</text:span> (a novis hominibus) nobilitas quasi p-ui consulatum credebat, Sa.; pax, amor p-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bruten, kränkt),</text:span> Vg.; domum stupro p., Hor.; feminam p. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skända);</text:span> nobilitatem familiæ, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollūtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Oren, okysk, fräck:</text:span></text:span> licentia, Sa.; (femina), L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Pollūbrum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Twättbäcken:</text:span></text:span> Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Impollūtus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obefläckad, okränkt, fläcklös:</text:span></text:span> virginitas, T.; fides, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skölja bort, spola, fösa bort:</text:span></text:span> fluctus pisces, silvas, Vg.; tempestas nives, Cs.; aqua terram, Col. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> pecuniam = profundere, Gell.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skölja, twätta:</text:span></text:span> manus in rore, Ov.; labra fonte caballino, Ps.; præcordia mulso, Hor.; se pleno auro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med den fulle bägaren),</text:span> Vg.; multa p-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(fuktad, drucken)</text:span> vappa, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bortsköljning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerswämning:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.; Romæ mira fuit p. (alii: alluvies), C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utflöde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af orenlighet, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">afföring:</text:span></text:span> ventris, Vg.; alvi, Col. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Prōlŭvio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> = proluvies a.: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕluo</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Åter inlösa:</text:span></text:span> Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Subluo</text:span>, ui, ūtum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skölja inunder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">flyta under, nedanför:</text:span></text:span> podicem, Mt.; radicem collis flumen, Cs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublŭvies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skarn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> under naglar l. klöfwar; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nagel-, hoftrång:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūpia, <text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>uppia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Germanien (Lippe).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŭpus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Warg, ulf:</text:span></text:span> rapax; infestus pecori; petit dente, Hor.; raptores l-i, Vg.; l-i in Algido visi, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i ordspråk:</text:span> l-o ovem committere (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sätta bocken till trädgårdsmästare);</text:span> l-um auribus tenere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om djerfwa företag),</text:span> Ter.; l-o agnum eripere (id.); homo homini l., Pt.; l. in fabula (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">när man talar om troll, komma de),</text:span> Ter., C. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om föremål, s. se ut l. bita som wargen:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gädda:</text:span></text:span> fluvialis, Varr.; Tiberinus, Hor. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Munstycke</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i betsel, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">taggigt betsel:</text:span></text:span> equus accipit ore duros l-os, Ov.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Båtshake</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (sök):</text:span> (in oppugnantes) l-i superne ferrei injecti ut - - in murum extraherentur, L.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Pors:</text:span></text:span> salictarius, Pn.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Spindel:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Warginna,</text:span></text:span> L. - = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sköka:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C., L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpānar</text:span>, āris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bordell:</text:span></text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpānāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">otuktig:</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: frena l-a, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">försedda med wargtänder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">taggiga,</text:span></text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpāti</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpāta</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m., n.</text:span> (sc. freni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> frena): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">taggiga betsel:</text:span> Vg., Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ŭpercus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (lupus, arceo, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wargfördrifwaren?):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">binamn för Faunus:</text:span> Js. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Fauni prester:</text:span> C. <text:line-break/>Lŭpercālis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: sacrum, Su. <text:line-break/>Lŭpercal, ālis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Luperci grotta wid palatinske kullen.</text:span><text:line-break/>Lŭpercālia, ium, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Luperci fest.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Warg-, warginne-:</text:span></text:span> ubera, C.; pellis, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpīnus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpīnum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wargböna, lupin:</text:span></text:span> Cato, Vg. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föreställde penningar på theatren:</text:span> (isto auro in barbaria boves pingues fiunt, Pt.); non - ignorat, quam distent æra l-is, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpillus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpīnāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lupinlik:</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpīnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.:</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är för l.:</text:span> Cato. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpīnārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lupinhandlande:</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">besöka bordeller:</text:span> Acc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭpŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Warginna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ss. skymford för qwinna):</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: os cullei: Fs. = culleus: Aus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lurco,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fråssare, wällusting:</text:span></text:span> Pt., C., Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lurco</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lurcor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Äta glupskt:</text:span></text:span> Non. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lurcĭnābundus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Lurchinābundus), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slukande:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūrĭdus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gulblek, askgrå, likblek:</text:span></text:span> dentes; pellis, Hor.; sulfur; horror, Ov.; sol, Pn.; mors, Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūror</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Likblekhet:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Oblūrĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gulblek:</text:span></text:span> spado, Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sublūrĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gulaktig:</text:span></text:span> cicatrix, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luscĭnia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> Hor. <text:line-break/>(<text:span text:style-name="T2">Luscĭnius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>): (Phdr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Näktergal:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luscĭniŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Luscus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Enögd:</text:span></text:span> C., Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luscīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lusciōsus</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luscĭtiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skumögd, swagsynt:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lusio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ludo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūsĭtānia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Portugal.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lūsĭtānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lusito <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ludo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ūsĭus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i Arcadien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>Lusor, -sorius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ludo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lustrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> luo? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sås.</text:span> monstrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> moneo, flustrum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> (Fs.) fluo?):<text:line-break/>I.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Renings-, försoningsoffer,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt det, s. i Rom anställdes hwart femte år wid census-förrättningens slut:</text:span> l-i faciendi (fundi agrique lustrandi) ergo, Cato; l. condere, C., L.; perficere, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf</text:span> <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">en tid af fem år;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> poet. i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tid, period:</text:span></text:span> quibus hoc l-o nihil solverant, etiam superioris l-i reddiderunt, C. Ep. Att. VI. 2; alterum, tertium; condere l. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">afsluta ett</text:span> quinquennium, Hor.; quinquennale ludicrum secundo l-o celebrabatur, T.; l-is labentibus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(under tidernas lopp),</text:span> Vg. <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smutspöl</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (jfr</text:span> col -, il-, proluvies), <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sump, moras</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (spec. ss. djurs håla l. ide):</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sues volutantur in l-is, Varr.; montes et invia l-a; deserta ferarum l-a, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skökohus, bordell;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> meton.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">liderligt lif, liderlighet:</text:span></text:span> ex l-is rapere aliquem, Pt.; in l-is ætatem degere; vino l-isque confectus, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till reningsoffer hörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Renings-:</text:span></text:span> sacrificium, L.; exta, Vg.; aqua Ov.<text:line-break/>b. = quinquennalis, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Femårig:</text:span></text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustrĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: dies, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">reningsdag för nyfödda barn (den 8:de l. 9:de),</text:span> Su., Mcb. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustrĭfĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Renande:</text:span></text:span> Vfl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rena</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med offer, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sona,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> anställa reningsoffer för ngn:</text:span> fundum; agros, Cato; coloniam; quum censor populum l-ret, bonis nominibus, qui hostias ducerent, eligebantur, C.; Capitolium; Servius Tullius exercitum omnem suovetaurilibus l-vit; urbem, L.; agros; viros purā undā; l-amur Jovi, Vg.; urbem, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mönstra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en här (hwarmed ofta reningsoffer war förenadt):</text:span> exercitum, C., Cs., L., Ct.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mönstra, öfwerskåda, granska, betrakta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i inre och yttre bem.):</text:span> pater Anchises inclusas animas superumque ad lumen ituras l-bat; Sol, qui terrarum flammis opera omnia l-as, Vg.; omnia ratione et animo l., C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bese, öfwerfara, öfwer-, genomwandra, kringfara:</text:span></text:span> Pythagoras Aegyptum; stella orbem, C.; Ausonium l-dum navibus æquor; muros equo, Vg.; Rhodope l-ta barbaro pede, Hor. - pericula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(genomgå),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustrāmen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Reningsmedel:</text:span></text:span> Vfl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rening, soning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> medelst offer:</text:span> Col.; exercitus, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Besökande, genomwandring, wandring:</text:span></text:span> municipiorum; solis; silvestres cursus l-esque, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustrātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genomwandrare:</text:span> orbis, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lustror</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hålla till i</text:span> lustra (II. b.): Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Bĭlustris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tioårig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= s. warar</text:span> 2 lustra): bello b-i superari, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Circumlustro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rundt omkring rena:</text:span></text:span> sulfure puro, Tib.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rundt omkring bestråla:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i tmesis),</text:span> Lucr.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kringfara:</text:span></text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collustro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerskåda:</text:span></text:span> oculis alqd, C., Vg., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Perlustro</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rena</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt, s. bars öfwer l. omkring:</text:span> paleas sulfure, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mönstra, öfwerskåda, betrakta:</text:span></text:span> omnia oculis, L.; alqd animo, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerfara, genomwandra:</text:span></text:span> loca, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lusus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Ludo.<text:line-break/>Lutamentum, Lutarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ŭtātius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lutensis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum.<text:line-break/>Luteolus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lūtum.<text:line-break/>Lutesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ŭtētia, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Gallien (Paris).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Luteus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> Lūtum.<text:line-break/>Lutito, Lŭto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum.<text:line-break/>Lūto <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luo. <text:line-break/>Lutosus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lutra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utter:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lutul . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lŭtum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lŭtum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(otwifwelaktigt af</text:span> luo; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr</text:span> rŭtus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> ruo): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blöt jord (lera), träck, slam, gyttja, smuts:</text:span></text:span> hæsitare in l-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl.),</text:span> Ter.; ex l-o et argilla factus; in l-o volutari, C.; udum et molle l. es (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildsam),</text:span> Ps.; l-o amica sus; l-o aspergi (in itinere), Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om mskor:</text:span> l. es, Pt.; o l.!, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. lefwer i gyttja:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtensis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. wäxer i gyttja:</text:span> Pu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppblötas, bli gyttjig:</text:span></text:span> litus, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭteus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som är af jord, träck, lera:</text:span></text:span> hirundo - l-um celsa sub trabe figit opus, Ov.; ædificium, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smutsig, gyttjig:</text:span></text:span> pedes, Pn.; l-um Rheni caput, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Usel, wärdelös:</text:span></text:span> homo; negotium, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭto</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bilda af</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bestryka, öfwersmörja med wåt jord, lera:</text:span></text:span> hirundo nidum, Calp.; granarium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lerslå),</text:span> Cato.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smörja:</text:span></text:span> (homo) l-tus amomis, Ps. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det hwarmed något bestrykes, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smetwerk:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtĭto</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Ritschl) l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtŭlo</text:span>, 1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nedsmutsa:</text:span></text:span> Pt. (semel).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŭtĭto</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Ritschl) l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŭtŭlo</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Collŭtŭlento</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Bergk),</text:span> 1.: id.: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēlŭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">belägga med lera, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lerslå:</text:span></text:span> habitationem, Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gyttjig:</text:span></text:span> ager, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lŭtŭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smutsig, gyttjig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> sus, C., Hor.; amnis, Ov.; palæstra (oleo uncta et arenā aspersa), Mt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om en författare, hwars stil liknas wid en flod:</text:span> fluit l. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(slammig, grumlig, mots.</text:span> liquidus), Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Smutsig, oren:</text:span></text:span> vitia; persona, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lūtum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wejde</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (s. färgar gult):</text:span> croceum, Vg.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūteus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gul, guldgul, eldgul, guldröd:</text:span></text:span> pallor, Hor.; Aurora, Vg.; sulfur, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūteum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gul färg:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eldgul </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brudslöja:</text:span></text:span> Catl.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lūteŏlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gulaktig:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lux <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Luceo.<text:line-break/>Luxur . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Luxus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Luxus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wriden ur led, förwriden:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ledwrickning, wred:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wrida ur led, förrycka, rubba</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ngt från deß plats:</text:span> membra l-ta, Pn.; reponere l-ta, Sen.; radices l-re, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēluxātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wriden ur led:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Luxus,</text:span> us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af samme stam, s.</text:span> I. luxus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppighet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prakt, lyx:</text:span></text:span> domus interior regali splendida l-u instruitur, Vg.; multa (in senatu) in l-um civitatis dicta decretumque, ne vasa solida auro cibis ministrandis fierent, T.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wällust, utswäfningar, liderlighet:</text:span></text:span> adolescens l-u perditus, Ter.; in vino et l-u, C.; (frigus et lassitudinem) l-u antecapere, Sa.; avaritia et l. ministrorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tjenstemännens),</text:span> T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxŭria</text:span>, ae <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxŭries</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppighet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppig wäxt, frodighet, saftrikhet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> l-em esse in herbis - etiam rustici dicunt, C.; segetum, Vg.; humoris (maris; mollis et fertilis nutrimenti), Pn. 9. 1.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span> (in Sulpicii oratione) in summa ubertate l. quædam inest, quæ stilo depascenda est, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppighet, wällefnad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lyx, öfwerdrift i mat, dryck, bohag m. m.):</text:span> l-a - senectuti foedissima est - sin vero libidinum etiam intemperantia accesserit, duplex malum est; odit populus Romanus <text:soft-page-break/>privatam l-am, publicam magnificentiam diligit; diffluere l-ā; in urbe <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i en stad, mots. till landsbygden)</text:span> l-es creatur; ex l-a avaritia, ex avaritia erumpit audacia, C.; nolo meis impensis (liberorum) ali augerique l-am, N.; diversis vitiis, avaritia et l-a, civitas laborat, L.; petulantia, libido, l. (Neronis), Su.; divitiarum l. cepit Græcos, Js.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utswäfningar, liderlighet:</text:span></text:span> mulierum corruptelæ et omnis ejusmodi l. et nequitia, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yrhet, sjelfswåld:</text:span></text:span> (animalium), Vfl.; l. morum (Alcibiadis), Js.; militaris, Aur. V.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxŭrio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxŭrior</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i kroppslig men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara yppig, frodas:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> vitis l-atur, Col.; seges membra l-ant, Ov. <text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. om stil: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara yppig, utswäfwande:</text:span></text:span> l-antia compescet, nimis aspera sano lēvabit cultu, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prunka, pråla, lysa:</text:span></text:span> facies deliciis novis, Ov.; arbores vere picturis variis, Pn.; liber umbilicis pictis; illa placet tellus, in qua res parva beatum me facit et tenues l-antur opes, Mt.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(syn.</text:span> lascivio) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara yr, yster, öfwerdådig; urarta till öfwerdåd, sjelfswåld,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm. till </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerdrift:</text:span></text:span> equus, Vg.; animi otio l-antur; gloriā, L.; rebus secundis l-re; litera malo meo l-ta est, Ov.; vereor, ne hæc lætitia nobis l-et et vana evadat; læta principia (decemviralis potestatis) nimis l-vere, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēluxŭrior</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utbreda sig alltför yppigt, frodigt:</text:span></text:span> vitis pampinis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxŭriōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= i wäxten yppig, alltför </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frodig:</text:span></text:span> frumenta, C.; pabula, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i lefnadssättet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppig, slösande, utswäfwande, wällustig:</text:span></text:span> nepos; lauta suppellex non l-i hominis, sed tamen abundantis; l-i persequuntur cujusque modi voluptates, C.; Alcibiades l., libidinosus, dissolutus, intemperans, N.; otio l-o (erat Sulla), Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwerhufwud: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utswäfwande, urartande, öfwerdådig:</text:span></text:span> amor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(otillbörlig),</text:span> Ov.; ea lætitia patribus nimis l-a fuit, L. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Luxŭriōse</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Yppigt, utswäfwande:</text:span></text:span> vivere, C., N.; epulari, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆æus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(befriaren) = Liber, Bacchus; meton.: winet:</text:span> Hor. </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆căbas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cæus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Arcadien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆cæus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cambes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆cambēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ly̆cāon,</text:span> ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags warg:</text:span> Mel.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆cāŏnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af L.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ly̆cāŏnĭus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cāŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Ly̆cāŏnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk och land i mindre Asien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆cāŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cēum, <text:line-break/>Ly̆cīum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett gymnasium i Athen (i hwilket Aristoteles underwisade).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lychnus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lampa:</text:span></text:span> dependent laquearibus l-i, Vg.; pensiles l-i, Lucr.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lychnis</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">namn på en ädelsten, blommor m. m.:</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lychnītes</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en art marmor.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lychnŏbĭus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. lefwer wid lampan, gör natten till dag:</text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lychnūchus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lampställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hwarpå lampor hängde); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ljus-,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (lamp-)</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-krona:</text:span></text:span> C.; elephanti gestabant l-os, Su.; pensiles l-i, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ellychnĭum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lampweke:</text:span></text:span> Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">land i mindre Asien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆cĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cĭdas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆ciscus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Ly̆cisca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Lycīum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Lyceum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆co, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cŏmēdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆cŏmēdēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ly̆cŏphōs,</text:span> ōtis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gryning:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cŏphro, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cōrĭas, ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en hafsnymph.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cōris, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cormas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cortas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cōtas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>yctus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad på Creta.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lyctĭus <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆curgus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆curgēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆cus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. person-, flod-, stadsnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ȳdus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> -di, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i Asien, Lyder (äfwen Etrusker).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lȳdus, <text:line-break/>Lȳdĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lydisk, etrurisk).</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lȳdĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lydien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ygdămus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lympha,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (v. gr.?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Watten</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (klart, jfr.</text:span> limpidus): dant (ministri) manibus l-as; fluviatilis, Vg.; l-æ puteales, Lucr.; obliquo laborat l. fugax trepidare rivo, Hor.; liquida l., Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personific.:</text:span> L-am precor - quoniam sine aqua omnis arida - agricultura, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lympho</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra ursinnig, förtrolla, skrämma från wettet:</text:span></text:span> Vfl., St.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphans</text:span>, tis (Pn.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förryckt, ursinnig, rasande, galen:</text:span></text:span> milites velut l-i et attoniti munimentis suis trepido agmine incidunt, L.; l-ati discurrunt, Ct.; l-ati repente centuriones evadunt, T.; mens l-a, H or. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphātĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.: pavor, L.; somnia, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphātĭcum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wattenskräck, yrsel, galenskap:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Lymphor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span> = lympha: Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>yncestæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folk i Macedonien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lyncestĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ynceus, ĕi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">styrman på Argo, berömd för sin skarpa syn, deraf = skarpsynt:</text:span> quis est tam L. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(l.</text:span> lyncēus)?, C. <text:line-break/>Lyncēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: l-i oculi, Hor. <text:line-break/>Lyncīdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>yncus, i:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn.</text:span><text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Macedonien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lynx,</text:span> cis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">c.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lo:</text:span></text:span> maculosa, Vg.; timida, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ly̆ra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyra, (lyrisk poesi, sång):</text:span></text:span> Themistocles quum in convivio recusaret l-am, habitus est indoctior, C.; l-ā celebrare (alqm.); sollers l-æ, Hor.; digitis increpare l-am, Ov.; institui l-ā, Qu.; non hæc jocosæ conveniunt l-æ, Hor.; Pindarica, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ly̆rĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyrans;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till l. hörande; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lyrisk:</text:span></text:span> modi, Ov.; vatibus l-is inserere alqm, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ly̆rĭci</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lyriske skalder, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyrici:</text:span></text:span> Qu. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ly̆rĭca</text:span>, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Lyrik, lyriska dikter:</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ly̆ristes</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ly̆rĭcen</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lyrspelare:</text:span> Pn., St.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>yrcēus i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">källa i Arcadien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lyrcēus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>yrnēsus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Troas.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lyrnēsĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lyrnēsis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆sander, dri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆sănĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆sĭas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Ly̆sĭăcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>ȳsĭmăchus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Lȳsĭmăchīa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">staden.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆sippus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ly̆sis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upplösning:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kranslist</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (archit.):</text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆sis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">L</text:span>y̆so, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lytron,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lösepenning, -summa:</text:span></text:span> Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lytta,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mask (under tungan), som gör hundar rasande:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span> =<text:line-break/>a. 1000.<text:line-break/>b. Marcus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förnamn).</text:span> <text:line-break/>M’ = Manius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förnamn).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(Măcar</text:span> ăris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lycklig.)</text:span> Insulæ macaron = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de saliges öar:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăcăreus, ĕi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> ĕos, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Măcărēis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dotter af M.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>accius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slägtn. (jfr</text:span> Plautus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Maccus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">characters-mask i</text:span> fabulæ Atellanæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Harlekin):</text:span> Gramm., Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăcĕdo <text:line-break/>(Măcĕdon), ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: - <text:span text:style-name="T1">pl.</text:span> -dŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Macedonier.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Măcĕdŏnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Macedonien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Măcĕdŏnĭus, <text:line-break/>Măcĕdŏnĭcus, <text:line-break/>Măcĕdŏniensis (Pt.), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măcellum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Măcellus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: Mt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kött-torg, mattorg; torgwaror:</text:span></text:span> venio ad m., rogito pisces, agninam, bubulam, Pt.; annona in m-o cara est, C.; pernicies, barathrum m-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om en storätare),</text:span> Hor.; ex horto plebei m-um, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcellārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: taberna, Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcellārius</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Köttmånglare:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măceo,</text:span> ēre:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcesco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om</text:span> mācero <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">är stamslägtadt, wäl ursprungl. = wara lös, swamlig): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara mager; magra:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcer</text:span>, cra, crum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mager</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om mskor, djur, wäxter, jord), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">torr, utmärglad:</text:span></text:span> homo, Hor., Qu.; taurus, Vg.; partes corporis m-rimæ, Sen.; solum exile et m-um, C.; ager m-ior, Cato; agellus, Hor.; vitis, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcĕries</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> (Afr.):<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcrĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcrĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magerhet:</text:span></text:span> Vitr., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcresco</text:span>, crui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magra, bli mager:</text:span></text:span> volucres m-unt, Varr.; invidus alterius mācrescit rebus opimis, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmăcresco</text:span>, ĕre: Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permăcer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: Ce.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕmăcresco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">magra igen:</text:span> Sil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macror <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcies</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magerhet, utmärgladt tillstånd; torrhet:</text:span></text:span> homo m-e torridus; corpus m-e extabuit, C.; corrumpi m-e, Cs.; m-e confectă suprema, Vg.; m. et nova febrium cohors, Hor.; tussis et m. equi; m. soli, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcĭlentus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utmagrad:</text:span></text:span> os, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcio</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmăcio</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra mager;</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">utmärglas, magra;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (om watten) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">minska, komma att utsina:</text:span></text:span> armentum e-tum; densitas plantas e-at, Col.; mare m-atur, Sol.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magerhet:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Pac. (alii: macror).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăcer, cri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Maceratio, -resco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macero.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mācĕria,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mācĕries</text:span>, ēi, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gärdesgård, mur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> kring trädgård, park, egor, hus, af naturlig, rå l. bränd sten:</text:span> m. est fabrile sæpimentum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mots. till häck, gärde af stockar, wall),</text:span> e lapide (aut) e lapidibus coctilibus (aut) e lateribus crudis, aut ex terra et lapillis compositis in formis, Varr.; horti, Ter., L.; nulla m., nulla casa, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Măceries <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macer, Maceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mācĕro,</text:span> 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppblöta, -mjuka, göra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (koka) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">mör:</text:span></text:span> salsamenta pulcre, Ter.; alqd sale; lana m-ta, Sen.; semen lacte, Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttära, förtära, plåga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till kropp l. sinne:</text:span> fame alqm, L.; iste morbus multos m-at, Pt.; penitus lentis m-or ignibus (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">swartsjuka),</text:span> Hor.; anime mi, noli te m-re, Ter.; mærore m-ri, Pt.; desiderio res alqm m-at, L.; <text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">abs. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gräma sig:</text:span></text:span> m-or, quod sim tibi causa dolendi, Ov. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mācĕrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: calcis, Vitr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mācĕresco</text:span>, ĕre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bli mör:</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmācĕrātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eller:</text:span> emăceratus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uttärd:</text:span></text:span> morbo, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permācĕro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppblöta:</text:span></text:span> Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macesco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Maceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăcĕtæ, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span> = Macedones.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măchæra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kort swärd, pamp), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dolk:</text:span></text:span> Pt. - <text:span text:style-name="T1">n. pr. m.</text:span>: Juv. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măchærŏphŏrus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Măchærŏphŏros), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Drabant:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăchærus, untis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bergsnamn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>achanĭdas, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">grek. personn.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăchāon, ŏnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">gr. myth. personn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Măchāŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăchĭmus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hundnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Māchĭna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (v. gr. μηχανή): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(machin), redskap, anstalt, hwarmedelst l. hwarifrån man sätter ngt i rörelse l. gör ett arbete:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Maskin, instrument, ställning, konstbyggnad;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> serskildt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">byggnadsställning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (”stallage”); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hißwerk, -maskin; krigsmaskin:</text:span></text:span> m-am fabricare exigendo operi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nivelleringsinstrument);</text:span> m. fabricanda est, qua clausa jumenta bovesque curentur, Col., amica de m-a (= catasta, q. v.) emere, C.; m. ædificationum, Pn.; lapidem m-ā apportare, C.; trahunt siccas m-æ carinas, Hor.; m-is urbem expugnare, Sa.; m. belli, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. m. mundi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(werldsbyggnaden, -maskinen),</text:span> Lucr., Luc.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl. uttryck för wåldsamma l. listiga anslag:</text:span> m-is percellere, labefactare, capere alqm; adhibere m-as ad alqm; commoliri, C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: scientia <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(att bygga maskiner, mechanik),</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">konstigt inrättad:</text:span> mola, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på konstrikt sätt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppfinna, inrätta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (construera), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">göra anstalter:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om materiella ting:</text:span> Tritonem (artifex) ita m-tus est, ut vento circumageretur, Vitr.; ad usum orationis incredibile est quanta opera m-ta natura sit, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppfinna, bereda:</text:span></text:span> hæc duo musici ad voluptatem m-ti sunt, versum atque cantum; Niobe sibi ipsa pestem videtur m-ri, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">listigt l. lömskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppspinna, anstifta, stämpla:</text:span></text:span> astutiam aliquam, Pt.; aliud quiddam; calamitatem civibus; pestem in alqm, C.; perniciem senatoribus, Sa.; necem alicui, L.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnāmentum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Maskin, redskap:</text:span></text:span> turres m-aque alia (belli), L.; m-a et artes oppugnationum, T.; m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om sinnena),</text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(konstig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">inrättning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anstalt) Mechanism, maskineri;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> concr.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">maskin,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sersk. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krigsmaskin:</text:span></text:span> m-e movere alqd; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bildl.)</text:span> judex tamquam m-e aliqua tum ad severitatem tum ad remissionem animi est contorquendus, C.; m-em instituere, promovere, Cs.; turres, vineæ aliæque m-es, Sa.; L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Konst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> att inrätta l. uppfinna, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">mechanisk skicklighet:</text:span></text:span> data est bestiis quibusdam m. quædam et sollertia (ut araneolis), C.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Listig anläggning, list:</text:span></text:span> Jct.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mechanicus, byggmästare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (constructör):</text:span> Archimedes inventor ac m. bellicorum tormentorum operumque, L.; Nero exstruxit domum magistris ac m-bus Severo et Celere, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anstiftare, tillställare:</text:span></text:span> horum omnium scelerum <text:soft-page-break/>improbissimus m., C.; belli, L.; doli, T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anstiftarinna:</text:span></text:span> Sen. trag.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillställning:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māchĭnōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">konstigt inrättad:</text:span> navigium, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macies, Macilentus, Macio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Maceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măcis</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcris</text:span>, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en krydda:</text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Maceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ācra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">flod i N. Italien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macresco <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macer, Maceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ăcrīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macis.<text:line-break/>Macritas, -critudo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macer, Maceo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ācrŏbii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(de långlifwade): folkslagsnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ācrŏbius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mācrŏchēra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: tunica. m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med långa ärmar),</text:span> Lpd.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>āchrŏchir, īros, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">långhändt, tilln. för en persisk konung:</text:span> N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mācrŏcollum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Regalpapper</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (p. i stort format):</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mācrŏlŏgĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">widlyftighet i föredrag (longör):</text:span> Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Macror <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Macor, Maceo.<text:line-break/>Mactea <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Matetea.<text:line-break/>Mact . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se för öfrigt</text:span> Mactus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mactus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blott i casus recti förekommande partic. af ett obrukl. verb., (besl. med</text:span> magnus, magis? <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr dock Madv. i företalet till latein. Gramm.</text:span> p. XIII; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr Curtius, griechische Etymologie</text:span> p. 153.):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ökad) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ärad, prisad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> blott förekommande prædicativt med</text:span> esse <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(utsatt l. underförstådt) i anropanden l. lyckönskningar, i formerna</text:span> mactus (raro), macte (<text:span text:style-name="T1">vocat.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l. wäl snarare</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i st. f.</text:span> mactus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> ipse, ille <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i st. f.</text:span> ipsus, ollus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen om flera subj.),</text:span> macti:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i böner till gudar, när offer frambäras:</text:span> Jane pater, sis mihi m-us hoc fercto; Jupiter, m-e hoc vino inferio esto, Cato.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i berömmande l. lyckönskande tilltal till mskor: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">War prisad; heder och tack; hell dig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">eder; lycka till, förträffligt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (med l. utan en</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">för den egenskap, hwarför ngn prisas l. lyckönskas):</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i direct tal:</text:span> m-e virtute esto, L., Hor., Sen.; m-e virtute diligentiaque esto; m-e virtute, milites Romani, este, L.; m-e virtute!, C.; m-e nova virtute, puer, sic itur ad astra, Vg.; m-e hac gloria, hoc merito, Pn.; (ejectus est Plancus a Buthrotiis) m-e!, C.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i indirect tal:</text:span> juberem (te) m-e virtute esse, si pro mea patria ista virtus staret, L. <text:line-break/>2. m-a hostia = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">offrad, enl.</text:span> Serv.<text:line-break/>3. boves Lucæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(elephanter, i fältslag)</text:span> ferro male m-æ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">illa tilltygade, (se</text:span> macto), Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Macto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af verbalst.</text:span> mag- i magnus?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">förstora, utrusta med ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">syn.</text:span> augeo):<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ngt godt: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyckliggöra, hedra smycka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> m-ri triumpho, Enn.; honoribus m-re alqm, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">serskildt i religiös betydelse:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hedra, ära</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med offer:</text:span> extis deos manes, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillreda ett offer l. smycka ett offerdjur (med blommor, salt m. m.); deraf i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Offra (slagta):</text:span></text:span> Latinas m., C. (poēt.); ferctum m., Cato; porcus molā m-tus, Varr.; nigras pecudes, Lucr.; victimas, C.; juvencos, Vg.; hostiam, Hor.; caprum, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen om menniskor ss. offer, i mer o. mindre eg. bet.:</text:span> eorum furori nisi cessissem, in busto Catilinæ m-tus essem, C.; hostes Orco, Telluri, dis manibus m-re, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf ock i allm.</text:span><text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dräpa, döda:</text:span></text:span> C. (poēt.), L.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med ngt ondt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Belägga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i sw. med förändrad construction: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">tillfoga), straffa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">pass.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lida):</text:span></text:span> infortunio m-re alqm; malo et damno m., Pt.; supplicio, morte m-re alqm; malo m-ri, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mactābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: plaga, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">dödlig,</text:span> Lucr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mactātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. dräper:</text:span> Sen.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mactātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slagtande, offring:</text:span></text:span> Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măcŭla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläck:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: (fläck på en kropp, så wäl naturlig l. med flit anbragt, s. wanställande l. orenande):</text:span> corporis m. nævus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(födslomärke),</text:span> C.; bos insignis m-is; albæ, pullæ m-æ, Vg.; marmoris, Pn.; m-as e facie tollere, e vestibus, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: moralisk </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläck, skamfläck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på seder l. rykte; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fel:</text:span></text:span> m-as furtorum et flagitiorum sanguine innocentium eluere; adolescentiæ (alicujus) m-æ; m-ā afficere, aspergere alqm; alicui m-as æternas inurere; delenda vobis est illa m. Mithridatico bello suscepta, C.; hanc m-am (avaritiæ) effugere debemus, Ter.; ubi plura nitent in carmine, non ego paucis offendar m-is, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläck</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">plätt, enstaka punkt:</text:span></text:span> habitatur in terra raris et angustis locis et quasi m-is, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Maska, lucka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i nät, stickning m. m.:</text:span> reticulum minutis m-is, C.; grandes (retis), Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläcka; befläcka:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> totum corpus (ægri) m-atur luridis maculis, Pt.; terram tabo m., Vg.; ferrum sanguine, Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> nemora Latiaris Jovis stupro et scelere; splendorem alicujus (turpi) negotio, C.; ne parricidio partus suos (Sabinarum) m-rent (Romani et Sabini) -, L.; Pausanias gloriam turpi morte m-vit, N.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläck:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commăculo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(helt) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Befläcka, besudla, nedsöla:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> manus sanguine, Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> se ambitu, C.; te cum Jugurtha - miscendo - c-as, Sa.; flagitiis, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmăcŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utrensa, uttaga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fläck), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rena</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (från fläck):</text:span> nigras vitiligines, Pn.; argentum e-tum et candefactum, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Immăcŭlo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fläcka:</text:span></text:span> Fr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Immăcŭlābĭlis</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Immăcŭlātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Obefläckad:</text:span></text:span> conscientia, Aus., Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măcŭlōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Full af fläckar, fläckig:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">= spräcklig, plättig:</text:span> lynx; auguis, Vg.; color, Col.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nedfläckad:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. bet.:</text:span> facies, Pt.; vestis, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wanryktad, oren, skamlig:</text:span></text:span> senator, C.; mos et lex m-um edomuit nefas, Hor.; vir omni dedecore, m., T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mădeo,</text:span> ui, 2.:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara wåt, fuktig, drypa:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> m-ent parietes (vino); coma m-ens, C.; metu m-o <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swettas af -),</text:span> Pt.; sanguine terra, Vg.; os fletu; humus rore, Ov.; tergus humore, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fuktad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">drucken, öfwerlastad:</text:span></text:span> vino m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och absol.</text:span> m., Pt.; non festa luce m-re est rubor, Tib.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flöda, wara indrucken</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">öfwerflöda, wara full</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af:</text:span> Socraticis sermonibus m-et <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> imbuo) Corvinus, Hor.; fercula deliciis, Ppt.; pectora voce Cecropia, Mt.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara (mör</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> =) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kokt:</text:span></text:span> facite, ut m-ant: ne mihi incocta detis, Pt.; igni m., Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mădĕfăcio</text:span>, fēci, factum, 3.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dränka, wäta, fukta</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngt:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> imbuti sanguine gladii vel potius m-facti; Græciam sanguine, C.; terram nectare, Ov.; sanguis fusus - herbas m-fecerat, Vg.; cæde Philippi m-fient, Ov. - glebam pluvia, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra drucken:</text:span></text:span> vos m-facitis, quum ego sim siccus, Pt.; multo m-factus Iaccho; Col.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppblöta, göra mör:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mădesco</text:span>, dui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Inch.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa wåt, genomdränkt:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> robora (aquā), Vg.; tellus nubibus pluvioque austro, Ov.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa drucken:</text:span></text:span> Fr.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppmjukas, blifwa mör:</text:span></text:span> ungula, Col.; in coctura brassica, Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mădĭdus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wåt, drypandc:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> fasciculus aquā, C.; vestis, Vg.; genæ, Ov.; radix suco, Pn.; m-a Capena (porta, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwaröfwer gick en wattenledning),</text:span> Juv.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fuktad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beskänkt:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flödande, full</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> libelli jocis lascivis, Mt.<text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppblötad, mör,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (genomkokt):</text:span> semina m-ora, Pn.; sumen thynni, Mt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mădĭde</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: m. madere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(liks. genomfull):</text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mădĭdo</text:span>, 1.: m-ta spongia, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">genomdrucken,</text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mădor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäta:</text:span></text:span> Sa.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wätska:</text:span></text:span> Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commădeo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara genom-mör:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēmădesco</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmădesco</text:span>, dui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa wåt:</text:span></text:span> Ov. (semel).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīmădesco</text:span>, dui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förrinna, gå i watten:</text:span></text:span> d-uere nives, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Immădesco</text:span>, dui, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa wåt:</text:span></text:span> lacrimis genæ, Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permădĕfăcio</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomfukta, göra wek:</text:span></text:span> amor cor, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permădesco</text:span>, dui, 3.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa genomwåt, -drucken:</text:span></text:span> terra pluviis, Col. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förwekligas:</text:span></text:span> animus deliciis, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mădulsa</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Drucken:</text:span></text:span> probe abeo m., Pt. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(enl.</text:span> Paul. Diac. p. 126. 8. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> madeo).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>æander <text:line-break/>(Mæandros <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæandrus), dri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slingrande flod i Asien. - deraf:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slingring, ranka</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett broderi l. en wäfnad:</text:span> circum chlamydem purpura duplici M-o cucurrit, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krokwäg, slingerbult:</text:span></text:span> C., Gell. <text:line-break/>Mæandrĭcus, <text:line-break/>Mæandrĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>æcēnas, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. cognomen, märkwärdigt genom</text:span> C. Cilnius M., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Augusti wän, efter hwilken wittra yrkens beskyddare kallas Mæcenater.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæcēnātiānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>æcius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ædi, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">thraciskt folk.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mædĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mædĭca, æ, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mædernes land.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ælius <text:line-break/>(Melius), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mæna</text:span> <text:line-break/>(mēna), ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fisk</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">-art:</text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ænălus <text:line-break/>(Mænălos), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Mænăla, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">berg i Arcadien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mænălĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Mænălis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">patronym.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mænălĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mænas,</text:span> ădis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mænad</text:span> i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inspirerad l. i hänryckning stadd qwinna, wanl. = Bacchant:</text:span> Ov., Ppt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ænius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn:</text:span> columna M-a, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på</text:span> forum R., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid hwilken kroppsstraff werkställdes.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæniānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mæniānum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Balcon, altan; logerad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på en theater l. amphitheater:</text:span> Varr., Val., Vitr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>æŏnes, um, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslag i Lydien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæŏnĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mæonien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæŏnĭdes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Mæonier:</text:span> vivet M. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(= Homerus),</text:span> Tenedos dum stabit et Ide, Ov. <text:line-break/>Mæŏnis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Mæŏnĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>æōtis, ĭdis (idos), <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Azowska sjön. - äfwen</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> = Mæotica. <text:line-break/>Mæōtĭcus, <text:line-break/>Mæōtĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mæreo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(moereo), ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sörja</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = wara försänkt i stum sorg</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. röjer sig i anletsdrag och utseende öfwerhufwud (wäl äfwen i tårar);</text:span> m. est cum silentio dolere, Serv.]; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wara förkrossad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af sorg, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wara bedröfwad,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">aliqua re</text:span>; <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T1">rem</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sörja, begråta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">öfwer ngns död:</text:span> (m. a marcere, quod corpus etiam marcet, Varr.); nemo m-et suo incommodo: dolent fortasse et anguntur, sed illa lugubris lamentatio fletusque m-ens ex eo est, quod eum, quem dileximus, vitæ commodis privatum arbitramur; m-re eventu (Scipionis); mortem filii graviter, C.; m-entem (maritum) carpi, Vg.; viro (mortuo), Tib.; insignibus lugentium abstinebant, altius animis m-bant, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> afflictus, debilitatus, m-ens (reus); alienis bonis m-re; calamitatem reipublicæ; casum alicujus; (patriam) nimis tarde concidere m-bant, C.; sola domo m-et vacua (Dido, relicto Aenea), Vg.; fugam Cinaræ; regium genus et penates iniquos, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mæror</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bitter) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorg, bedröfwelse,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> djup </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nedslagenhet:</text:span></text:span> m. est ægritudo flebilis; quam civitati carus fuerit (Scipio), m-e funeris indicatum est; accedunt ægritudines, molestiæ, m-es, qui animos exedunt; m. venit ad aliquem; dare se m-i; in m-e versari, jacere; m-e affligi, urgeri, confici, lacerari; m-em minui, dolorem non potui; m-em deponere, C.; cum m-e et luctu vitam exigere, Sa.; m-e gravi ad terram deduci, Hor.; m-e premi, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mæstus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgsen, bedröfwad,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> djupt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">nedslagen:</text:span></text:span> m-o et conturbato vultu; senex m. et sordidatus; tristis erat Calchas, m-ior Ulixes, C.; m-um silentium; fortunā publicā m-ior, quam suā, L.; m-um timorem mittite; in somnis m-simus Hector visus adesse mihi, Vg.; hoc genus omne m-um ac sollicitum est cantoris morte Tigelli; m-um omni tempore vivere; tristia m-um vultum verba decent, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorglig, bedröflig:</text:span></text:span> aræ; ignis, Vg.; funera, Ov.; m-i loci visuque ac memoria deformes <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Vari slagfält),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mæste</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mæstĭter</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgligt, bedröfligt:</text:span></text:span> C., Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mæstĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Mæstĭtūdo, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Pt.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sorgsenhet, nedslagenhet, dysterhet, wemod:</text:span></text:span> m-æ resistere; esse in m-a; pellere ex animis m-am; (flebiles modi) totis theatris inferunt m-am; orationis severitas et quasi m., C.; tacita m. defixit (Albanorum ex patria migrantium) animos; incessit animum, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Submæstus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt bedröfwad:</text:span> Amm.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>æsia silva, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wid Veji.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ævius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mæviānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Maga <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Māgālia,</text:span> ium, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(puniskt ord): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hyddor, kojor:</text:span></text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Mage <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magis, Magnus.<text:line-break/>Magīa, Magic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magus.<text:line-break/>Magida <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Magis.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măgīrus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgīriscium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kock:</text:span></text:span> Lpd., Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgīra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kok-konst:</text:span></text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Măgis,</text:span> ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgĭda</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fat</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skål</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (räknas af</text:span> Varro <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till</text:span> ”vasa in mensa escaria”): nihil distat hac magis illa, Hor. Sat. II. 2. 29. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr Tidskrift for Philol. etc.</text:span> I. 38. 65.); lances antiqui m-as appellaverant, N. ap. Pn. XXXIII. 52.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Magis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măgister,</text:span> stri, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(beslägtadt med</text:span> magnus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förman, föreståndare, styresman, uppsyningsman:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> m. populi (= dictator); m. equitum; m. morum (= censor); m. societatis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bolags förman, dirigent);</text:span> m. scripturæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för klöfskatten);</text:span> cujus bona ex edicto possidentur, cui m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(curator l. god man i concurs)</text:span> et domini constituuntur, C.; dictator moderator et m. consulibus appositus; sacrorum; navis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kapten);</text:span> regii pecoris m. Faustulus erat, L.; excutitur pronusque m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(styrmannen)</text:span> volvitur in caput; ipse gubernaclo rector subit, ipse m.; pecoris, ovium m., <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">äfwen absol. = herde,</text:span> Vg.; fingit equum docilem tenera cervice m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(stallmästare),</text:span> Hor.; operarum; chori, Col.; m-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förmän)</text:span> vicorum, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skolföreståndare, läromästare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för barn), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">skollärare, lärare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (till yrket):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. = literator, grammaticus, rhetor: bonarum, liberalium artium m-i; pueri exercentur apud m-um; ludi literarii, ludi magister, C.; sævo m-o dictata reddere, Hor.; m. eloquentiæ, Qu.; occidit miseros crambe repetita m-os, Juv.; unicus m., Su.; m-um exuere (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">komma ur skolan),</text:span> T.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ss. tilltalsord till en grammaticus,</text:span> Gell.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om lärare i musik, fäktareskolors föreståndare</text:span> (lanistæ) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">m. m.:</text:span> qui Pythia cantat tibicen, didicit prius extimuitque m-um, Hor.; m. hic Samnitium (gladiatorum) summa jam senectute est et quotidie commentatur, C.; nullius addictus jurare in verba m-i (i. e. lanistæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl.),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. l. med utwidning af begreppet: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lärare:</text:span></text:span> stilus est optimus dicendi m.; virtutis auctores et m-i (Stoici); ille non intelligendi solum, sed etiam dicendi gravissimus auctor et m.; usus m. est optimus, C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistra</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skol-</text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förestånderska; lärarinna:</text:span></text:span> ludo - m-am esse, Ter.; philosophia m. vitæ; vita (rustica) m. parsimoniæ, C.; non hæc humanis opibus, non arte m-a proveniunt - major agit deus, Vg.; culpā potare m-ā, Hor.; consuetudo loquendi m., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistĕrium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förmanskap, föreståndareskap, förmans</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppsyningsmans embete:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> morum m. (ɔ: censura); conviviorum m-a (= regna vini), C.; equitum; collegii, Su.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Läroembete, underwisning:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistrālis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">föreståndare l. lärare tillhörig:</text:span> Vop.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistĕro</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistro</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förestå:</text:span></text:span> Sp. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistrātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgistrātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Embete, befattning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i staten:</text:span> m-um petere; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om folket)</text:span> mandare, dare; m-um adipisci, assequi, consequi, obtinere, inire, habere, gerere, peragere; m-um abdicare; abdicare se m-u; abire m-u; in m-u gerere aliquid, C.; capere, abrogare alicui; m-um N., L.; m-ui summo (apud Gallos) præesse, Cs.; m-um ingredi, Sa.; continuare m-um <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(behålla för flera år, omwäljas till - -),</text:span> Sa., L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Embetsman</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (högre och lägre), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">(myndighet;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> när det brukas om de högste embetsmännen = regent, regering, öfwerhet):</text:span> m-bus leges, populo præsunt m-us; m. est lex loquens, lex autem mutus m.; m. personam gerit civitatis, C.; m-us seditiosi; m-us rogare; oppida per m-us administrare; m-us minores <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i mots. till consuler, prætorer, censorer ss.</text:span> majores, Gell.), Sa.; (apud Hæduos) singuli m-us creari atque regiam potestatem annum obtinere consueverant; m-us, qui bello præsint et vitæ necisque habeant potestatem, deliguntur, Cs.; annui m-us; concessum est, ut plebi sui m-us essent sacrosancti (tribuni), L.; jura m-usque legunt sanctumque senatum, Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magmentum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> magnus): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillägg till ett offer:</text:span> Varr. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magmentārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Magnanim . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Animus.<text:line-break/>Magnarius <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>agnes, ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Magnessa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">folkslagsnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Magnēsĭa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lands- och stads - namn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Magnēsĭus, <text:line-break/>Magnētĭcus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Magnētarches, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">högste embetsmannen i Magnesia (i Thessalien):</text:span> L. <text:line-break/>Magnētis, ĭdis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A. f.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Magnes,</text:span> ētis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magnet:</text:span></text:span> trahit ferrum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Magni . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magnus.<text:line-break/>Magnopere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> III. Opus 3. b.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magnus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Comp.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Major</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Sup.</text:span>: <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Maxĭmus</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor (större, störst):</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men., till utsträckning, antal m. m.:</text:span> mons; domus; gaza, C.; m-i corporis homo, N.; m-a, major, maxima pars; oppidum maximum; maximum iter, Cs.; mare m-um; m-a manus; m-æ legiones, divitiæ, Sa.; dos m-a; calceus si pede major erit, subvertet, si minor, uret, Hor.; Italia m-a; m. populus; m-um agmen, Vg.; imperium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rike)</text:span> m-um; numerus major, L.; m-a corpora Germanorum, T.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till grad, wärde, kraft; ofta, der wi i sw. bruka mera speciella uttr., ss. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hög, djup, innerlig, kraftig, wäldig,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. än mera bestämda:</text:span> timor, beneficium, gratia, invidia, laus, amicitia, imperator, vox; m-a opinio fuit -; m-a me spes tenet -, C.; gloria, scientia, opportunitas, gaudium, bellum; m-o usui esse, Sa.; dolor, periculum, Cs.; m-um discrimen; auctor <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sagesman)</text:span> rei m-æ, L.; hi m-mi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förnämste)</text:span> laudatores; m-a adulteria <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skandalösa),</text:span> T.; clamor, dedecus, labor, Hor. - m-i (pluris), maximi esse, alqd facere, æstimare <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wärderas, wärdera);</text:span> m-o constat <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(kostar mycket);</text:span> m-o emere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(köpa för högt pris, dyrt),</text:span> C.; m-o mercari alqd <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(betala mycket för ngt),</text:span> Vg.; m-i refert, C.; in majus extollere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förstora, i framställningen; öfwerdrifwa),</text:span> Sa., L.; in majus celebrare, accipere, L.; in majus credere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(tro ngt wara större, än det är),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor, hög,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wigtig, betydande, swår:</text:span></text:span> dii m-a curant, parva negligunt; m-a ars; m-um opus et arduum; m-um est = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">det är ngt stort, wigtigt, swårt:</text:span> m-um est eadem habere monumenta majorum; m-um est efficere, ut quis intelligat, quid sit illud verum et summum bonum, C.; m. casus, Cs.; majora molior, C.; majora et aspera aggredi, Sa.; in hora sæpe ducentos, ut m-um, versus dictabat stans pede in uno, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">långwarig;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. om person, i comp. och superl. (i l. utan förening med</text:span> natu): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">äldre, äldst:</text:span></text:span> m. annus, C., Vg.; Veturia; m-o natu mulier, L.; Cato Major; adolescentis est m-res natu revereri, C.; haud ambigam, hicine fuerit Ascanius, an major quam hic; Numitor stirpis maximus fuit, L.; legantur in Africam m-res natu, Sa.; maxima natarum Priami (Ilione); maximus Ilioneus placido sic pectore coepit, Vg.; o major juvenum; majores audire, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.:</text:span> <text:line-break/>α.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Majōres</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förfäder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ngns); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anor, fäder, förfäder</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ett folks):</text:span> m-bus suis dignissimus, C.; ab his m-bus orti; nullis m-bus orti, Hor.; multa præclara m-rum; m-res nostri, C.; instituta m-rum domi militiæque, C., Sa.; m-res nostri, religiosissimi mortales, Sa.; delicta m-rum immeritus lues; ita voluere m-res, Hor.<text:line-break/>β. major = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en skolas l. läras </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">mästare:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i afs. på (samhälls-)ställning; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hög, upphöjd, förnäm; stolt:</text:span></text:span> pontifex maximus, C., L.; magistratus majores, Gell.; genus - majus auctiusque reliquit posteris, L.; fuge m-a; m. eques; m-i pueri m-is centurionibus orti; cum m-s vivere; nec m-o nec parvo ulla est fuga leti; m. amicus; m-a fortuna, Hor.; rex m-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om Jupiter),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i egna ögon, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stolt; stor,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ord:</text:span> ut res sese dant, ita m-i et humiles sumus, Ter.; m-a loqui; m-a lingua, Hor.<text:line-break/>f. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till personlighet, character, snillegåfwor, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hög, ädel, utmärkt:</text:span></text:span> viri m-i est in omni fortuna recta et honesta conservare; Panætius m. <text:soft-page-break/>homo et in primis eruditus; judex m.; nemo vir m. sine afflatu aliquo divino fuit; vir maximus et spectatus; m. animus = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">hög-, storsinthet, mod:</text:span></text:span> in magnis animis ingeniisque plerumque exsistit gloriæ cupiditas; hoc animi, illud etiam ingenii m-i est; res m-o animo fortiter gestæ, C.; Cato clarus atque m. habetur; virtute m., Sa.; bello major et armis; maximus Hector; m-a sacerdos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(om</text:span> Sibylla), Vg.; m-æ animæ prodigus Paulus; m. Hercules, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Comp., Adv.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(magĕ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">arch.): </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mer, i högre grad, snarare:</text:span></text:span> m. elegans; m. vereor, Ter.; causa antiquior et m. a natura ipsa profecta; liberius et fortius et m. more nostro; m. delirare; multo m. exspecto; mærere hoc ejus eventu invidi m. quam amici est; id mihi eo m. cordi est, quod -; m. est, ut ipse moleste ferat, quam ut istius - crimen reformidet; m. m-isque, m. et m. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mer och mer,</text:span> C.; in dies, quotidie m., C., L.; postque m-isque <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(allt mer och mer),</text:span> Enn.; m. atque m. clarescunt sonitus, Vg.; non m. est contra naturam morbus aut egestas, quam detractio aut appetitio alieni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(sw.: lika mycket som -);</text:span> sin processeris longius, non m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(lika litet)</text:span> dolendum est, quam -, præterita verni temporis suavitate, æstatem auctumnumque venisse, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Maxĭme</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Superl., Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mest, i högsta grad; högst, ganska:</text:span></text:span> pulcherrima illa et m. naturali carent amicitia; m. necessarius; m. libet; m. omnium studuit, ut -; hæc me vel m. movent; id ex hoc m. intelligi potest; tam sum amicus, quam qui m., C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I synnerhet, serdeles, förnämligast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (wanl. med en följande wilkors-, orsaks- l. tids-sats l. liktydigt uttryck):</text:span> quibus in rebus duo m. sunt fugienda -; id m. tum solet evenire, quum - de absentibus - malevole dicitur; ampla domus dedecori domino fit, si est in ea solitudo, et m. si aliquando alio domino solita est frequentari, C.<text:line-break/>b. nunc, tunc, tum, quum m., nunc quum m. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">nu, då som mest, som bäst:</text:span> jam admodum mitigati animi raptis erant: at raptarum parentes tum m. - civitates concitabant; quum m. hæc in senatu agerentur, Canulejus (ad plebem) ita disseruit, L.; (Cæsarem) armis oppressa civitas pertulit paretque, quum m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(nu som mest)</text:span> mortuo, C.<text:line-break/>c. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ungefär, närmast:</text:span></text:span> hoc m. modo, L.; scuta cetræ m. speciem præbentia, Ct.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Helst;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> isynn. i swar = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gerna, godt:</text:span></text:span> (imperavit,) ut Jugurtham m. vivum, si id parum procedat, necatum sibi traderent, Sa.; operam mihi da ! - m., Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. drifwer ngt i stort:</text:span> negotiator, Ap.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭdĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stortalande:</text:span></text:span> Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭfĭcus</text:span>, -centior, -centissimus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(eg. s. gör stora ting) i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stor, storartad, herrlig, hög:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre, ädel men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i l. om sinnelag och handlingar:</text:span> animus excelsus et m.; ad altiora quædam et m-ora nati sumus; decretum m-simum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ärofull),</text:span> C.; Atheniensium res gestæ amplæ et m-æ, Sa.; vir factis m-us, factorum ostentator non minor, L.; m-simum factum Thrasybuli, N. <text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om stil:</text:span> genus dicendi præclarum atque m-um, C.<text:line-break/>2. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">praktälskande, praktfull, ståtlig, rik:</text:span> (Romani) in suppliciis deorum m-i, domi parci erant, Sa.; consul; ornatus; opera; coena; venationes; ludi; vectigalia; apparatus, C.; domus, Pn. <text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stolt, stortalande, -skrytande, skrytsam:</text:span></text:span> facio me m-um; miles, Pt.; verba, Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭfĭce</text:span>, -centius, -centissime, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På ett storartadt sätt, herrligt, med ära, ädelt, ärofullt:</text:span></text:span> m. vicimus hominem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wunnit öfwer honom en herrlig seger);</text:span> m. virtutes appetere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med högsinthet);</text:span> conficere alqd, tractare alqm m.; vivere m., graviter, animose, C.; dicere m-ius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i högre, mera storartad stil,</text:span> C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Praktfullt:</text:span></text:span> convivium exornare, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stolt, skrytsamt:</text:span></text:span> incedit m. (consul), nostris (regum) decoratus insignibus, L.; loqui, C. ep.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭfĭcentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">inre </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storhet; själs-storhet, -höghet, ädelhet:</text:span></text:span> m. est rerum magnarum - cum animi ampla quadam - propositione - administratio; m. et despicientia rerum humanarum, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ordens </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storhet, ståt:</text:span></text:span> virtutem ne - verborum m-ā metiamur, C.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Prakt, ståt:</text:span></text:span> villæ, epularum, funerum; populus Rom. publicam m-am diligit, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭfĭco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Högt akta; upphöja, prisa:</text:span></text:span> alqm; turris m-atur, Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭlŏquus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Som talar storartadt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ett högt språk:</text:span> St.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stortalande, -skrytande:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭlŏquentia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Högt språk:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hög stil:</text:span></text:span> Homeri, C. <text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skryt:</text:span></text:span> L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Magnĭtūdo</text:span>, ĭnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storlek; storhet:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i yttre men., i utsträckning, massa, antal m. m.:</text:span> metiri mundi m-em; solis; maris Aegæi; regionum m-es; fructuum m. (magna copia); æris alieni, C.; corporum; silvæ, Cs.; copiarum, N.; itineris, Sa; (respublica) m-e laborat sua, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i inre men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till grad, intensitet, kraft:</text:span> frigorum; amoris; odii et acerbitatis; periculi; vocis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(omfång),</text:span> C.; m. (sceleris), Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">betydenhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (swårhet), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wigtighet:</text:span></text:span> animo rei m-em complecti; rei m. postulat etiam exercitationem, C.; rerum gestarum m., N. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Längd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i tiden:</text:span> dierum, Pn.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med afs. på samhälls-ställning, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">höghet:</text:span></text:span> imperatoria, T.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storhet; storhet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = utmärkthet, berömdhet;</text:span> animi m. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">högsinthet, storsinthet, mod:</text:span> ut quisque animi m-e maxime excellit, ita maxime vult princeps omnium esse; vera et sapiens animi m. honestum - in factis positum, non in gloria putat; maxime ipse populus Rom. animi m-e excellit; m-em animi ne inflectas cujusquam injuria, C.; omnia facilia ex difficilibus animi m. redegerat, Cs.; m. animi in utrisque (Cæsare et Catone) par, Sa. - m. Romani nominis, Sa.; si mea fama in obscuro sit, m-e eorum, qui <text:soft-page-break/>nomini officient meo, consoler; (Scipionis) m-em (Cato) allatrare solitus erat, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ajesta, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en gudomlighet:</text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Majestas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> major (majestus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">liks.</text:span> honestas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> honor, honestus]:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i familje- och samhällsförhållanden:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(factiskt öfwerordnad ställning), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Myndighet, makt, rätt, maktfullkomlighet; öfwerhöghet</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (souveraineté):</text:span> si in sua quisque matre familiæ jus et m-em viri retinere instituisset -; nec imperium consulare nec patriam m-em vereri; Coriolanus nec publica m-e in legatis, neque in sacerdotibus - religione motus erat, L.; quum (in foedere) alterius populi m. conservari jubetur, de altero siletur, certe ille populus in superiori condicione causaque ponitur; consulis, C.; imperii, N. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett folks l. en stats </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höghet, majestät</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">wärdighet, ära:</text:span></text:span> si m. est amplitudo et dignitas civitatis, is eam minuit, qui exercitum hostibus populi Rom. tradidit; m-em pop. R-i imminuere, lædere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förgripa sig på l. låta intrång göras på),</text:span> C.; m-em solvere, L.; deminutio m-is; crimen m-is; lex m-is, C.; reus m-is <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för majestätsbrott),</text:span> T. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i andra förh.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personlig </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Höghet, wärdighet, majestät:</text:span></text:span> deorum; quanta in oratione (Scipionis) m.!, C.; m. tua (Augusti) non recipit parvum carmen, Hor.; verecundia singularum (matronarum) magis m-is, quam universarum, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anseende:</text:span></text:span> novi m-em boum (; bos debet maxima esse auctoritate), Varr.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ståtlighet, ståt:</text:span></text:span> loci m. (Capitolii - i. e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deß ståtliga läge);</text:span> semper ea res (ut paludati proficiscantur ex urbe imperatores) cum magna dignitate et m-e geritur, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Majōrīnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af större form l. slag:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Majuscŭlus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Något större; något äldre:</text:span></text:span> folia, Pn.; cura, C.; mulier, Ter.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Maxĭmĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wäldig storhet:</text:span></text:span> immanis, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permagnus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket stor; ganska stor;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">neutr. gen.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl. pretii</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ganska mycket:</text:span></text:span> vis; p-i interest; p-o æstimare, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Magontiacum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Moguntiacum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măgŭdăris,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stängeln af wäxten</text:span> laserpitium: Pt., Pn. XIX. 15.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măgus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mager,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> persisk l. medisk prest, philosoph:</text:span> m-i, genus doctorum in Persis, divinant et augurantur; m-orum disciplina, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măga</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Klok qwinna; beswärjerska:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i beswärjelser kunnig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trollsk:</text:span></text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgīa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg. magernes lära l. konst; oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Trollkonst, swartkonst:</text:span></text:span> Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Magisk, trollsk, troll-, beswärjare-:</text:span></text:span> m-as accingier artes; m-a sacra, Vg.; m-i terrores, Hor.; portenta, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măgĭcē</text:span>, es, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> = magia: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>aja, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personnamn (sersk.: Mercurii moder).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Majālis,</text:span> is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Galt:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Majesta, -jestas, Major, -jorinus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ajus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>Majus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Maj-, Maj:</text:span></text:span> mensis, C., Ov.; Calendæ M-æ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Majusculus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Magnus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Māla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wäl</text:span> = mand-la <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> mando; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> C. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">af</text:span> maxilla):<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Käk:</text:span></text:span> m-is mandare (mandĕre?), Pac. ap. C.; crepitant m-æ (cestibus), Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kind:</text:span></text:span> teneræ, Ov.; permulcere m-as, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>alăca, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Hispanien (Malaga).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mălăcus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mjuk, smidig, weklig:</text:span></text:span> pallium; moechus; modus, Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălăcĭa</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Windstilla:</text:span></text:span> subito exstitit, Cs.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Matleda:</text:span></text:span> gravidarum, Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălăcisso</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Göra mjuk, uppmjuka:</text:span></text:span> Pt., Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Male <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mălus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ălĕa <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mălēa, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">udde af Laconien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Maledic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Dīco.<text:line-break/>Malefac . . ., Malefic . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Facio.<text:line-break/>Malesuadus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Suadeo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ălĕventum, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Samnium (äldre namn för Beneventum).</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Malevol . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ālĭăcus sinus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafswik i Thessalien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mālĭensis, <text:line-break/>Mālĭus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Malifer <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mālum.<text:line-break/>Malign . . ., Malit . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mălus.<text:line-break/>Malivol . . . = Malevol . . .</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Malleus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hammare, klubba, slägga:</text:span></text:span> Pt.; popæ, Ov.; fabri, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Malleătus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hamrad:</text:span></text:span> Col.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Malleŏlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Ce.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Telning, ympqwist, stickling:</text:span></text:span> C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Brandpil, beck-krans:</text:span></text:span> Cs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Malleŏlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: virga, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ympqwist,</text:span> Col.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>alloea, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Thessalien.</text:span> </text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>allus <text:line-break/>(Mallos), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Cilicien.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mallōtes, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. är från M.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mallus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ull-flockor:</text:span> Cato.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Malo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Volo.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mālŏbăthrum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en indisk wäxt och </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">balsam</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> deraf:</text:span> Hor., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Maltha,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bergolja:</text:span></text:span> Pn. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">kitt:</text:span></text:span> fit e calce, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Maltho</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kitta:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>althīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">personn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Malva,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en wäxt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kattost:</text:span></text:span> beta et m., C.; leves m-æ, Hor.; molles, Mt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Malvāceus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Mălum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mălus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mālum,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Äple:</text:span></text:span> m-o me Galatea petit, Vg.; m. citreum, Mt.; m. Persicum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(persika);</text:span> granatum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(granatäple),</text:span> Pn.; Punicum (id.), Col.; aureum (id.), Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mālĭfer</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. bär äplen:</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mālŏgrānātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Granatäple:</text:span></text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mālus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Äpleträd:</text:span></text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mălus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: (<text:span text:style-name="T1">Comp.</text:span> pejor, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Sup.</text:span> pessimus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> pejor): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ond, elak, dålig:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i physisk och intellectuel men.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ond = skadlig, förderflig; olycklig = olycksbringande:</text:span> omnia, quæ turpia sunt, m-a sunt, C.; m-um virus, Vg.; m-a scabies, cicuta; m. Jupiter, Hor.; m. nuntius; m-a pugna, C.; res; eventus; exitus, Sa.; m-um auspicium; m-a avis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(olyckligt förebud),</text:span> Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dålig, usel, oduglig, underhaltig:</text:span></text:span> valetudo, C.; poēta; versus; loquendi consuetudo, C.; crus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ful);</text:span> aper <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(till smaken),</text:span> Hor.; regibus boni quam m-i suspectiores sunt, Sa.; ager; coluber m-a gramina pastus, Vg.; facies <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(ful),</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i moralisk mening:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ond, stygg, elak</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (= s. söker att skada); spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">illistig, illslug:</text:span></text:span> homines minime m-i (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wälmenande),</text:span> sed non satis acuti; fides; dolus, C.; ingenium m-um pravumque; m-i et scelesti; m-æ artes, Sa.; m. fur; m-a fraus; m-a carmina <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(smädedikter),</text:span> Hor.; edocebo decem minime m-as, ut sint m-æ; nescis m-a et fraudulenta esse, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">moraliskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dålig, usel, förderfwad:</text:span></text:span> consuetudo, C.; mores; exemplum; ambitio, Sa.: lustra; fastidium; pudor, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">något </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ondt; ondt ting; olycka, olägenhet:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> ex m-is minima eligere oportet; m. accidit, erumpit, crescit, serpit, sedatur; turpitudo summum m. est; omne m. nascens facile opprimitur; maximis in m-is hoc boni assecuti videmur; habere, sustinere m.; fugere majus, eligere levius, C.; m. repentinum, præsens, Cs.; m. publicum; m-a mortalium; m-a perpeti, Sa.; fama m., quo non aliud velocius ullum; non ignari sumus ante m-orum, Vg.; maxima m-a; m-a multa precari alicui; omne m. vino levare, Hor.; id m-o est alicui; m-a inferre in domum alicujus, N.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lyte, brist, fel, orättfärdighet, last, brott:</text:span></text:span> tua pervides oculis m-a lippus inunctis, Hor.; hanc tantam m-orum sementem a diis factam <text:soft-page-break/>esse arbitramur?, C.; superbia commune nobilitatis m.; divitiæ materies omnium m-orum, Sa.; (e terra) effodiuntur opes, irritamenta m-orum, Ov.; veterum m-orum supplicia, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ondt, olycka, s. tillfogas ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skada, lidande;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sersk.: (hårda medel), tuktan, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">straff:</text:span></text:span> abstinet se injuria, ne m. habeat, C.; m. dare alicui, Ter.; pudore magis quam m-o exercitum coërcebat, Sa.; m-um minari alicui, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i utrop = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">För en olycka:</text:span></text:span> quid vos, m.? -, Ter.; quæ, m., ista est ratio?; quæ te, m., ratio in istam spem induxit?, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălum</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălĕ</text:span>, pejus, pessime, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = till skada, men, (afsigtligt l. oafsigtligt), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">olyckligt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (argt, ondt, obehagligt, ofördelaktigt):</text:span> m. facere alicui, Pt., C.; res m. vertat tibi, Ter.; m. sit ei, C.; Carthagini m. jamdiu cogitanti bellum denuntio, C.; m. suadere alicui, Pt.; m. rem gerere, C., N.; m. olere; m. verbis accipere alqm; m. mulcari; res se m. habet; m. mereri de aliquo, C.; Sequanis pejus accidit, quam Hæduis, Cs. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dåligt (illa), klent, knappt, ej rätt,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (föga):</text:span> m. sanus; m. fidus, C.; m. sustinere arma, L.; m. amicum numen; m. pingue solum, Vg.; m. si mandata loqueris <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(på scenen),</text:span> aut dormitabo aut ridebo; digitus m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swagt)</text:span> pertinax, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permălĕ</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mycket olyckligt:</text:span></text:span> pugnare: C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălignus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: (gigno?)<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: om personer och deras sinnelag, handlingar m. m.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wrång, ogin, hätsk, mißunnsam:</text:span></text:span> m-a facta est (amica alicui), Ter.; m-is oculis (Trojanæ matres) spectabant rates, Vg.; m-um spernere vulgus, Hor.; mens, Catl.; homo, Pn.; capita m-sima et optimo cuique inimicissima, Sen.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Snål, nidsk, karg:</text:span></text:span> caupones, Hor.; in laudando, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om saker: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Karg, knapp, ringa:</text:span></text:span> terra <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(föga gifwande),</text:span> Pn.; lunæ lux m-a, Vg.; ostium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(trång),</text:span> Sen. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Măligne</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illwilligt, wrångt, hätskt:</text:span></text:span> maledice ac m.loqui, L.; bene facta m. detrectare, Ov.; habere sermonem m-ius, Ct. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Kargt, nidskt:</text:span></text:span> prædam dividere, decernere, L.; laudare, Hor.; agere cum aliquo, Sen. <text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knappt, föga:</text:span></text:span> fores m. apertæ, Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălignĭtas</text:span>, ātis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wrånghet, oginhet, mißunnsamhet, afund:</text:span></text:span> naturali quadam m-e desciscunt etiam probata semina, Col.; pudor vicit m-em triumphumque frequentes decreverunt (patres), L.; vitare dentes m-is, Val.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nidskhet, karghet:</text:span></text:span> m. patrum, qui prædā militem fraudavere; m-is auctores quærendo consul rem arbitrii sui ad senatum rejecit, L.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălĭtia</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illfundighet, illslughet, arglistighet:</text:span></text:span> m. est certi cujusdam vitii nomen; est versuta et fallax nocendi ratio; vult - videri se esse prudentiam, sed ab ea distat plurimum; nemo qui for titudinis <text:soft-page-break/>gloriam consecutus est insidiis et m-a, laudem est adeptus; versare mentem ad fraudem et m-am; id olet m-am; m-æ omnes, C.<text:line-break/>2. (= vitium, vitiositas <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Dålighet, osedlighet, last:</text:span></text:span> se (Jugurtham) virtute, non m-ā (i. e. ignavia) P. Scipioni placuisse, Sa.; bona sunt, quibus virtus -, turpia, quibus m. conjuncta est, Sen.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i phys. men.:</text:span> terræ, Pall.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălĭtiōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Illfundig, illslug, arglistig:</text:span></text:span> nimis callida et m-a juris interpretatio; homo versutus, obscurus, astutus, fallax, m., C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mălĭtiōse</text:span>, -ius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: agitur inter eos dolose aut m.; gerere rem mandatam m-ius sui quæstus causa; litem intendere m., C.; aut m. aut negligenter facere alqd, N.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Mālus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mast:</text:span></text:span> m-os scandere, C.; m-um de nave erigere, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bjelke, stång,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hwarpå ngt hwilar, fästes l. uppspännes:</text:span> turrium, Cs.; m. in circo instabilis decidit, L.; carbasus (malis) intenta theatris, Lucr.; m. in torculari, Pn,</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. Mālus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mālum.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>āmercus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. tillnamn.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3"><text:line-break/>M</text:span>āmers, tis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">osk. och sab. = Mars.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Māmertīni, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">de italiske inwånarne i Messana.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Māmertīnus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>āmilius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. tillnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Mamill . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mamma.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mamma,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bröst; spene:</text:span></text:span> dare puero, filio, Pt., Ter.; puer appetit m-m; viris m-æ (nullam ob utilitatem quasi ad quendam ornatum donatæ), C.; exserta m. (Amazonis); pressis manabunt flumina m-is, Vg.; (quibusdam bestiis) m-rum data est multitudo, C.; m-æ suis; m-æ sterilescunt, exstinguuntur, Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">mor, i barns språk:</text:span> Varr.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwistknöl</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (af bröstlik form):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mammātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: m-a (fictilia) ad balineas, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wäl = kupiga wärmeledningsrör,</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mammeātus</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mammōsus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Storbröstad:</text:span></text:span> amica, Pt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bröstformig, fylligt rundad:</text:span></text:span> pira, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mammŭla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (Varr.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mămilla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">litet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bröst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bröstwårta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.</text:span> major infante m.; læva in parte m-æ nil salit Arcadico juveni, Juv. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Knapp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ändan af wattenledningsrör:</text:span> in fistulam m-as imponere tenues, quæ eructent aquam, Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mămillānus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: ficus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mjölkfylld),</text:span> Pn. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mămillāre</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bröstbindel:</text:span></text:span> Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mamphūla,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. syr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett slags bakelse:</text:span> Lucil. ap. Fs.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>āmŭrius, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ett i Saliernes sånger förekommande namn:</text:span> Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>āmurra, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. slägtnamn.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Manabilis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mano.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mānālis,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> mano): fons = perennis, Fs. - lapis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(regnsten</text:span> i. e.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sten, s. man släpade omkring i staden (Rom) för att framkalla regn,</text:span> Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Manceps,</text:span> cĭpis (-cŭpis), <text:span text:style-name="T1">c.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> manus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> capio = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">den som tager ngt i handen,</text:span> i. e.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">som ikläder sig answaret för en förbindelses fullgörande, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hemulsman,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> syn.</text:span> auctor; m., quia manu sublata significat se auctorem emptionis esse, Fs.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om den, som i första hand answarade för en auctionssumma, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hufwudman:</text:span></text:span> m. fit Chrysogonus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wid försäljningen af S. Roscii egendom),</text:span> C.; nullius rei neque præs neque m. factus est, N.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Entreprenör</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ett arbete:</text:span> operis, C., T.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">General-förpaktare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af statsinkomster:</text:span> decumarum, C.<text:line-break/>d. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Löftesman:</text:span></text:span> Pt.<text:line-break/>e. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Agent</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för ett företag, bolag:</text:span> m. operarum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. lejer arbetsfolk),</text:span> Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mancĭpium</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Mancŭpium), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egendoms öfwergång, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Köp</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i laga form (i wittnens närwaro,</text:span> per æs et libram); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">lagligt förwärfwad </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">egande rätt</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (egendom, i abstr. men.):</text:span> in m-o dicere (rei vitia); lex m-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(köpecontract),</text:span> C.; m-o dare alicui, accipere ab aliquo alqd, Pt., C.; vitaque m-o nulli datur, omnibus usu, Lucr.; res m-pi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(mots.:</text:span> nec m-pi) = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. öfwerlåtes till egendom med wissa formaliteter,</text:span> C.; res m-pi sunt animalia, prædia rustica et urbana, Gaj. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwad s. eges med full egande rätt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slaf:</text:span></text:span> in m-o vendendo dicenda vitia (mendacem esse, aleatorem, furem), C.; retinere fugitiva m-a, Pn.; m-is locuples eget æris Cappadocum rex; m. frugi et domino amicum, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mancĭpo</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Mancŭpo), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerlåta, afträda, gifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till laga egendom; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">sälja:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.:</text:span> alienos, Pt.; quædam, si credis consultis, m-at usus, Hor.; agrum alicui, Pn. <text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> luxui m-tus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hängifwen, begifwen på),</text:span> T.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mancĭpātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerlåtelse</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till egendom under wissa formaliteter:</text:span> m. dicitur, quia res manu capitur, Jct. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mancĭpātus</text:span>, us, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: id.: res venit in m-um, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmancĭpo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afträda, afyttra</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> egendom: </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sälja:</text:span></text:span> agrum, Su.; filium in adoptionem Silano, C.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frigifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> en son; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förklara fri, sjelfständig:</text:span></text:span> filium, C., L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sälja, göra till slaf:</text:span></text:span> se alicui, Pt.; ita senectus honorata est, si nemini e-ta est; tribunatus venditus et e-tus, C.; feminæ e-tus, Hor.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmancĭpātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Frigifning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> från faders- l. husbondemakten:</text:span> filii, Qu.; testamentum fit per e-em familiæ, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ancīnus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">cognomen i</text:span> gens Hostilia.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Mancip . . ., Mancup . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Manceps.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mancus,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemlästad, lytt, ofärdig:</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> Q. Scævola perditus morbo, m. et membris omnibus captus ac debilis, C.; dux m-orum et debilium, L.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Ofärdig, oförmögen, half-färdig, -gången, bristfällig:</text:span></text:span> in sapientem ruit m-a fortuna; dixi me talibus officiis (<text:span text:style-name="T1">dat.</text:span>) m-um, Hor.; prætura (Clodii) m-a ac debilis consule Milone; virtus m-a sine aliqua accessione; cognitio m-a est, si nulla actio rerum consequitur, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmanco</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemlästa, stympa:</text:span></text:span> Labien. ap. Sen.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Mandat . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> II. Mando.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>andēla, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bynamn:</text:span> Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Mandibulæ, Mando (onis) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Mando.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Mando,</text:span> di (dui, dĭdi, Prisc.), sum, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tugga, söndertugga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tuggande förtära):</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> cibus dentibus m-itur, C.; lora detractasque scutis pelles m-re conabantur, L.; cibi m-si, Qu.; humum m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bita i gräset),</text:span> Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">bildl. = förtära:</text:span> corpora igni m-untur, poēt. ap. Varr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mansum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tuggad </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bit</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tugga):</text:span> omnia minima m-a in os pueri inserunt (nutrices), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandĭbŭlæ</text:span>, ārum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tuggredskap, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Käkar:</text:span></text:span> Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mando</text:span>, ōnis <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandūco</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fråssare, storätare:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Ap.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandūcus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>a. id.: Non.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">comisk mask med utstående käftar; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Nötknäppare:</text:span></text:span> Varr., Pt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandūco</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dep.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandūcor</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tugga, förtära:</text:span></text:span> farre m-to saginare pullos, Varr.; duas bucceas in balineo m-re, Su.; m-ri, Lucil.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commando</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commandūco</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Commandūcor, Lucil.), 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Söndertugga:</text:span></text:span> Val., Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præmando</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tugga före</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (tugga tillreds åt ngn): bildl.,</text:span> Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕmando</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tugga omigen:</text:span></text:span> eadem scripta sæpius revolvere et quasi eundem cibum r., Qu.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Sŭpermando</text:span>, 3.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tugga,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> förtära </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ofwanpå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (efter) ngt:</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Mando,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> manus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> do): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Öfwerlemna, antwarda, betro:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt att förwara, skydda, gömma:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt person:</text:span> res suas, filiam alicui, Pt.; bona sua fidei alicujus, Ter.; S. Roscius cum fama bonisque publice Roscio m-atur, C.; Polydorum alendum regi Threicio Priamus m-vit, Vg. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt sak:</text:span> humo mortuos, Vg.; tumulis peremptos, poēt. ap. C.; hordea sulcis, Vg.; semen terræ, Col.; vitam fugæ et tenebris, C.; se <text:soft-page-break/>fugæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa sig på, söka räddning i flykt),</text:span> Cs.; alqd animis et mentibus, memoriæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(inprägla i);</text:span> alqd immortalitati; aliquid literis (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skriftligen uppteckna),</text:span> literis Latinis, scriptis, versibus, monumentis annalium, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ngt att ombesörja, sköta = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppdraga, lemna i uppdrag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ngn, gifwa </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppdrag,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (ordres), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">befallning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om ngt:</text:span> huic m-es, si quid recte curatum velis, Ter.; honores, magistratus, imperia alicui, C.; sacerdotia, L.; rem m-tam malitiosius gerere; filio m-vi, quæ illum vellem loqui tecum; procuratori m. alqd de agricultura; vasa, typos alicui m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(gifwa i uppdrag att beställa);</text:span> m-o tibi, ut perspicias, cujusmodi hoc totum sit, C.; his m-vit, ut, quæ diceret Ariovistus, ad se referrent; huic m-at, Belgas adeat, Cs.; Cethego atque Lentulo m-at, (ut) quibus rebus possint, opes factionis confirment, Sa.; seniles partes juveni m. (in scena); male m-ta loqui, Hor.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tillskicka, -skynda:</text:span></text:span> pestis m-ta hostili manu, Enn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtrodt gods:</text:span></text:span> cave, ne titubes m-aque frangas, Hor.<text:line-break/>2.<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppdrag, befallning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (commission):</text:span> m. recipere, negligere, procurare; habere m. ab aliquo; m-i <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(för försummadt uppdrag)</text:span> judicium non minus turpe quam furti; m-a conficere, exhaurire, persequi, exsequi; m-is satisfacere, C.; m. interficiendi, Pisonis dare alicui, T.; efficere, Sa.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.: sändebuds </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppdrag</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">instruction, ärende, budskap, helsning, framställning,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. genom ett sändebud framföres:</text:span> mittere legatos cum m-is; m-a Cæsaris deferre ad alqm oratoris modo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(Cæsars ord, upprop);</text:span> m-a Cæsari referebantur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(swar på framställningen),</text:span> Cs.; venire cum m-is; m-a dare alicui de re ad alqm; mittere in alqm m-a literasque, C.; instruere alqm m-is, L.; verbis dare m-a alicui; legati Sullæ m-a Bocchi <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(anbud)</text:span> patefaciunt; Marius - m-a Bocchi cognoscit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(pröfwar, rådgör om -),</text:span> Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. gifwer uppdrag, bemyndigar:</text:span> Jct. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sersk.: s. gifwer uppdrag åt ngn att anklaga, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anstiftare</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af anklagelse:</text:span> Su. -<text:line-break/>(Mandātus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>) <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mandātu</text:span> alicujus: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På l. i någons uppdrag, å någons wägnar:</text:span></text:span> m-u meo, Sullæ, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Āmando</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortskicka, aflägsna, förwisa:</text:span></text:span> alqm in ultimas terras; in Græciam; infra mortuos; rem procul a sensibus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> me expulso, Catone a-to, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Āmandātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bortskickande, förwisning:</text:span></text:span> C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendo</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">factiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förtro, anförtro, öfwerlemna</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i någons wård, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anbefalla, betro:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt person:</text:span> se alicui in clientelam; se fidei alicujus, Ter.; rem et famam suam alicui c. et concredere; alicui liberos, opes, fortunas suas; filios tutelæ alicujus, testamento alicui; se alicui totum; alicui alqd non solum committere, sed etiam c.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">absol.:</text:span> suos (morientem) c-re, C.; regnum alicui, N.; se alicui, Cs.; Orestillam c-o tuæque fidei trado, Sa.; sacra suosque tibi c-at Troja penates, Vg.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">åt sak:</text:span> memoriæ alqd c-re; historia immortalitati voce oratoris c-<text:soft-page-break/>atur; vitam alicujus monumentis ad æternam memoriam, C.; se fugæ <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(söka skydd i -),</text:span> Cs.; nunc tibi c-o, communia pignora, natos, Ppt.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anbefalla, recommendera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> hos ngn, åt ngns gunst, uppmärksamhet; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förorda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men., med ord:</text:span> alqm apud alqm studiose, valde, intime, diligentissime, C.; qualem c-es, etiam atque etiam aspice, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Recommendera</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = winna l. söka winna gunst, uppmärksamhet, intresse för ngn; göra omtyckt l. ansedd; befordra, framdraga till ngt:</text:span> modestia adolescentem c-at; vox una maxime eloquentiam vel c-at vel sustinet; nulla re una orator magis c-atur, quam splendore verborum et copia; P. Rutilii adolescentiam ad opinionem et innocentiæ et juris scientiæ P. Mucii c-vit domus, C.; se c-re tonsa cute, dentibus atris; (vinum) quod me Lucanæ juvenem c-et amicæ, Hor. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">säkert öfwerlemnad (förswarad); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Omtyckt, ansedd:</text:span></text:span> quæ res c-ior hominum memoriæ sempiternæ?; quis est, cui non illa civitas sit hujus studio, curā, diligentiā c-ior?, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wärd att anbefallas, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Aktningswärd, angenäm:</text:span></text:span> Perseus nullo c. merito; multa in (Philippo rege) dexteritas et humanitas, quæ c-ia apud Scipionem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(syn.</text:span> gratus) erant, L.; aves cantu c-es, Val.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendātīcius</text:span> <text:line-break/>(Commendātītius), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: literæ, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">recommendations-bref,</text:span> C. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anbefallande, recommendation, förord:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span> contempti hominis <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(obj.)</text:span> c. ad alqm; sui; mea; accurata; magna; amicorum c-e gratus; egere, valere c-e, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Befordran</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till l. sätt att winna ngt; en saks (egenskaps) förmåga att winna, intaga för ngn (fördelaktigt intryck af, det intagande i -):</text:span> prima est adolescenti c. ad gloriam, si qua ex bellicis rebus comparari potest; vita ejus et mores omnem c-em ingenii evertebat; Crassi mirificus pudor non solum non oberat orationi, sed etiam probitatis c-i proderat, C.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendātor</text:span>, ōris, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>:<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commendātrix</text:span>, īcis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">s. anbefaller, wäcker intresse för -: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förespråkare:</text:span></text:span> (nullius) ingenium potest emergere, nisi illi - - fautor c-rque contingat, Pn. - legem esse oportet c-cem virtutum, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Incommendātus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: ventis - omnis tellus i-a est, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hwarje land ej anbefaldt = intet är för dem fridlyst,</text:span> Ov.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēmando</text:span>, 1.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">factiskt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Lemna från sig</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i ngns wård; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">anförtro, öfwerlemna:</text:span></text:span> curā sacrorum sacerdotibus d-tā; plures pueri - unius (magistri) curæ d-bantur, L.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Anbefalla, uppdraga</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">gifwa befallning</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> om:</text:span> curam (sauciorum militum) nominatim - præfectis d-bat, L.; funeris sui curam alicui; puerum mergendum servis ipsius d-bat, Su.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skicka bort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för säkerhets skull):</text:span> in proximam civitatem, Su.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præmando</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I förwäg gifwa befallning:</text:span></text:span> p-vi, ut conquireretur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(förr än han på stället inträffade),</text:span> C.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Præmandātum</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">I förwäg skickadt bref, ordres:</text:span></text:span> p-is requirere alqm, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕmando</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">skicka bud tillbaka; helsa tillbaka:</text:span> Eutr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mandra,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: (v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stängsel, gård, stall):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slutet </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tåg</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af wagnar och dragare:</text:span> stantis convicia m-æ, Juv.; longa mulorum m., Mt.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> ludus latrunculorum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">slutet led l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mur</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af piecer (eller af linier?), s. motspelaren sökte genomtränga:</text:span> fractā perrumpit in agmina m-ā, Luc.; m-is et vitreo milite claudere (adversarium), Mt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mandrăgŏras</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">en sömn-gifwande wäxt</text:span> (atropa m.): Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>andubii, ōrum, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">galliskt folk.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Manduc . . . <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> I. Mando.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>anduria, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stad i Calabrien.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Māne,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">def.</text:span> (<text:span text:style-name="T1">nom.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc.</text:span> mane, <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span> mane <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> mani; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om etymologien se</text:span> Varr. VI. 4. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">jfr.</text:span> matutinus), <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Morgon, tidig morgonstund:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med fullständig substantivnatur (ss. subj.; i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med attribut l. med præp.):</text:span> primum m., novissimum vesper, Varr.; dum m. novum, dum gramina canent, Vg.; m. erat, Ov.; jam clarum m. fenestras intrat, Ps.; stertere ad ipsum m., Hor.; m. totum dormire, Mt.; a m-i ad noctem, Pt.; a m-e diei, Cs.; multo m-e, C.; obscuro m-e; a primo m-e, Col.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">adverbielt = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Om morgonen, tidigt, bittida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (arla):</text:span> hodie m.; eo die m.; bene m.; postridie m., C.; m. egredior, vesperi domum revertor, Ter.; m. forum, vespertinus pete tectum, Hor. - [magis, maxime mane <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> manius, - sime non dicitur <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Varr. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(emedan ordet urspr. ej är adv.)</text:span>].</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Măneo,</text:span> mansi, mansum, 2.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förblifwa, blifwa, wänta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>I. <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i mots. till röra sig, gå bort (förändras):</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i eg. men.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa, dröja qwar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på ett ställe; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stanna, wänta, bida</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (hålla stånd):</text:span> <text:line-break/>α. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> mane, dum narro, Pt.; m. domi; in eo loco; m-sum oportuit, Ter.; Romæ; in patria m.; hic m-ri non potest, C.; totam hiemem ad exercitum, Cs.; fugere an m-re tutius foret, in incerto erat; (dixit se) etiamsi certa pestis adesset, m-surum potius, quam turpi fuga - vitæ parceret, Sa.; ibidem; eodem loco, N.; nec m. nec transire ausus; ad urbem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(wänta),</text:span> L.; m-et imperterritus; illa m-ent immota locis nec ab ordine cedunt, Vg.; in urbe; (nec mens mihi) nec color certa sede m-et, Hor.<text:line-break/>β. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stanna, uppehålla</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> sig öfwer natten:</text:span> apud me, C.; non m-bit extra domum patris sponsa Icilii, L.; m-suri oppidulo, quod versu dicere non est; venator m-et sub Jove frigido, Hor.; in villa alicujus, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förblifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> uti ett tillstånd; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">blifwa, stå, stå fast</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wid ngt:</text:span> in sententia; in voluntate; in fide; in amicitia; in officio; in veritate <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(hålla sig till);</text:span> in pristina mente; nihil semper suo statu m-et; hæc perpetuo animo meo fixa m-bunt, C.; Leptitani semper boni <text:soft-page-break/>fidelesque m-sere, Sa.; Hæduis se - bellum illaturum non esse, si m-rent in eo, quod convenisset, Cs.; in societate, N.; hac casta m-ant in religione nepotes; m-ent immota tuorum fata tibi, Vg.; promissis, dictis (<text:span text:style-name="T1">abl.</text:span>), Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara, bestå</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (i mots. till förstöras, förswinna, gå under); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">ännu finnas</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> qwar; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">fortwara, -lefwa, ega bestånd:</text:span></text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span> dolor plures dies m-et; parietes urbis stant et m-ent, rempublicam vero penitus amisimus; aut m-ent animi post mortem aut intereunt; lex, mos m-et; dum memoria rerum Romanarum m-bit, Tib. Gracchus laudabitur, C.; induciæ m-ent; munitiones integræ m-ent, Cs.; non diu pax Albana m-sit; inde institutum m-sit, - ne Pinarii extis vescerentur, L.; vestigia servitutis; opinio, N.; Trojaque nunc stares Priamique arx alta m-res, Vg.; m-runt hodieque m-ent vestigia ruris, Hor.; triumphus decernitur m-ente bello; m-bat nihilo minus quædam imago reipublicæ; m-isse sub Julio - imperium, m-suram fuisse sub Pompejo rempublicam, T.<text:line-break/>b. m. <text:span text:style-name="T1">alicui</text:span> = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förblifwa, fortwara</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> för l. hos ngn:</text:span> mihi cum illo contentio m-et; m-ent ingenia senibus, modo permaneat studium et industria, C.; ne errarent: m-re iis bellum, quod positum simuletur, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om satser, meningar: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stå fast:</text:span></text:span> m-eat ergo, quod turpe sit, id nunquam utile esse, C.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">wara förwaradt = säkert </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förestå, skola komma:</text:span></text:span> illius fatum tibi m-et, C.; terrā graviora m-ent; (docebo) qui m-ant Itala magni de gente nepotes, Vg. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> II. b.). <text:line-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wänta:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">egentl. om personl. subj.: wänta på ngt l. ngn, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Afbida, afwakta:</text:span></text:span> domi te, Pt., Hor.; patruum, Ter.; hostem, L.; aulæa (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rideauns uppdragande)</text:span> m-et spectator, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: om sakl. subj.:</text:span> nos manet Oceanus, Assaraci tellus, Hor. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">häraf i allm. = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förestå,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> wara </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">beskärd, bestämd</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> åt ngn:</text:span> periculum ingens alqm, L.; te triste m-bit supplicium, Vg.; debita jura te m-ent; omnes una m-et nox et calcanda semel via leti; hoc te m-et, ut - te occupet senectus, Hor.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mansio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwarblifwande, -stannande, -dröjande:</text:span></text:span> crebræ itiones et m-es Lemni, Ter.; m. et decessio tua; m. in vita, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wistelseort</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (öfwer natten); </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">bostad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (fr.: maison); spec.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">herberge, rasteställe, station</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> på resa:</text:span> m. pecorum sub dio, Pn.; ad primam m-em febrim nactus est, Su. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">deraf: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">station, håll</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> ss. wägmått (jfr gr.</text:span> σταθμός): locus a loco octo m-bus distat, Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mansĭto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppehålla sig, bo</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (logera):</text:span> (avis) in campis, Pn.; sub eodem tecto cum aliquo, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Manto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Frequ.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wänta,</text:span></text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">trans.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">intr.</text:span>: Pt.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commăneo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stadigt wistas, bo:</text:span></text:span> non ii, qui adveniunt, sed qui c-ent in domo -, Mcb.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Ēmăneo</text:span>, mansi, 2.:<text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Uppehålla sig utanför</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> -:</text:span> lucis vetitus e-isse sacerdos, St. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blifwa borta öfwer orlofstiden:</text:span> Jct.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Intermăneo</text:span>, ēre: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Stanna under tiden:</text:span></text:span> defessus Cæsar mediis i-et agris, Luc.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permăneo</text:span>, mansi, mansum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">stadigt </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förblifwa; hålla, härda ut:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">på ett ställe:</text:span> eodem loco; in vallo, Cs.; in lecticula lucubratoria ad multam noctem, Su.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blifwa, fortfara wid en mening, med en sysselsättning, i ett tillstånd m. m.:</text:span> in incepto; in eadem mente; in sententia, C.; in eadem tristitia; in armis; in amicitia alicujus; annos viginti in disciplina (Druidum), Cs.; in suis artibus (Jugurtha), Sa.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Wara, fortwara, -lefwa, -fara, bestå:</text:span></text:span> ira diu, Ter.; nihil difficilius esse, quam amicitiam usque ad extremum vitæ p-re; Persæ mortuos cera circumlitos condunt, ut - p-ant <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(bibehålla sig)</text:span> diuturna corpora; vita (ceterorum hominum) humi retinetur et p-et tamen; senibus studium et industria, C.; amicitia, Sa.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Permansio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Förblifwande:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>a. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">qwarstannande:</text:span> quodvis supplicium levius est hac p-e, C.<text:line-break/>b. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">widblifwande:</text:span> in una sententia; in ratione, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕmăneo</text:span>, mansi, mansum, 2.:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Blifwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">stanna qwar</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> någorstädes efter ngn l. något, sås. återstod:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i egentl. men.:</text:span> ceterorum discessu r.; in exercitu r. (quum legio dimitteretur), C.; domi; Romæ, Cs.; ferrum (ex hastili) in corpore, N.; cubito r-ete presso, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span> in consilio <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(blifwa stående),</text:span> Cs.; hostis nomen a peregrino recessit et proprie in eo, qui arma contra ferret, r-sit, C.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Fortwara, -lefwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> efter ngt; </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">finnas qwar, wara öfrig, återstå:</text:span></text:span> animi r-ent post mortem; causa injuriæ r-et; (tribunis creatis) senatus auctoritas tamen gravis et magna r-bat; in hac muliere - vestigia antiqui officii r-ent, C.; vobis æterna sollicitudo r-bit; si ulla apud vos memoria r-et avi mei Massinissæ, Sa.<text:line-break/>3. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">blifwa stilla = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upphöra:</text:span></text:span> suspirium - retardatum est et r-sit, Sen. ep. 54.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Rĕmansio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Qwarstannande:</text:span></text:span> (in provincia), C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mānes,</text:span> ium, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Fs. = boni <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> mānus) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eller</text:span> quod eos per omnia manare credebant]: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">De döde, de dödes skuggor, andar, wålnader,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">maner</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (äfwen om </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">en</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> död;</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">sing. acc.</text:span> manem <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hos</text:span> Ap.): deorum m-ium jura sancta sunto. Sos (suos; nos, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">Vahl.)</text:span> leto datos divos habento, C.; diis m-bus servilibus facere <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(offra),</text:span> Varr.; m-bus divis inferias mittere, Lucr.; m-es placare, L. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spec. tänkta</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">sås. hwilande i grafwen jemte stoftet (jfr</text:span> animam condere sepulcro, Vg.): sepulcra diruta, omnium nudati m-es, nullius ossa terra tegi, L.; id cinerem aut m-es credis curare sepultos, Vg.; draco m-es Scipionis custodire traditur; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rent af = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">lik:</text:span></text:span> alites e m-bus hominum oculos potissimum appetunt, Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom kringirrande </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Skuggor:</text:span></text:span> m-es Virginiæ per tot domos ad poenas petendas vagati - tandem quievere, L.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">såsom boende i underjorden, derföre öfwerhufwud</text:span> = inferi, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Underjordens rike, underjordens herrar:</text:span></text:span> hæc m-es veniet mihi <text:soft-page-break/>fama sub imos; Orpheus m-es adiit regemque tremendum; quo fletu m-es, qua numina voce moveret?, Vg.; carmine di superi placantur, carmine m-es, Hor. - quisque suos patimur m-es <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(straff, luttringar i underjorden?),</text:span> Vg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mango,</text:span> ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Slafhandlare;</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> i allm.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">krämare,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> s. upputsar l. -stofferar och utprånglar gamla waror:</text:span> Hor.; m-es colorem fuco et verum robur inani sagina mentiuntur, Qu.; spadones, qui apud m-es erant - -, Su.; puer sectus arte m-is, Mt. -; m. gemmarum, Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mangōnĭcus</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Krämare-, slafhandlare-:</text:span></text:span> quæstus, Su.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mangōnium</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">n.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">tillredning med konst (om konstgödning af höns):</text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mangōnizo</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Upputsa, -stufwa</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> (för att säljas):</text:span> Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mānia,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(besl. med</text:span> mānes): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">spöke, sås. phantasibild l. docka:</text:span> M-a mater Larum, Varr.; ficta quædam ex farina in hominum figuras. - M-as, quas nutrices minitentur pueris parvulis, (dicunt) esse larvas, i. e. manes. - Sunt, qui M-am larvarum matrem aviamve putant, Paul. Diac.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Māniŏla</text:span>, ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: id.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mănĭa,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: v. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">ursinne:</text:span> Cæl.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Manica, -catus, -cula <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mănus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mănĭfestus</text:span> <text:line-break/>(manŭfestus), <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(af</text:span> mănus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och st. i</text:span> of-fendo?): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.: med handen gripen, ertappad:</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i fråga om brott:</text:span> <text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gripen på bar gerning, ertappad</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> med ngt, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">förwunnen</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> till ngt:</text:span> homo, Pt.; m-um habere alqm (ɔ: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">hafwa klara bewis på ngn);</text:span> m. tanti sceleris, rerum capitalium, Sa.; uxor delicti m-a, T.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om brottet sjelf l. bewisen derför: (notorisk), </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Handgriplig, uppenbar, öppen, ögonskenlig:</text:span></text:span> scelus m-um et deprehensum; furtum; in m-o peccatu teneri; res m-as proferre, C.; cædes m-a, L.; fraus m-ior, Pn.; scelus m-simum, Qu.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i allm.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">handgriplig, ögonskenlig, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Tydlig, otwifwelaktig:</text:span></text:span> m-a rotæ vestigia cernes; deus m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> præsens), Ov.; m-us multo lumine; te majoribus ire per altum auspiciis, m-a fides; amaror, Vg.; m-um cælibis obsequium, Hor.; hoc m-um facit <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">acc. cum inf.</text:span>), Pn.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om personer: s. tydligt röjer, wisar, låter märka ngt</text:span> [<text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">gen.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(jfr</text:span> 1. a.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">inf.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">efter grekisk construction</text:span>]: vitæ m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. röjer tecken till lif);</text:span> Aper - m. est jamdudum in contrarium accingi, T.; m-a doloris, Ov.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭfestārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(notorisk) </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Gripen på bar gerning; klar; bewisad:</text:span></text:span> fur; res, Pt.; soloecismus, Gell. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭfeste</text:span>,<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭfesto</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>: p. tr. gr.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">På bar gerning; handgripligen, ögonskenligen, bewisligen, tydligt, uppenbarligen:</text:span></text:span> in furto m-o prehendi; m-o fur es, Pt.; conjuratio m-e <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> m-o inventa ac deprehensa; indicia m-o comperisse et manu tenere, C.; quid struat, m-ius ipsi apparet quam regi, Vg. m-sime, Ap.<text:line-break/><text:soft-page-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭfesto</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Röja, wisa, bewisa:</text:span></text:span> nitor galeæ - latentem, Ov.; Parthos Scytharum exsules esse, ipsorum vocabulo <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(namn)</text:span> m-atur, Js.<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭfestātor</text:span>, ōris <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: Non.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ānīlius, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Mānīliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">Maniola <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mānia.<text:line-break/>Maniplus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Manipulus.<text:line-break/>Manipretium <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">se</text:span> Mănus.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Mănĭpŭlus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:line-break/>(Mănīplus, <text:line-break/>Mănŭpŭlus, <text:line-break/>Mănūplus; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl. de gamle etymologerne af</text:span> manus, <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">men sättet är oförklarligt):</text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(handfull,</text:span> Isid.) <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Hö-</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">strå-bundt, -knippe; hög, famn</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af hö, strå:</text:span> de herba, quum peraruit, m-os facere, Varr.; feni m.; vincire m-os, Col.; m-os mille ducentos, quaterna pondo, alligare, Pn.; soluti m-i; filicum m-is sternere humum (stabuli), Vg.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T1">Manipel</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> = </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">rote,</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> afdelning af romerska infanteriet (= 1/30 af en legion = 2:ne</text:span> centuriæ = 120 <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">man</text:span> hastati <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> principes, 60 triarii): m-i minimæ manus, quæ unum signum sequuntur, Varr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">enl.</text:span> Ov. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">så kallad af sitt fälttecken:</text:span> pertică suspensos portabat longa maniplos <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(höbundtar);</text:span> imperator turmas et m-os circumiit, Sa.; ad signa m-os continere; m-os laxare, Cs.; m-is centuriones imponere, L. - m. furum <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(skämts.),</text:span> Ter. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭpŭlāris</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst., m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">till rote hörande:</text:span> miles m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> m. = <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rotesoldat, </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Simpel soldat</text:span></text:span> (= miles gregarius); <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">soldat ur ngns rote:</text:span> miles m., Ov.; imperator, judex m. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(s. tjenat sig upp från - -)</text:span> C.; me torquet, quod non Pompejum ut unus m. secutus sum, C.; scurræ laudant, m-es mussitant; m-es mei, Pt.; centurio tres suos nactus m-es murum ascendit, Cs. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭpŭlārius</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: habitus <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(simpel soldats),</text:span> Su. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mănĭpŭlātim</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">Adv.</text:span>:<text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Bundtwis:</text:span></text:span> Pn.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Manipelwis, rotwis; i hopar:</text:span></text:span> m. structa acies; non m., sed latronum modo vagantur; dispersi - m. excurrunt ad vim arcendam, L.; præfecti m. allocuti sunt milites, T.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commănĭpŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (Inscr.):<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commănĭpŭlo</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (Sp.):<text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commănĭpŭlāris</text:span>, is, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: (T.): <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rotekamrat.</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Commănĭpŭlātio</text:span>, ōnis, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">-kamratskap:</text:span></text:span> Sp.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>ānius (M’), i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">romerskt prænomen (enl.</text:span> Varr. = mane natus).</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>anlius, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">och</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">Subst.,</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">rom. gentilnamn.</text:span> <text:line-break/>Manliānus, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span></text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Manna,</text:span> ae, <text:span text:style-name="T1">f.</text:span> = mica turis, croci: Pn., Veg.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1">I. <text:span text:style-name="T3">Mannus,</text:span> i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Häst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af (liten) gallisk race:</text:span> anguis territat m-os; m-is impositus, Hor.; rapientes esseda m-i, Ov.; Ppt. <text:line-break/><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mannŭlus</text:span>, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="T1">Dem.</text:span>: Pn.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:soft-page-break/>II. <text:span text:style-name="T3">M</text:span>annus, i, <text:span text:style-name="T1">m.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">myth. personn. hos Germanerne:</text:span> T. Germ. 3.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Māno,</text:span> 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Rinna, flyta, drypa, strömma, flöda:</text:span></text:span><text:line-break/>1. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">eg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om wätskan, s. rinner o. s. w.:</text:span> latices perennes, Lucr.; cruor non de stipite m-at; flumina pressis mammis, Vg.; sudor ad talos imos; mella ex ilice; imbres in agros, Hor.; rivi ex montium radicibus, Ct.; guttæ de vulnere, Ov.; - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bildl:</text:span> omne supervacuum pleno de pectore m-at, Hor.<text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om kroppen, s. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">flödar, dryper</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af ngt:</text:span> Herculis simulacrum sanguine, C.; culter cruore, L.; sanie, Pn.; alveus m-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(läckar),</text:span> T. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">med</text:span> <text:span text:style-name="T1">accus.</text:span>: arbor picem, Pn.; lacrimas marmora, Ov. - <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> fidis, te solum m-re poētica mella, Hor.<text:line-break/>c. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">om ljus, luft, ljud m. m.: </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Strömma, flöda, sprida, utbreda sig:</text:span></text:span> āer per maria; multa e luna m-ant, quibus animantes alantur, C.; foras per artus anima <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(i döden),</text:span> Lucr.; sonitus per āera, Lucr.; dies m-at <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">(rinner upp)</text:span> ab oriente, Varr.; <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">i bild:</text:span> m-bit tibi copia benigno cornu, Hor.<text:line-break/>2. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">oeg.:</text:span><text:line-break/>a. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Utbreda, sprida sig, sträcka sig:</text:span></text:span> malum per Italiam, in dies latius; fama; sermo; alqd sine capite <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur">l.</text:span> auctore; nomen bonæ fidei m-at latissime, C.; m-at tota urbe rumor, L. <text:line-break/>b. <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Härflyta, härröra, hafwa sin källa i</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> l. </text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">uppkomst</text:span></text:span><text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"> af, från:</text:span> proposui genera quattuor, e quibus honestas officiumque m-ret; videre, unde omnia m-ent; peccata e vitiis; ab Aristippo Cyrenaica philosophia m-vit, C.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Mānābĭlis</text:span>, <text:span text:style-name="T1">A.</text:span>: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Genomträngande:</text:span></text:span> frigus, Lucr.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dēmāno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Flyta ned:</text:span></text:span> potus per pulmonem, Gell.</text:p>
   <text:p text:style-name="P1"><text:span text:style-name="T2">Dīmāno</text:span>, 1.: <text:span text:style-name="Fraktur"><text:span text:style-name="T3">Sprida sig, utbreda sig:</text:span></text:span> flamma sub artus (al.: demanat), Catl.; meus labor forensis - ad existimationem hominum paulo latius d-vit commemoratione - meorum, C.</text:p>
  </office:text>
 </office:body>
</office:document>